\id LEV
\h Ilawiyyen 
\toc1 Ilawiyyen 
\toc2 Ilawiyyen 
\toc3 Lawi 
\mt1 Ilawiyyen  
\c 1
\s1 Tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ  
\m
\v 1 Iřaɣa i Musa uca issiweř SIDI akides zeg Uqiḍun n Umsagar, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca ini asen:  
\b  
\m ‘Mařa issqarreb ijj n bnadem zzaywem tawhibt i SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad dd-tessqarrbem \bd tawhibt nwem zi řebhayem\bd*, zeg ifunasen d tfunasin niɣ zeg wuǧi. \f ◼ \fr 1:2 \ft \+fk niɣ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘u’.\f*   
\m
\v 3 Mařa tawhibt nnes d \bd taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ zeg ifunasen d tfunasin\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad dd-issqarreb ijj n uwtem icnan qaɛ. Ad t yiwi ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, maḥend ad yaf arḍa zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 4 Ad yegg afus nnes x uzeǧif n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca ammu i ɣa tᵉttwaqbeř \add tɣarṣt\add* s arḍa di ṭṭweɛ nnes, maḥend ad yiři i weṣřaḥ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Uf. 29:10\x*  
\v 5 Ad iɣarṣ i umeẓyan n ufunas zzat i wudem n SIDI uca arraw n Harun, ikehhanen, ad dd-iwyen idammen, ad zeǧɛen idammen ɣar marra iɣezdisen x uɛalṭar nni iǧan ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 6 Ad ikkes tiřmect n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca ad ibḍa \add afunas\add* d iceǧiqen.  
\v 7 Arraw n akehhan Harun ad ssarɣen timessi x uɛalṭar uca ad settfen akeccuḍ x tmessi.  
\v 8 Arraw n Harun, ikehhanen, ad settfen iceǧiqen d uzeǧif d tadunt x ukeccuḍ nni iǧan x tmessi i iǧan x uɛalṭar.  
\v 9 Netta ad issird adan nnes d iḍaren nnes s waman. Akehhan ad issbexxar man aya marra x uɛalṭar, aqa d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, d tawhibt n tmessi, d ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI.   
\m
\v 10 Mařa tawhibt nnes d \bd taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ zeg wuǧi\bd*, zeg iḥuřiyyen niɣ zeg iɣayḍen, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad dd-issqarreb awtem icnan qaɛ.  
\v 11 Ad as iɣarṣ zzat i wudem n SIDI ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal n uɛalṭar uca arraw n Harun, ikehhanen, ad zeǧɛen idammen nnes x uɛalṭar ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes.  
\v 12 Ad t ibḍa d iceǧiqen, ak-d azeǧif nnes d tadunt nnes, uca akehhan ad ten isettef x ukeccuḍ nni iǧan x tmessi \add i iǧan\add* x uɛalṭar.  
\v 13 Ad issird adan nnes d icekraden nnes s waman. Akehhan ad yawi man aya marra u ad t issbexxar x uɛalṭar. \add Aqa\add* d ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, ict n tewhibt n tmessi, ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI.   
\m
\v 14 Mařa tawhibt nnes d \bd taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ zeg ijḍaḍ\bd* i SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad yawi tawhibt nnes zi tejlilliḥin niɣ zeg idbiren imeẓyanen.  
\v 15 Akehhan ad t yawi ɣar uɛalṭar, ad as ikkes azeǧif uca ad t issbexxar x uɛalṭar. Ad iẓemm idammen nnes x uɣezdis n uɛalṭar  
\v 16 uca ad as ikkes aseyru ak-d min dayes iqqimen u ad inḍar aya zzat i uɛalṭar ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq x wemcan n iɣɣeḍ n min iqqimen n tadunt  
\v 17 Ad t icarreg ɣar wefriwen, \add maca\add* war t ibeṭṭi ca qaɛ, uca akehhan ad t issbexxar x uɛalṭar, x ukeccuḍ nni iǧan x tmessi. Aqa d ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, d ict n tewhibt n tmessi, d ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Tiɣarṣa n řɣiǧet  
\m
\v 1 “Mařa iqeddem ḥed \bd tawhibt \+bdit n řɣiǧet\+bdit*\bd* ɣar SIDI, ad tiři tewhibt nnes n waren azdad uca ad xas iseyyeb zzect uca ad xas issars jjawi. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Uf. 6:15; 9:17; Řxř. 15:4\x*  
\v 2 Ad tt yawi ɣar warraw n Harun, ikehhanen, uca ad zzayes iksi ukehhan ijj n wuru iccur zeg waren azdad nni u zi zzect nni ak-d marra jjawi, uca akehhan ad issbexxar aya x uɛalṭar i řidaret \add i tewhibt nni\add*, aqa d ict n tewhibt n tmessi d ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Lawi 6:8\x*  
\v 3 Min iqqimen n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* \add ad yiři\add* i Harun u i warraw nnes. \add Aqa\add* d amqeddas qaɛ zi marra tiwhibin n tmessi n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Lawi 10:12\x*   
\m
\v 4 Mařa tqeddmed tawhibt i iǧan d \bd tawhibt \+bdit n řɣiǧet\+bdit* darḥen tt di tefqunt\bd*, \add xenni ad tiři\add* d řemsemnat břa antun, ixeǧḍen s zzect, uřa d tiřfaf břa antun ttwadehnent s zzect, \add marra\add* zeg waren azdad.   
\m
\v 5 Mařa tawhibt nnec d \bd tawhibt \+bdit n řɣiǧet\+bdit* ggʷin tt x wexdim\bd*, ad tiři n waren azdad ixeǧḍen s zzect, wardayes bu wentun.   
\m
\v 6 Ad ten tarẓed d ifetwiten uca ad xas tseyybed zzect. Aqa-tt d ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*.   
\m
\v 7 Mařa tawhibt nnec d \bd tawhibt \+bdit n řɣiǧet\+bdit* ggʷin tt di ṭṭajjin\bd*, ad tiři tewjed s waren azdad ak-d zzect.  
\v 8 Tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i zzaysen iwejden, ad tt tawyed ɣar SIDI. Bnadem ad zzayes dd-iqarreb ɣar ukehhan uca wanita ad tt yawi ɣar uɛalṭar.  
\v 9 Ad iksi ukehhan zi tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* ict n řidaret uca ad \add tt\add* issbexxar x uɛalṭar, \add aqa\add* d tawhibt n tmessi, d řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI.  
\v 10 Min iqqimen n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* ad yiři i Harun u i warraw nnes. \add Aqa-t\add* d amqeddas qaɛ zi tewhibin n tmessi n SIDI.   
\m
\v 11 War iɛeddeř i uřa d ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i ɣa tqeddmem i SIDI ad tiři tewjed s wentun. Maɣar zi min ma n wentun d zi min ma tamment war zzayes tessbexxaram ca uřa d ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI.   
\m
\v 12 Ad tiwyem \bd tawhibt n usuffeɣ amezwaru \+bdit n ṣṣabet\+bdit*\bd* ɣar SIDI, maca nitni war zemmaren ad ssbexxaren \add tawhibt-a\add* x uɛalṭar \add am\add* řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Řxř. 18:12\x*   
\m
\v 13 Kuř tawhibt n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* nnec ad tiři tmeǧḥed s tmeǧaḥṭ. Tameǧaḥt n Řɛahd n AREBBI nnec war tzemmar ad tenqeṣ ɣar tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* nnec. Ad tqeddmed tameǧaḥt ɣar kuř tawhibt nnec. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt Mk. 9:49\x*   
\m
\v 14 Mařa tiwyed ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* n tmenzut, ad tiwyed tidrin yiwḍen, tinni ittwafaren x tmessi, ak-d řḥebb aziza ibaryen am tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* zi tmenzut nnec.  
\v 15 Ad xas tseyybed zzect u ad xas tessarsed jjawi, aqa d tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*.  
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* ad issbexxar ukehhan \add ijj n wezyen\add* zi řḥebb ibaryen u zi zzect nnes ak-d marra jjawi nnes i xas iǧan am tewhibt n řidaret di man aya. \add Aqa\add* d tawhibt n tmessi i SIDI.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Tiɣarṣa n řeḥna  
\m
\v 1 “Mařa tawhibt nnes d \bd taɣarṣt n řehna\bd*, ittxeṣṣa, mařa xenni issqarreb-dd \add amuddar\add*, ad yiři d awtem \add niɣ\add* d tawtemt \bd n ifunasen d tfunasin\bd*, ad dd-issqarreb \add ijj n umuddar\add* icnan qaɛ zzat i wudem n SIDI.   
\m
\v 2 Ad issars afus nnes x uzeǧif n tewhibt nnes uca ad as iɣarṣ qibač i wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca arraw n Harun, ikehhanen, ad zeǧɛen idammen nnes x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen \add nnes\add*.  
\v 3 Zi tewhibt n řehna ad iqeddem ict tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI, \add ixs ad yini\add* tadunt i idřin adan d marra tadunt \add i iǧan\add* x wadan. \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Uf. 29:13, 22\x*  
\v 4 Ad ikkes tnayen n tiẓẓař ak-d tadunt i xasent \add iǧan\add* ɣar tejɛinna uřa d min yuyřen ɣar tsa u \add yarsa\add* x tiẓẓař. \f ◼ \fr 3:4 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’. Uřa di ayat 10 d 15.\f*  
\v 5 Arraw n Harun ad ssbexxaren aya x uɛalṭar x tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i iǧan x ukeccuḍ i din iǧan x tmessi. Aqa-t d tawhibt n tmessi, d ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Uf. 29:25; Lawi 6:5\x*   
\m
\v 6 Mařa tawhibt nnes d \bd taɣarṣt n řehna\bd* i SIDI, awtem \add niɣ\add* d tawtemt \bd n wuǧi\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad dd-issqarreb \add ijj n umudar\add* icnan qaɛ.   
\m
\v 7 Mařa \bd d uḥuři\bd* i dd-issqarreb d taɣarṣt, \add xenni\add* ad t-i-dd issqarreb zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 8 Netta ad issars afus nnes x uzeǧif n tewhibt nnes uca ad as iɣarṣ zzat i Uqiḍun n Umsagar, uca arraw n Harun ad zeǧɛen idammen nnes x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen \add nnes\add*.  
\v 9 Ad iqeddem tadunt n tɣarṣt n řehna am yict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI: marra tanewwart \add n tadunt\add* nni yudsen abeɛṣuṣ ad tt ikkes, uřa d tadunt i idřin adan d marra tadunt \add i iǧan\add* x wadan  
\v 10 uca ad ikkes uřa d tnayen n tiẓẓař ak-d tadunt i xasent \add iǧan\add* ɣar tejɛinna d min yuyřen ɣar tsa u \add yarsa\add* x tiẓẓař.  
\v 11 Akehhan ad issbexxar aya x uɛalṭar. \add Aqa\add* d macca, ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt Lawi 21:6, 8, 17, 21, 22; 22:25; Ḥiz. 44:7; Mal. 1:12\x*   
\m
\v 12 Mařa tawhibt nnes d \bd iɣayḍ\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad t-i-dd-issqarreb zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 13 Ad issars afus nnes x uzeǧif nnes uca ad as iɣarṣ zzat i Uqiḍun n Umsagar, uca arraw n Harun ad zeǧɛen \add cwayt n\add* idammen nnes x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen \add nnes\add*.  
\v 14 Ad zzayes iqeddem tawhibt nnes, \add ixs ad yini\add* tadunt i idřin adan, u marra tadunt i \add iǧan\add* x wadan, am tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI  
\v 15 uca ad ikkes uřa d tnayen n tiẓẓař ak-d tadunt i xasent \add iǧan\add* ɣar tejɛinna uřa d min yuyřen ɣar tsa u \add yarsa\add* x tiẓẓař.  
\v 16 Akehhan ad issbexxar aya x uɛalṭar, \add aqa\add* d macca n tewhibt n tmessi s ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen. Marra tadunt \add ad tiři\add* i SIDI.  
\v 17 \add Ta\add* d tawṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem, mani ma i ɣa tzedɣem: marra tadunt d marra idammen war ten ttᵉttem.” \x ◘ \xo 3:17 \xt Amz. 9:4; Lawi 7:26; 17:10, 14\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 Tiɣarṣa n ddenb  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini:  
\m ‘\bd Mařa ca n yijjen ixḍa am iweddar\bd* x marra tiweṣṣa n SIDI, min war ittxeṣṣi ad ittwagg, u netta ixḍa deg ict zzaysent, \add xenni ad tiři tmesřact ammu\add*:   
\m
\v 3 \bd Mařa akehhan amedhun ixḍa\bd*, ařami idweř řgens ixḍa, ad dd-issqarreb ijj n ufunas. - ameẓyan icnan qaɛ n ict n tfunast - am tɣarṣt n ddenb i SIDI di ṭṭweɛ n ddenb nnes i igga.  
\v 4 Ad yawi afunas \add nni\add* ameẓyan ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, zzat i wudem n SIDI, uca netta ad issars afus nnes x uzeǧif n ufunas ameẓyan uca ad as iɣarṣ i ufunas ameẓyan zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* akehhan amedhun ad iksi \add ca\add* zeg idammen n ufunas ameẓyan uca ad t yawi ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 6 Ad issuf ukehhan aḍaḍ nnes deg idammen uca ad irucc ca zeg idammen nni sebɛa n twařawin zzat i wudem n SIDI, zzat i uřeḥḥaf n Zzawect Iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Lawi 16:14; Řxř. 19:4\x*  
\v 7 Ad igg ukehhan \add cwayt\add* n idammen x waccawen n uɛalṭar i řebxur ittfuḥen i \add din\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar. Netta ad ifarreɣ marra idammen \add i iqqimen\add* n ufunas ameẓyan ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar. \f ◼ \fr 4:7 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’. Uřa di ayat 18, 25, 30 d 34.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Lawi 9:9\x*  
\v 8 Ad ikkes marra tadunt n ufunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt: tadunt i idřin adan d marra tadunt \add i iǧan\add* x wadan \f ◼ \fr 4:8 \ft \+fk Ad ikkes\ft  - s Tɛibranit’ ‘ad issgaɛɛed’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Lawi 3:3, 4\x*  
\v 9 uca ad ikkes tnayen n tiẓẓař ak-d tadunt i xasent \add iǧan\add* ɣar tejɛinna uřa d min yuyřen ɣar tsa u \add yarsa\add* x tiẓẓař, \f ◼ \fr 4:9 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*  
\v 10 am mammec ikkes man aya x ufunas n tɣarṣi n řehna, uca akehhan ad issbexxar aya x uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 4:10 \xt Lawi 3:5\x*  
\v 11 Iřem n ufunas ameẓyan d marra aysum nnes ak-d uzeǧif d icekrad nnes d wadan nnes d umessař nnes \add i dayes\add*, \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Uf. 29:14; Řxř. 19:5\x*  
\v 12 aqa marra afunas ameẓyan ad t issuffeɣ barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ɣar ijj n wemcan iṣfa mani tteggen iɣɣeḍ i iqqimen n tadunt uca ad t issecmeḍ s tmessi x ukeccuḍ. Ad t cemḍen mani zeǧɛen iɣɣeḍ. \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Lawi 16:27; Řxř. 19:3; Ɛbr. 13:11\x*   
\m
\v 13 \bd Mařa teffeɣ tmesmunt n Israil marra zeg webrid\bd* uca teffar tmesřact x tiṭṭawin n wegraw \add n řgens\add*, uca nitni ggin ict \add n řḥajjet\add* \add nni iffɣen\add* x marra tiweṣṣa n SIDI, \add zi jjihet n\add* min war ittxeṣṣi ad yegg, uca idweř daysen umarwas, \x ◘ \xo 4:13 \xt Lawi 9:15; Řxř. 15:24-31\x*  
\v 14 uca iban-dd ddenb i zi iffɣen x webrid n řumurat, \add xenni\add* ad dd-issqarreb wegraw \add n řgens\add* ijj n ufunas - ameẓyan n tfunast - d taɣarṣt i ddenb, uca ad t awyen zzat i Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 15 Imɣaren n tmesmunt ad ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif n ufunas ameẓyan zzat i wudem n SIDI uca netta ad as iɣarṣ i ufunas \add nni\add* ameẓyan zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 16 Akehhan amedhun ad yawi \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n ufunas ameẓyan ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar,  
\v 17 uca ad issuf ukehhan aḍaḍ nnes deg idammen uca ad irucc \add s idammen nni\add* sebɛa n twařawin zzat i wudem n SIDI, zzat i uřeḥḥaf.  
\v 18 Netta ad igg \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen \add nni\add* x waccawen n uɛalṭar nni \add iǧan\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar. \add Xenni\add* ad ifarreɣ marra idammen \add iceṭṭen\add* ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar n wecmad i din zzat i wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 19 Ad xas ikkes marra tadunt uca ad \add tt\add* issbexxar x uɛalṭar.  
\v 20 Uca ad igg s ufunas ameẓyan am mammec igga s ufunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb, ammu i ɣa yegg. Akehhan ad xasen igg aṣřaḥ uca ad asen ittwaɣfar. \f ◼ \fr 4:20 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ad issuffeɣ afunas ameẓyan barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar uca ad t issecmeḍ am mammec issecmeḍ afunas amezwaru. \add Aqa-tt\add* d taɣarṣt n ddenb n wegraw \add n řgens\add*.   
\m
\v 22 \bd Mařa ijj n řḥakem ixḍa,\bd* uca s uweddar igga ict n řḥajjet \add nni itteffɣen x webrid\add* n marra tiweṣṣa n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, i war ittcuwwaren ad ittwagg, uca idweř dayes umarwas,  
\v 23 niɣ \add mařa\add* ittwassargeb as uxeṭṭu nnes i igga ḍidd i \add řumur\add*, ad tiři tewhibt nnes, tenni i ɣa iqeddem, d ijj n umyan zeg iɣayḍen, ijj n wewtem icnan qaɛ.  
\v 24 Ad issars afus nnes x uzeǧif n umyan uca ad as iɣarṣ deg wemcan mani ɣarṣen i taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ zzat i wudem n SIDI. \add Aqa\add* d taɣarṣt n ddenb.  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* ad iksi ukehhan s uḍaḍ nnes \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n tɣarṣt n ddenb uca ad ten igg x waccawen n uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ uca \add xenni\add* ad ifarreɣ idammen \add iceṭṭen\add* ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ.  
\v 26 Ad issbexxar marra tadunt nnes x uɛalṭar, am mammec \add d as igga i\add* tadunt n tɣarṣt n řehna. Akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ di ṭṭweɛ n ddenb nnes uca ad as ittwaɣfar. \f ◼ \fr 4:26 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*   
\m
\v 27 \bd Mařa ijjen bnadem zi řgens n temmurt ixḍa s uweddar\bd* am igga \add mɣir\add* ict n řḥajjet \add nni itteffɣen\add* x icten n tweṣṣa n SIDI, min war ittcuwwar ad ittwagg, uca idweř dayes umarwas, \x ◘ \xo 4:27 \xt Řxř. 15:27\x*  
\v 28 niɣ ittwassargeb as uxeṭṭu nnes i igga, \add xenni\add* ad tiři tewhibt nnes nni i ɣa iqeddem d \bd ict n tɣayḍet\bd*, ict n tewtemt icnan qaɛ, d taɣarṣt x ddenb i igga.  
\v 29 Ad issars afus nnes x uzeǧif n tɣarṣt n ddenb uca ad as iɣarṣ i tɣarṣt n ddenb deg wemcan n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* ad iksi ukehhan s uḍaḍ nnes \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen uca ad t igg ɣar waccawen n uɛalṭar n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca ad ifarreɣ marra idammen \add iceṭṭen\add* ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar.  
\v 31 Ad xas ikkes marra tadunt nnes am mammec kksen tadunt n tɣarṣt n řehna uca akehhan ad tt issbexxar x uɛalṭar, ad tiři d ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI. Uca akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ uca ad as ittwaɣfar. \x ◘ \xo 4:31 \xt Uf. 29:18; Lawi 3:3, 4 ,14\x*   
\m
\v 32 Mařa iqeddem \bd ijj n izmar\bd* d tawhibt i tɣarṣt n ddenb, \add xenni\add* ad iqeddem ict n tawtemt icnan qaɛ.  
\v 33 Ad issars afus nnes x uzeǧif n tɣarṣt n ddenb uca ad as iɣarṣ i tɣarṣt n ddenb deg wemcan mani ɣarṣen i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.  
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* ad iksi ukehhan s uḍaḍ nnes \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n tɣarṣt n ddenb uca ad t igg x waccawen n uɛalṭar n wecmaḍ uca ad ifarreɣ marra idammen nnes \add iceṭṭen\add* ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar.  
\v 35 Ad xas ikkes marra tadunt nnes, am mammec ikkes tadunt n uḥuři n tɣarṣt n řehna, uca akehhan ad tt issbexxar x uɛalṭar, x tewhibin n tmessi i SIDI uca akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ x ddenb i igga, uca ad as ittwaɣfar.’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\m
\v 1 “Mařa ixḍa ḥed \add umi\add* \bd isřa ahejji n ict n nneɛřet\bd* uca netta d acehhad xas, niɣ iẓra \add i-t\add* niɣ issen \add i-t\add*: mařa war \add xas\add* iqqar walu, \add xenni\add* ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet nnes. \f ◼ \fr 5:1 \ft \+fk ahejji\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘tmijja’.\f*   
\m
\v 2 Niɣ mařa \bd iḥada ḥed min ma zi tmesřact ixemjen\bd*, řxecbet n řmař ixmej, niɣ řxecbet n řebhimet ixemjen, niɣ řxecbet n \add umuddar\add* ixmej ittbuɛen, uca netta war issin \add aya\add*, aqa ixmej u dayes amarwas. \x ◘ \xo 5:2 \xt Ḥag. 2:13; 2 Kur. 6:17\x*   
\m
\v 3 Niɣ mařa \bd iḥada \+bdit ca n\+bdit* řexmej n bnadem\bd*, min ma zi řexmej nnes i zi idweř netta ixmej, mařa tennuffar xas uca issen it \add awarni as\add*, aqa dayes amarwas.   
\m
\v 4 Niɣ \bd mařa iẓẓuǧ ḥed s tcarfayeḥ nnes\bd*, maḥend ad igg řɣar niɣ ad igg řxar, \add niɣ\add* min ma izemmar bnadem ad inṭeq amenni waha s ict n tjaǧit, am war tt issin, \add maca\add* issen i-t \add awarni man aya\add*, aqa dayes amarwas di ssibbet n ict zi tmesřayin-a.   
\m
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* ad imsar, mařa dayes amarwas di ssibbet n icten \add zi tmesřayin-a\add*, ad inɛem x min tuɣa ixḍa. \f ◼ \fr 5:5 \ft \+fk icten \+bdit zi tmesřayin-a\+bdit*\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘icten zzaysent’, uřa di ayat 13.\f*  
\v 6 X ddenb i igga, ittxeṣṣa as ad iqeddem ict n tewtemt n wuǧi d taɣarṣt n umarwas, ict n texsi niɣ ict n tɣayḍet, d taɣarṣt n ddenb i SIDI, uca akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ di ssibbet n ddenb nnes.\f ◼ \fr 5:6 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*   
\m
\v 7 Maca mařa afus nnes war \add ɣares min\add* iqedden i yijj zeg wuǧi, \add xenni\add* ad yawi i SIDI i tɣarṣt n umarwas x ddenb i igga, tnayen n tejlilliḥin niɣ tnayen n idbiren imeẓyanen, ijjen i tɣarṣt n ddenb u ijjen i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 5:7 \xt Lawi 12:8; Lk. 2:24\x*  
\v 8 Ad ten yawi ɣar ukehhan, wenni dd ɣa yawyen d amezwaru \add tajlilliḥt niɣ aḍbir\add* i \add iǧan\add* i tɣarṣt n ddenb uca ad ikkes azeǧif nnes zi cwayt awarni yiri nnes, \add maca\add* war t ibeṭṭi \add marra\add*. \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Lawi 1:15\x*  
\v 9 Ad irucc \add cwayt\add* n idammen ɣar uɣezdis n uɛalṭar uca min iceṭṭen zeg idammen, ad \add t\add* iẓemm ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar. \add Aqa-tt\add* d taɣarṣt n ddenb.  
\v 10 Ad issewjed \add ameddar\add* nneɣni am tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ ɛlaḥsab lfariḍa uca \add ammu\add* i xas i ɣa yegg ukehhan aṣřaḥ x ddenb nnes i igga uca ad as ittwaɣfar.\x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Lawi 1:15\x*  
\v 11 Mařa afus nnes war \add ɣares min\add* iqedden i tnayen n tejlilliḥin niɣ i tnayen n idbiren imeẓyanen, \add xenni\add* wenni ixḍan, ad yawi am tewhibt nnes taɛcart n ijj n ifa n waren azdad d tawhibt n ddenb. War xas ittegg zzect uřa war xas issrusi jjawi, minzi aqa-tt d taɣarṣt n ddenb.  
\v 12 Ad tt yawi ɣar ukehhan uca akehhan ad zzayes iksi ijj n wuru iccur uca ad issbexxar aya am řidaret dayes x uɛalṭar, x tewhibin n tmessi i SIDI. \add Aqa-tt\add* d taɣarṣt n ddenb. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Lawi 2:2; 4:35\x*  
\v 13 \add Ammu i\add* xas ɣa yegg ukehhan aṣřaḥ x ddenb nnes nni igga zi jjihet n icten zi tmesřayin-a uca ad as ittwaɣfar. Min iceṭṭen ad yiři i ikehhanen am mammec \add i yeǧan ak-d\add* tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*.” \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt Lawi 2:3\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tiɣarṣa n umarwas  
\m
\v 14 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 15 “Mařa igga ḥed s řeɣdar uca \bd ixḍa s uweddar di tmesřayin iqeddsen n SIDI\bd*, ittxeṣṣa ad yawi icarri icnan qaɛ zeg wuǧi d taɣarṣt n umarwas i SIDI. \add Ad tiři řqimet nnes\add* ɛlaḥsab řqimet i tqeddared cek deg iciqluten n nnuqart ɛlaḥsab ciqlu n Zzawect Iqeddsen. \add Aqa\add* d taɣarṣt n umarwas. \x ◘ \xo 5:15 \xt Uf. 30:13; Lawi 27:2-27.\x*  
\v 16 Zi tmesřayin iqeddsen ad yarr di min di ixḍa qbeř, uca ad dayes yarni řexmus. Uca ad iwc man aya i ukehhan uca akehhan ad t isseṣřeḥ s icarri n tɣarṣt n umarwas uca ad as ittwaɣfar.  
\v 17 Mařa ixḍa ḥed uca igga ict n tmesřact i war tᵉttcuwwar ad tᵉttwagg, \add am dd-iffeɣ\add* deg ict n tmesřact zi tweṣṣa n SIDI, uca tuɣa tnuffar xas, ad dayes yiři umarwas uca ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet nnes.  
\v 18 Ad yawi ijj n icarri icnan qaɛ zeg wuǧi ɣar ukehhan i tɣarṣt n umarwas, \add ad tiři řqimet nnes\add* ɛlaḥsab řqimet i tqeddared cek uca ad t isseṣřeḥ ukehhan x uweddar nnes i di iweddar am war t issin uca ad as ittwaɣfar.  
\v 19 Aqa d taɣarṣt n umarwas. S tidett tuɣa dayes amarwas zzat i SIDI.”   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 21 “Mařa ixḍa ḥed uca iɣdar SIDI am issxarriq x jjar nnes x min \add d as\add* immewcen, maḥend ad t iḥḍa, niɣ x min ijja deg ufus nnes, niɣ x min \add xas\add* yucaren, niɣ x ca n ubeɛɛej i igga i jjar nnes,  
\v 22 niɣ am issxarriq x \add ca\add* min iweddaren \add i ca n yijjen\add* u ittwaf zzayes uca \add xenni\add* netta ijjuǧ ẓur, \add wah, am issxarriq netta\add* x icten zi marra \add timesřayin nni\add* ittegg bnadem ařami ixeṭṭa s man aya, \x ◘ \xo 5:22 \xt Num 5:6\x*  
\v 23 xenni ittxeṣṣa, umi ixḍa uca idweř dayes umarwas, aqa netta ad dd-yarr tuceffart nni yucar, niɣ min ittwakksen nni iksi netta s uɣiř, niɣ min tuɣa iḥḍa nni d as immewcen maḥend ad tt iḥḍa, niɣ min iweddaren nni yufa.  
\v 24 Uca marra min xef ijjuǧ ẓur, ad dd-yarr řqimet nnes tmun uca ad yarni řexmus. Netta ad t iwc i wenni umi dd-tusa deg wass n tɣarṣt nnes n umarwas.  
\v 25 Netta ad yawi taɣarṣt nnes n umarwas ɣar SIDI, ijj n icarri icnan qaɛ zeg wuǧi, \add wenni řqimet nnes ad tiři\add* ɛlaḥsab řqimet i tqeddared cek, ad tiři d taɣarṣt n umarwas, \add uca ad t yawi\add* ɣar ukehhan.  
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* akehhan ad xas igg asřaḥ zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ad as ittwaɣfar x min igga, mařa idweř dayes amarwas s ict n tmesřact zi marra timesřayin-a.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Umur Harun d warraw nnes, ini asen: ‘Wa d \bd azerf i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ\bd*. Taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ x ukeccuḍ x uɛalṭar ad teqqim tareqq ǧiřet tekmeř ař ṣṣbeḥ u ittxeṣṣa timessi n uɛalṭar ad teqqim ad tecmeḍ dayes.  
\v 3 Akehhan ad yarḍ aseřham nnes n řeqṭen, ad ibyes ssarwař nnes n řeqṭen x arrimet nnes, uca ad iksi iɣɣeḍ n min iqqimen n tadunt n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, tenni tecca tmessi, uca ad t issars zzat i uɛalṭar.  
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* ad ikkes arruḍ nnes uca ad yarḍ arruḍ nneɣni, ad yawi iɣɣeḍ n min iqqimen n tadunt barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ɣar yijj n wemcan iṣfa.  
\v 5 Ittxeṣṣa ad teqqim tmessi tareqq x uɛalṭar, ittxeṣṣa war txessi ca. Akehhan ad xas issarɣ akeccuḍ kuř ṣṣbeḥ uca ad xas isettef taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca ad xas issbexxar tadunt n tɣarṣa n řehna.  
\v 6 Timessi x uɛalṭar ad teqqim tareqq řebda, war txessi.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 7 “Wa d \bd azerf i tewhibt \+bdit n řɣiǧet\+bdit*\bd*. Arraw n Harun ad tt awyen zzat i wudem n SIDI zzat i uɛalṭar. \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt Řxř. 15:4-21.\x*  
\v 8 Netta ad zzayes iksi ijj n wuru zeg waren azdad n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* ak-d \add ca n\add* zzect nnes d marra jjawi i iǧan x tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*. Ad issbexxar \add aya x\add* uɛalṭar. \add Aqa\add* d ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen, ict n řidaret dayes i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 6:8 \xt Lawi 2:9\x*  
\v 9 Harun d warraw nnes ad ccen min zzayes iceṭṭen. Ittxeṣṣa ad t ccen břa antun deg wemcan amqeddas. Ad t ccen di řemraḥ n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 10 War iɛeddeř ad t ggʷen s wentun. Ta d taɣarṣt nsen nni wciɣ Necc zi tewhibin inu n tmessi. Aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ am tɣarṣt n ddenb d tɣarṣt n umarwas.  
\v 11 Marra iwetman jar warraw n Harun ad zzayes ccen. Aqa-tt d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda x tewhibin n tmessi n SIDI i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem. Marra wi tt ɣa iḥadan, ad ittwaqeddes.” \x ◘ \xo 6:11 \xt Uf. 29:37\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 13 “Ta d \bd tawhibt n Harun d warraw nnes\bd* i zi dd ɣa qarrben ɣar SIDI \bd deg wass min di i ɣa ittwadhen Harun\bd*: taɛcart n ijj n ifa n waren azdad \add am\add* ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i řebda, azyen nnes di ṣṣbeḥ d wezyen nnes \add nneɣni\add* ɣar uɛecci.  
\v 14 Deg ijj n uxdim ad tessewjed aya s zzect \add n zzitun\add* uca ad t tawyed \add d tawhibt\add* awarni t txeǧḍed. Ad tqeddmed iřeqqwaz ttwarẓan n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet am\add* ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI.  
\v 15 Akehhan nni ɣa dehnen deg wemcan nnes zeg iḥenjiren nnes, ad tt issewjed. Aqa-tt d tawṣeyyet i řebda. \add Tawhibt-a\add* ad tᵉttwabexxar i SIDI marra.  
\v 16 Marra tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* n ukehhan ad tiři tekmeř. War zzayes ttᵉtten ca.”   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 18 “Siweř ak-d Harun d warraw nnes, ini asen: ‘Wa d \bd azerf i tɣarṣt n ddenb\bd*: deg wemcan mani tᵉttwaɣarṣ taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, ad tᵉttwaɣarṣ \add ɛawed\add* taɣarṣt n ddenb zzat i wudem n SIDI. Aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ.  
\v 19 Akehhan nni tt ɣa iqeddmen d taɣarṣt ad zzayes yecc. Ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwacc deg ijj n wemcan amqeddas di řemraḥ n Uqiḍun n Umsagar. \x ◘ \xo 6:19 \xt Ḥuc. 4:8 \x*  
\v 20 Marra wi ɣa iḥadan aysum nnes ad \add zzayes\add* ittwaqeddes. Mařa ingez \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen x yijj n warruḍ, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad tessirded min xas ibeqqḍen deg ijj n wemcan amqeddas.  
\v 21 Uca řqecɛet n třaxt i di tt ssnennan, ad tᵉttwarẓ, \add maca\add* mařa ssenwen tt deg ict n řqecɛet n nnḥas, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad ḥekken u ad ssřiřen \add řqecɛet\add* s waman.  
\v 22 Marra wi iǧan d awtem jar ikehhanen ad zzayes yecc. Aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ.  
\v 23 \add Maca\add* uřa d ict n tɣarṣt n ddenb i zi ttwaqeddmen idammen nnes deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar, maḥend ad iřin i weṣřaḥ di Zzawect Iqeddsen, war zzayes ittwacc ca. Ad tᵉttwacmeḍ s tmessi.’” \x ◘ \xo 6:23 \xt Lawi 4:5; Ɛbr. 13:11\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\m
\v 1 “Wa d \bd azerf i tɣarṣt n umwarwas\bd*. Aqa d tamqeddast qaɛ.   
\m
\v 2 Deg wemcan mani ɣarrṣen i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, ad ɣarṣen i tɣarṣt n umarwas. Ad izeǧeɛ idammen nnes x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen \add nnes\add*.  
\v 3 Ad yawi marra tadunt nnes: anewwar n tadunt d tadunt nni idřin adan,  
\v 4 uca ad ikkes tnayen n tiẓẓař ak-d tadunt i xasent iǧan ɣar tejɛinna, uřa d min yuyřen ɣar tsa uca \add yarsa\add* x tiẓẓař, \f ◼ \fr 7:4 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*  
\v 5 uca akehhan ad issbexxar aya x uɛalṭar am yict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI. Aqa-tt d taɣarṣt n umarwas.  
\v 6 Marra awtem jar ikehhanen ad zzayes yecc. Ad ittwacc deg ijj n wemcan amqeddas, aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ.  
\v 7 Ad yiři ijj n uzerf am i tɣarṣt n ddenb am i tɣarṣt n umwarwas. Ad yiři \add weysum n tɣarṣt\add* i ukehhan, wenni tuɣa zzayes igg aṣřaḥ \add x ca n yijjen\add*. \f ◼ \fr 7:7 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  
\v 8 Akehhan nni i ɣa iqeddmen taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ n ca n ijjen, i ukehhan \add nni\add* \add ad tiři\add* teřmect n tɣarṣt n tmessi nni dd-iqeddem, \add tiřmect\add* ad tiři i netta.  
\v 9 Kuř tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* nni ḍarrḥen nitni di tefqunt uřa d marra min ittwasswejden di ṭṭajjin niɣ deg wexdim, d man aya ad yiři i ukehhan nni t iqeddmen, ad yiři i netta.  
\v 10 Kuř tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i ittwaxeǧḍen s zzect \add n zzitun\add* niɣ yuẓɣen, ad tiři i marra arraw n Harun, am i yijj am i wenneɣni.”   
\b  
\m
\v 11 “Wa d \bd azerf i tɣarṣt n řehna\bd* tenni i ɣa iqeddem \add bnadem\add* i SIDI.   
\m
\v 12 Mařa ad tt iqeddem \bd i uqadi\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad iqeddem ak-d \add tewhibt n\add* uqadi uřa d řemsemnat břa antun ixeǧḍen s zzect d teřfaf břa antun ttwadehnent s zzect d řemsemnat n waren azdad ttwaxeǧḍent s zzect. \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt Izhd. 116:17\x*  
\v 13 Ad iqeddem tawhibt nnes ak-d řemsemnat n weɣrum s wentun, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d \add tewhibt n\add* uqadi, \add tenni iǧan\add* zi tewhibin nnes n řehna.  
\v 14 Zi kuř \add ddarb n\add* tawhibt ad iqeddem icten zzayes \add am\add* tewhibt n usgeɛɛed i SIDI. \add Ad tiři\add* i ukehhan nni i ɣa izeǧɛen idammen n tɣarṣa n řehna x uɛalṭar \add ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes\add*, ad tiři i netta.  
\v 15 Aysum n tewhibt n uqadi, \add tenni iǧan zi\add* tewhibin nnes n řehna, ad ittwacc deg wass \add i di ɣa iqeddem\add* tawhibt nnes. War ittejji zzayes walu ař ṣṣbeḥ.   
\m
\v 16 Mařa tawhibt nnes \add tusa-dd ak-d\add* \bd ijj n lwaɛd\bd* niɣ \add teǧa\add* d \bd ict n tewhibt s řxaḍar\bd*, ad tᵉttwacc deg wass i di i ɣa iqeddem taɣarṣt nnes uca min zzayes iceṭṭen ad ittwacc deg wass i-t-i-dd-iḍfaren. \x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Lawi 19:6\x*  
\v 17 Min iceṭṭen ɛad zeg weysum n tɣarṣt ad ittwacmeḍ s tmessi deg wass wiss třata.  
\v 18 Mařa ittwacc \add ɛad\add* zeg weysum n tɣarṣt nnes n řehna deg wass wiss třata, \add xenni\add* wenni tt iqeddmen war ittiři i arḍa \add n SIDI\add* u \add taɣarṣt nnes\add* war d as tᵉttwiḥsib ca \add d taɣarṣt n řehna\add*. Ad tiři d ict n jjɛifect uca wenni zzayes ɣa iccen ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet nnes.  
\v 19 Aysum nni iḥadan ca n tmesřact ixemjen, war zzayes ttᵉttem. Ad t sscemḍen s tmessi. Zi \add min iceṭṭen n\add* weysum, izemmar ad zzayes yecc marra wenni izedgen.  
\v 20 D wenni i ɣa iccen zeg weysum n tɣarṣt n řehna, tenni iǧan i SIDI, am xas yarsa řexmej nnes, řeɛmar nni ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:20 \xt Lawi 15:3\x*  
\v 21 Mařa iḥada ḥed ca n tmesřact ixmej, \add amecnaw\add* řexmej n bnadem niɣ \add řexmej\add* n yict n řebhimet ixemjen niɣ ca n tmesřact i iǧan d nnɛi n řexmej, uca \add xenni\add* ad yecc zeg weysum n tɣarṣin n řehna i SIDI, řeɛmar nni ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tadunt d idammen aqa d řeḥram i macca  
\m
\v 22 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 23 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini: ‘Kenniw war ttᵉttem ca qaɛ tadunt n ufunas niɣ n izmar niɣ n iɣayḍ.  
\v 24 Tadunt n ict n řxecbet d tadunt n \add ijj n umuddar\add* mezzqen t, tɛeddeř ad tᵉttwagg i mammec ma tegga řxedmet, maca kenniw war zzayes ttᵉttem walu.  
\v 25 Man wen i ɣa iccen tadunt n yict n řebhimet i zi dd ɣa ssqarrben ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI, řeɛmar nni zzayes i ɣa iccen, ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes. \f ◼ \fr 7:25 \ft \+fk bnadem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*  
\v 26 Di marra tizeddiɣin nwem war ttᵉttem uřa d ca zeg idammen, am zeg ijḍaḍ am zi řebhayem. \x ◘ \xo 7:26 \xt Amz. 9:4; Lawi 3:17; 17:14\x*  
\v 27 Kuř ijj n řeɛmar nni i ɣa iccen \add mɣir ca\add* zeg idammen, řeɛmar nni ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tasɣart n tɣarṣa n řehna i ikehhanen  
\m
\v 28 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 29 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini: ‘Wi i dd ɣa issqarrben tɣarṣt nnes n řehna i SIDI, ad iqeddem tawhibt nnes i SIDI zi tɣarṣt n řehna nnes.  
\v 30 S ifassen nnes ad yawi tiwhibin n tmessi zzat i SIDI. Tadunt \add i iǧan\add* x idmaren ad tt yawi ak-d idmaren nni, maḥend ad tt issenhezz zi ssa ɣar da am yict n tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 7:30 \xt Uf. 29:24\x*  
\v 31 Akehhan ad issbexxar tadunt x uɛalṭar, \add maca\add* idmaren ad iřin i Harun d warraw nnes.  
\v 32 Zi tɣarṣa nwem n řehna ad tqeddmem i ukehhan \add ɛawed\add* acekrud afusi d tawhibt n usgeɛɛed.  
\v 33 Acekrud afusi ad yiři d tasɣart n wenni zeg warraw n Harun i ɣa iqeddmen idammen n tɣarṣi n řehna d tadunt \add nsent\add*.  
\v 34 Minzi Necc ksiɣ idmaren n wenhezzi d ucekrud i dd-ittwassgeɛɛden d tawhibt zi tɣarṣi n řehna n ayt n Israil u wciɣ ten i ukehhan Harun u i warraw nnes am yict n lfariḍa i řebda, zi jjihet n ayt n Israil.\x ◘ \xo 7:34 \xt Uf. 29:27; Řxř. 18:11\x*  
\v 35 Ta d tasɣart ittwassdehnen n Harun d tesɣart ittwassdehnen n warraw nnes zi tewhibin n tmessi n SIDI deg wass i ten dd-issqarreb, maḥend ad iřin d ikehhanen i SIDI,  
\v 36 \add tasɣart\add* nni iwca SIDI i ayt n Israil deg wass i ten idhen. Aqa d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 37 Wa d azerf i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tɣarṣt n ddenb d tɣarṣt n umarwas d tɣarṣa i udeccen d tɣarṣa n řehna,  
\v 38 \add azerf\add* i iweṣṣa SIDI i Musa deg wedrar n Sina, ass min di iweṣṣa ayt n Israil ad qeddmen tiwhibin nsen i SIDI di řexřa n Sina.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Ařeqqem n Harun d tarwa nnes  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Ksi Harun jmiɛ ak-d warraw nnes d warruḍ d zzect i wedhan d ufunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb d tnayen n icarriyyen d tsuǧet s weɣrum břa antun, \x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Uf. 28:1, 2; 30:25\x*  
\v 3 u řaɣa i marra tamesmunt ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.”   
\m
\v 4 Igga Musa am mammec d as iweṣṣa SIDI uca tmun tmesmunt ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 5 Inna Musa i tmesmunt: “Wa d min iweṣṣa SIDI ad ittwagg.” \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt Uf. 29:4\x*   
\m
\v 6 Musa issqarreb-dd Harun d warraw nnes uca issird i-ten s waman.  
\v 7 Issars xas tcamir, ibyes as s tḥezzamt, issyarḍ as aseřham. Igga xas apalṭu uca ibyes as s tḥezzamt izewwqen n upalṭu uca iqqen as zzayes \add apaltu\add*. \x ◘ \xo 8:7 \xt Uf. 28:4\x*  
\v 8 Issemten xas tajmect uca igga \add iẓra n\add* ‘Urim’ d ‘Tumim’ di tajmect. \x ◘ \xo 8:8 \xt Uf. 28:30\x*  
\v 9 Igga areẓẓet x uzeǧif nnes uca ɣar zzat x areẓẓet igga \add tařwiḥt s\add* nnuwwar n wureɣ n ttaj iqeddsen \add n weɛzař\add*, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 8:9 \xt Uf. 28:36; 29:6\x*   
\m
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* iksi Musa zzect i wedhan uca idhen Tazeddiɣt d marra min dayes iǧan uca issqeddes \add marra\add* aya.  
\v 11 Irucc zzayes x uɛalṭar sebɛa n twařawin uca idhen \add ɛawed\add* aɛalṭar d marra řeqcuɛ nnes uřa d tabanyut ak-d uḍar nnes maḥend ad ten issqeddes.  
\v 12 Iseyyeb zzect i wedhan x uzeǧif n Harun uca idhen i-t, ḥima ad t issqeddes. \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Izhd. 133:2\x*  
\v 13 Issqarreb-dd Musa arraw n Harun uca yarḍ asen tcamirat uca ibyes asen s tḥezzamin uca inneḍ asen ticuccay am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 8:13 \xt Uf. 29:9\x*   
\m
\v 14 Issqarreb-dd afunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb uca Harun d warraw nnes ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif n ufunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Uf. 29:1\x*  
\v 15 Iɣarṣ \add as\add* uca \add iksi\add* Musa idammen uca igga \add cwayt zzaysen\add* s uḍaḍ nnes x waccawen n uɛalṭar \add i iǧan\add* ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen nnes uca \add ammu i\add* issizdeg aɛalṭar. \add Xenni\add* iseyyeb idammen ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar. \add Ammu i\add* issqeddes i-t i weṣřaḥ xas. \f ◼ \fr 8:15 \ft \+fk accawen\ft  - niɣ ‘iqiccawen’.\f*  
\v 16 Iksi marra tadunt nni iǧan x wadan d min yuyřen ɣar tsa d tnayen n tiẓẓař d tadunt nsent uca Musa issbexxar \add aya\add* x uɛalṭar. \f ◼ \fr 8:16 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*  
\v 17 \add Maca\add* afunas ameẓyan d yiřem nnes d weysum nnes d amessař nnes, issarɣ \add i-ten\add* barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt Uf. 29:14; Lawi 4:11\x*   
\m
\v 18 Issqarreb-dd \add Musa\add* icarri n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca Harun d warraw nnes ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif n icarri.  
\v 19 Iɣarṣ \add i icarri\add* uca izeǧeɛ Musa idammen x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen nnes.  
\v 20 Ibḍa icarri d iceǧiqen nnes uca issbexxar Musa azeǧif d iceǧiqen d tadunt.  
\v 21 Issird adan d iḍaren s waman uca issbexxar Musa marra icarri x uɛalṭar, aqa d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ s yict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen, aqa d tawhibt n tmessi i SIDI, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 8:21 \xt Uf. 29:18\x*   
\m
\v 22 Issqarreb-dd \add xenni\add* icarri nneɣni, icarri i udeccen, uca Harun d warraw nnes ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif n icarri.  
\v 23 Uca iɣarṣ \add as\add* uca iksi Musa \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen uca igga i-ten x iɣes n umezzuɣ afusi n Harun u x uḍaḍ n yimez n ufus nnes afusi u x uḍaḍ n yimez n uḍar nnes afusi.  
\v 24 Issqarreb-dd \add ɛawed\add* arraw n Harun uca igga Musa \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen x iɣes n umezzuɣ nsen afusi u x uḍaḍ n yimez n ufus nsen afusi u x uḍaḍ n yimez n uḍar nsen afusi uca izeǧeɛ Musa idammen \add iqqimen\add* x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen \add nnes\add*.  
\v 25 Iksi tadunt d unewwar \add s tadunt\add* d marra tadunt tenni iǧan x wadan d min yuyřen ɣar tsa d tnayen n tiẓẓař ak-d tadunt nsent uřa d acekrud afusi. \x ◘ \xo 8:25 \xt Uf. 29:22\x*  
\v 26 Zi tsuǧet s weɣrum břa antun, tenni tuɣa zzat i wudem n SIDI, iksi ijj n řemsemmem břa antun d yict n temsemmemt \add isswejden\add* s zzect d ict n teřfeft uca issars i-ten x tadunt u x ucekrud afusi.  
\v 27 Igga marra man aya deg ifassen n Harun u deg ifassen n warraw nnes uca issenhezz aya am yict n tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 8:27 \xt Uf. 29:24\x*  
\v 28 \add Awarni as\add* iksi ten Musa \add ɛawed\add* zeg ifassen nsen uca issbexxar \add i-ten\add* x uɛalṭar, x tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ. Aqa d tiɣarṣa i udeccen s yict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen, aqa d tawhibt n tmessi i SIDI.  
\v 29 Iksi Musa idmaren uca issenhezz i-ten am yict n tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI. Man aya d tasɣart n ucarri i udeccen, tenni iǧan i Musa, am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 8:29 \xt Uf. 29:26; Lawi 7:33\x*   
\m
\v 30 Iksi Musa \add cwayt\add* n zzect i wedhan u n idammen i iǧan x uɛalṭar uca irucc man aya x Harun u x warruḍ nnes, x warraw nnes u x warruḍ n warraw nnes, \add inni\add* akides \add iǧan\add*. \add Ammu i\add* issqeddes Harun d warruḍ nnes d warraw nnes d warruḍ n warraw nnes akides. \x ◘ \xo 8:30 \xt Uf. 29:21\x*   
\m
\v 31 Inna Musa i Harun u i warraw nnes: “Senwem aysum nni ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca teccem t dinni s weɣrum nni iǧan di tsuǧet n tɣarṣa i udeccen, am mammec weṣṣiɣ necc, nniɣ: ‘Harun d warraw nnes ad t ccen.’ \x ◘ \xo 8:31 \xt Uf. 29:32; Lawi 24:9\x*  
\v 32 Min iceṭṭen n weysum d weɣrum, ad t tesscemḍen s tmessi.  
\v 33 Zeg wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar war zzayes dd-tᵉtteffɣem ca sebɛa n wussan, ař ass min di i ɣa kemmřen wussan n uřeqqem nwem, minzi netta ad kenniw yařeqqem sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 34 Am mammec igga \add marra\add* deg wass-a, \add ammu\add* i iweṣṣa SIDI, maḥend ad xawem igg aṣřaḥ.  
\v 35 Ad teqqimem ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, ass d ǧiřet, sebɛa n wussan uca ad tᵉṭṭfem \add a\add*ḥeṭṭu i SIDI, ḥima war tᵉttmettim ca, minzi ammu i \add t\add* ttweṣṣiɣ necc.”  
\v 36 Harun d warraw nnes ggin marra min d \add asen\add* iweṣṣa SIDI s tsexxart n Musa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Tiɣarṣa timezwura - aɛuǧi n SIDI  
\m
\v 1 Deg wass wiss tmenya imsar, aqa Musa iřaɣa i Harun d warraw nnes d imɣaren n Israil  
\v 2 uca inna i Harun: “Ksi ɣarek ijj n uɛejmi, ameẓyan n ufunas, \add am\add* tɣarṣt n ddenb, uřa d ijj n icarri \add am\add* tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, \add aqa ad iřin\add* cnan qaɛ, uca ejj i-ten ad dd-qarrben ɣar wudem n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 9:2 \ft \+fk aɛejmi\ft  - niɣ ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’. Uřa di ayat 3 d 8.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Uf. 29:1\x*  
\v 3 Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca ini: “Ksim ijj n umyan zeg iɣayḍen am tɣarṣt n ddenb u \add ksi\add* ijj n uɛejmi d ijj n yezmar, \add aqa ad iřin imuddaren\add* cnan qaɛ n ijj n useggʷas, i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ,  
\v 4 uca \add ksi ɛawed\add* ijj n ufunas d ijj n ucarri am tɣarṣa n řehna, maḥend ad \add ten\add* qeddmen \add d ddbiḥet\add* i SIDI, uřa d ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* ixeǧḍen s zzect, minzi ass-a ad awem dd-iban SIDI.”   
\m
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* awyen min xef iweṣṣa Musa ɣar zzat n Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca tamesmunt tqarreb-dd uca bedden nitni zzat i wudem n SIDI.   
\m
\v 6 Uca Musa inna: “D man aya min xef iweṣṣa SIDI maḥend ad \add t\add* teggem. Uca \add xenni\add* ad awem dd-iban uɛuǧi n SIDI.”   
\m
\v 7 Inna Musa i Harun: “Qarreb-dd ɣar uɛalṭar uca sewjed \bd taɣarṣt nnec n ddenb d tɣarṣt nnec n wecmaḍ\bd* uca egg aṣřaḥ x yixef nnec u x řgens. Sewjed \add ɛawed\add* tawhibt n řgens uca egg xasen aṣřaḥ am mammec \add t\add* iweṣṣa SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Lawi 16:6; Ɛbr. 7:27\x*  
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iqarreb-dd Harun ɣar uɛalṭar uca iɣarṣ i uɛejmi n tɣarṣt n ddenb \add i iǧan\add* i yixef nnes.  
\v 9 Arraw n Harun iwyen as-dd idammen uca netta issuf aḍaḍ nnes deg idammen uca igga i-ten x waccawen n uɛalṭar. \add Min iceṭṭen n\add* idammen iseyyeb i-ten ɣar uḍar n uɛalṭar.  
\v 10 Issbexxar tadunt d tiẓẓař d min yuyřen ɣar tsa n tɣarṣt n ddenb x uɛalṭar am mammec yumur SIDI i Musa. \f ◼ \fr 9:10 \ft \+fk tiẓẓař\ft  - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’. Uřa di ayet 19.\f*  
\v 11 Issecmeḍ aysum d yiřem s tmessi barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.   
\m
\v 12 Iɣarṣ taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca arraw n Harun qeddmen as idammen uca netta izeǧeɛ \add i-ten\add* x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen nnes.  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* qeddmen as taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ \add i ttwabḍan\add* d iceǧiqen, uřa d azeǧif, uca netta issbexxar i-tt x uɛalṭar.  
\v 14 Issird adan d iḍaren uca issbexxar \add i-ten\add* x tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i iǧan x uɛalṭar.   
\m
\v 15 \add Awarni as\add* issqarreb-dd \bd tawhibt n řgens\bd*. Netta iksi amyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb i řgens uca iɣarṣ as uca issewjed i-t d taɣarṣt n ddenb am mammec \add issewjed icarri\add* amezwaru. \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt Lawi 4:13\x*   
\m
\v 16 Issqarreb-dd taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca issewjed i-tt ɛlaḥsab lfariḍa.  
\v 17 Iqeddem tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* uca iksi zzayes ijj n wuru iccur uca issbexxar \add aya\add* x uɛalṭar, zzat i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ n ṣṣbeḥ. \x ◘ \xo 9:17 \xt Uf. 29:38; Lawi 2:1\x*   
\m
\v 18 Iɣarṣ ɛawed i ufunas u i yicarri n tɣarṣt n řehna di ṭṭweɛ n řgens, uca arraw n Harun qeddmen as idammen uca izeǧeɛ i-ten x uɛalṭar ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen nnes.  
\v 19 X tadunt n ufunas u n icarri: anewwar \add s tadunt nnes\add* d min idřin \add aḍan\add* d tiẓẓař d min yuyřen ɣar tsa,  
\v 20 aqa ssarsen tadunt \add nni\add* x idmaren uca netta issbexxar tadunt x uɛalṭar.  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* idmaren d ucekrud afusi issenhezz i-ten Harun \add amecnaw\add* ict n tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI, am mammec \add t\add* iweṣṣa Musa. \x ◘ \xo 9:21 \xt Lawi 7:32\x*   
\m
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed Harun ifassen nnes ɣar řgens uca ibarek i-ten uca ihwa awarni řami iqeddem taɣarṣt n ddenb d tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣt n řehna.  
\v 23 Uca yudef Musa ak-d Harun ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca nitni ffɣen \add zzayes ɛawed\add* uca barken řgens uca iban uɛuǧi n SIDI i marra řgens  
\v 24 uca teffeɣ-dd tmessi zi zzat i wudem n SIDI, tecca taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ x uɛalṭar uřa d tadunt. \add Umi\add* iẓra řgens \add man aya\add*, sřiweřwen uca wḍan \add ɣar temmurt\add* x uɣembub nsen. \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt 1 Ij. 18:38; 2 Im. 7:1\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\s1 Řmewt n Nadab d Abihu  
\m
\v 1 Nadab d Abihu, arraw n Harun, ksin kuř ijj řmejmar nnes uca ggin dayes řebxur uca \add ammu i\add* yiwyen nitni timessi teɣrib zzat i wudem n SIDI, min war d asen iweṣṣa Netta.  
\v 2 Teffeɣ-dd tmessi zi zzat i wudem n SIDI, tecc i-ten uca mmuten zzat i wudem n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt Řxř. 3:4; 26:61; 1 Im. 24:2\x*  
\v 3 Inna Musa i Harun: “D man aya x min xef issiweř SIDI \add umi\add* inna: ‘S yinni i ɣari dd ɣa iqarrben ad ttwaqeddseɣ uca zzat i wudem n marra řgens ad ttwassɛuǧeɣ.’” Uca isqar Harun. \x ◘ \xo 10:3 \xt Lawi 8:35\x*  
\v 4 Iřaɣa Musa i Micayil d i Ilṣafan, arraw n Ɛuzziyil, ɛemmis n Harun, uca inna asen: “Qarrbem-dd, tarbum aytmatwem zi qibač n Zzawect Iqeddsen, \add awyi ten barra\add* i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.”  
\v 5 Qarrben-dd nitni uca arbun ten di tcamirat nsen barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, am mammec \add t\add* inna Musa.  
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa i Harun u i Aliɛazar d Itamar, arraw nnes: “War ḍeǧqem i \add ucuwwaf x\add* izeǧifen nwem niɣ ttcarrgem arruḍ nwem \add i wecḍan\add*, ḥima war tᵉttmettim uca ad yiři uduqqez n weɣḍab x marra tamesmunt. \add Maca\add* aytmatwem, marra taddart n Israil, ad run x tmessi-ya, tenni issecmeḍ SIDI.  
\v 7 War dd-tteffɣem ca zi wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, ḥima war tᵉttmettim ca, minzi zzect n wedhan n SIDI aqa tt xawem.” Uca nitni ṭṭaɛen i wawař n Musa. \x ◘ \xo 10:7 \xt Lawi 21:12\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tawṣeyyet x binu d ccrab  
\m
\v 8 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Harun, inna:   
\m
\v 9 “War iɛeddeř ad tsessed binu niɣ ccrab ijehden xmi ɣa tadfem ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar, cek \add lla\add* uřa d iḥenjiren nnec \add nni\add* akidek \add lla\add*, ḥima war tᵉttmettim ca. Aqa-tt d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem,  
\v 10 ḥima ad af tzemmarem ad tfarzem jar min \add iǧan\add* iqeddsen d min war \add iǧin\add* iqeddsen u jar min iṣfan d min war iṣfin,  
\v 11 u ḥima ad tessřemdem i ayt n Israil marra tiweṣṣa nni ɣarsen issiweř SIDI s tsexxart n Musa.”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Aliɛazar d Itamar  
\m
\v 12 Uca issiweř Musa ak-d Harun u ak-d Aliɛazar d Itamar, arraw nnes iqqimen: “Ksim tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* nni iceṭṭen zi tewhibin n tmessi i SIDI uca ccem tt břa antun zzat i uɛalṭar, minzi aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ.  
\v 13 Ad tt teccem deg ijj n wemcam iqeddsen, minzi ta d taɣarṣt i cek u i iḥenjiren nnec zi tewhibin n tmessi n SIDI, minzi ammu i d ayi ittwaweṣṣa. \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt Lawi 2:3; 6:16\x*  
\v 14 Deg ijj n wemcan iṣfa ad teccem \add ɛawed\add* idmaren n wenhezzi d ucekrud n tewhibt i dd-ittwassgeɛɛden, cek d iḥenjiren nnec d tḥenjirin nnec akidek, minzi \add d man aya\add* d tasɣart nnec d tasɣart n tarwa nnec zi tɣarṣa n řehna n ayt n Israil.  
\v 15 Ad awyen acekrud n tewhibt i dd-ittwassgeɛɛden uřa d idmaren n wenhezzi ak-d tewhibin n tmessi n tadunt, maḥend ad ten ssenhezzen zzat i wudem n SIDI am tewhibt n wenhezzi. Aqa d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i cek u i iḥenjiren nnec akidek, am mammec \add t\add* iweṣṣa SIDI.”   
\m
\v 16 Uca Musa yarzu s cḍaret x umyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb, \add maca\add* xzar, icemḍ. \add Xenni\add* iffugem x Aliɛazar d Itamar, arraw iqqimen n Harun, inna:  
\v 17 “Mayemmi war teccim taɣarṣt n ddenb deg wemcan iqeddsen? Minzi aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ uca netta iwca awem tt-i-dd ḥima kenniw ad tarbum řmuɛṣiyyet n tmesmunt, maḥend ad xasen teggem aṣřaḥ zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 18 Xzarem, ḥdam war ssidfen walu zeg idammen daxeř i Zzawect Iqeddsen. Tuɣa ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad tt teccem di Zzawect Iqeddsen am mammec d awem weṣṣiɣ necc.” \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt Lawi 4:5; 6:19; 16:27\x*  
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Harun ak-d Musa: “Xzar, ass-a aqa qeddmen taɣarṣt n ddenb d tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ zzat i wudem n SIDI. \add Mařa\add* necc, awarni řami xafi kkent tmesřayin-a, aqa cciɣ zi tɣarṣt n ddenb ass-a, ma \add xenni\add* man aya icna di tiṭṭawin n SIDI?”  
\v 20 \add Umi\add* isřa Musa aya, iban as-dd \add man aya\add* d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnes.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Imuddaren izedgen d inni ixemjen  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa d Harun, inna asen:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca inim: ‘Ina aqa aten d \bd řmař, inni umi iɛeddeř ad teccem\bd* zi jar marra řmař nni din x temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt Aɛwd. 14:4; Řex. 10:14\x*  
\v 3 Iɛeddeř ad teccem zi marra řmař i ɣar teǧa \bd tecḍect immsebḍan\bd*, aqa farqa n tecḍect imssebḍan \add qaɛ\add*, \bd u\bd* \add sennej i man aya\add* \bd ttarran ifeẓ\bd*.   
\m
\v 4 Maca zeg inni ittarran ifeẓ d yinni ɣar teǧa tecḍect immsebḍan, \bd war ttᵉttem ina\bd*: \bd ařɣem\bd*, minzi itteffeẓ, \add maca\add* war ɣares bu tecḍect immsebḍan, \add s uyenni\add* aqa ixmej i kenniw,  
\v 5 \bd akawka n teṣḍart\bd*, minzi ittarra ifeẓ, \add maca\add* tacḍect war temmsebḍi, u \add s uyenni\add* aqa ixmej i kenniw, \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt Aɛwd. 14:7\x*  
\v 6 amenni \bd ayarziz\bd*, minzi ittarra ifeẓ, maca war ɣares tacḍect immsebḍan, \add s uyenni\add* aqa ixmej i kenniw, \x ◘ \xo 11:6 \xt Aɛwd. 14:7\x*  
\v 7 ɛaweḍ \bd iřef\bd*, minzi ɣares tacḍect immsebḍan uca aqa farqa n tecḍect immsebḍan \add qaɛ\add*, maca war ittarri ifeẓ, \add s uyenni\add* aqa ixmej i kenniw.  
\v 8 Zeg weysum nsen war zzayes ttᵉttem niɣ ad tḥadam řxecbat nsen, aqa xemjen i kenniw.’”   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Ina iɛeddeř ad ten teccem zi jar marra \add imuddaren\add* nni \add iddaren\add* deg waman: \bd marra wi ɣar iǧa wafriwen d teqcurt\bd* deg waman u di řebḥur u di tɣezratin, ina iɛeddeř ad ten teccem,  
\v 10 \add maca\add* marra wi war ɣar yeǧi ifriwen niɣ taqcurt di řebḥur u di tɣezratin, zi jar marra i zi sseffyen aman uřa zi jar marra min iddaren deg waman, ad awem yiři d nnɛi.  
\v 11 \add Wah\add* ad awem yiři d nnɛi. War iɛeddeř ad teccem zeg weysum nsen u řxecbat nsen ad ɣarwem iřint d nnɛi.  
\v 12 Marra min iǧan deg waman břa ifriwen d teqcurt, ad ɣarwem yiři d nnɛi.”   
\b  
\m
\v 13 “\bd Zeg ijḍaḍ\bd* ad ɣarwem iřin ina d nnɛi, \bd war zzaysen ttᵉttem ca\bd*, aqa aten d nnɛi: agider, isɣi, agider n řebḥar, \x ◘ \xo 11:13 \xt Aɛwd. 14:12\x*  
\v 14 \add aceffar\add* iṭṭawen s tazřa, amessɣuy \add amuqḍiɛ n tiṭṭawin\add* ak-d marra markat nnes, \x ◘ \xo 11:14 \xt Aɛwd. 14:13\x*  
\v 15 marra markat n ubaɣeř, \x ◘ \xo 11:15 \xt Aɛwd. 14:14\x*  
\v 16 yeǧis n tɣuyyit, aɛennaf, ajḍiḍ n řebḥar, řbaz ak-d markat nnes, \x ◘ \xo 11:16 \xt Aɛwd. 14:15\x*  
\v 17 \add aḥemmař\add* n řkas, bu-tcararrut, bu-usuḍi \add n řmewt\add*,  
\v 18 bu-yuntaḥ, bu-uɛuqqi, bu-uḥawar, \x ◘ \xo 11:18 \xt Aɛwd. 14:16, 17\x*  
\v 19 abellarj, bu-usuḍi iɛeffnen ak-d marra markat nnes, dundun d řweḍwaḍ.” \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Aɛwd. 14:18\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 “\bd Marra wi ɣar iǧa afriwen i ittbuɛen u igguren x arebɛa n iḍaren, ad ɣarwem yiři d nnɛi.\bd*  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* zi marra inni ittbuɛen am ɣarsen afriwen \add u\add* gguren x arebɛa n iḍaren, \bd iɛeddeř i kenniw ad teccem inni ɣar iǧa iḍaren \+bdit i wengaz\+bdit* sennej i iḍaren nsen \+bdit i tecři\+bdit*\bd*, ḥima ad zzaysen negzen x temmurt.  
\v 22 Ina tzemmarem ad zzaysen teccem: tamurɣi n weyřaf ak-d markat nnes, tamuɣri n teṣḍart ak-d markat nnes, tamuɣri ineggzen ak-d markat nnes d tamuɣri iřeḥḥfen ak-d markat nnes.  
\v 23 Marra wi ɣar iǧa afriwen i ittbuɛen u ɣares arebɛa n iḍaren, ad ɣarwem yiři d nnɛi.”   
\b  
\m
\v 24 “S \add imuddaren-a\add* i ɣa tᵉttwaxemjem. Marra wi ɣa iḥadan řxecbat nsen, ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 25 Manwen yiwyen ca zi řxecbat nsen, ad issird arruḍ nnes uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 26 Marra řebhayem, inni ɣar teǧa tecḍect immsebḍan i zi farqa \add n tecḍect\add* war tfarq qaɛ, uřa war ttarran ifeẓ, ad ɣarwem iřin xemjen. Marra wi ten i ɣa iḥadan, ad yiři ixmej.  
\v 27 Kuř \add amuddar\add* jar imuddaren i igguren x arebɛa n třeqqa \add n iḍaren\add* nsen, ad ɣarwem yiři ixmej. Marra wi ɣa iḥadan řxecbat nsen, ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 28 Wi yiwyen ca n řxecbat nsen, ad issird arruḍ nnes uca ad yiři ixmej ař tmeddit. Ad awem iřin xemjen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 29 “\bd Zi jar \+bdit imuddaren\+bdit* ittbuɛen, inni ittbuɛen x temmurt, d ina ad xawem iřin xemjen\bd* i kenniw: ajarbuɛ, aɣerda, icfar ak-d markat nnes,  
\v 30 iqqli, taknakart, azermummuy, aḥdiḍ d tata.\f ◼ \fr 11:30 \ft \+fk taknakart\ft  - niɣ ‘tiqqlit’.\f*  
\v 31 Ina ad ɣarwem iřin xemjen zi jar marra \add imuddaren\add* nni ittbuɛen \add x temmurt\add*. Marra wi ten i ɣa iḥadan awarni řmewt nsen, ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 32 Marra min xef iwḍa ca zi řxecbat nsen ad yiři ixmej, niɣ ict n řqecɛet n tefřawt, niɣ arruḍ, niɣ tiřmect, niɣ taxancet, niɣ min ma řqecɛet i xef iwḍa ca zzaysent, ittxeṣṣa ad ittwassars deg waman, ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit u \add awarni aya\add* ad yiři izdig. \x ◘ \xo 11:32 \xt Lawi 15:12\x*  
\v 33 Marra řqecɛet n třaxt, tenni umi di iwḍa \add cwayt zzayes\add*, aqa marra min dayes iǧan ad yiři ixmej uca ittxeṣṣa i kenniw ad tarẓem ṭṭebṣi.  
\v 34 Marra macca nni ttnuman \add iwdan\add* ad ccen, tenni x wḍan waman nni, ad tiři texmej, u marra tissit nni ttnuman \add iwdan\add* ad swen, mammec ma tegga řqecɛet i di teǧa \add macca niɣ tissit\add*, ad tiři texmej.  
\v 35 Marra min xef iwḍa ca n řxecbat nsen, ad yiři ixmej. Afarnu d tzewḍa ad ttwarẓen, aqa xemjen uca ad ɣarwem iřin xemjen.  
\v 36 Maca řɛunṣar niɣ d anu mani ɣar ssizzřen aman, ad yiři izdeg. \add Maca\add* wi ɣa iḥadan řxecbat nsen, ad yiři ixmej.   
\m
\v 37 Uca mařa iwḍa \add ca\add* zi řxecbat nsen x ca n zzariɛet i uzarɛ, tenni ittxeṣṣa ɛad ad zarɛen, \add xenni\add* ad tiři tizdeg.  
\v 38 \add Maca\add* mařa seyyben aman x zzariɛet uca iwḍa xas \add ca\add* zi řxecbat nsen, \add xenni\add* ad ɣarwem tiři \add zzariɛet nni\add* texmej.   
\m
\v 39 Uca mařa immut \add ijj\add* zi jar řmař nni teccim, \add xenni\add* wi ɣa iḥaḍan řxecbet nnes, ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 40 Wenni iccen zi řxecbet nnes, ad issird arruḍ nnes uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit. Wenni yarbun ca zi řxecbet nnes, ad issird arruḍ nnes uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.   
\m
\v 41 Kuř \add amuddar\add* ittbuɛen x temmurt, aqa-t d nnɛi. War iɛeddeř ad ittwacc.  
\v 42 Zi jar marra \add imuddaren\add* ittbuɛen, inni ittbuɛen x \add wudem n\add* temmurt, war ttᵉttem ca marra min igguren x uɛeddis niɣ marra min igguren x arebɛa \add n iḍaren\add* ař marra min igguren x waṭṭas n iḍaren, minzi aqa aten d nnɛi.  
\v 43 War tteggem nnɛi i řeɛmur nwem s marra imuddaren ittbuɛen nni \add din\add* ittbuɛen \add x wudem n temmurt\add*, war zzayes ssxemmajem ixef nwem ařami ad zzaysen txemjem.  
\v 44 Minzi Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem. Kenniw ad tessqedsem ixef nwem uca ad tiřim d imqeddasen, minzi Necc aqa d amqeddas. War ssxemmajem řeɛmur nwem s marra immudaren ittbuɛen, inni ittbuɛen x \add wudem n\add* temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 11:44 \xt Lawi 19:2; 20:7; 1 Bṭ. 1:16\x*  
\v 45 Minzi Necc D SIDI, wenni kenniw dd-issgeɛɛden zi temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nwem. Iřim d imqeddasen, maɣar aqa Necc d amqeddas.”   
\m
\v 46 Wa d azerf x řmař, x ijḍaḍ u x marra imuddaren nni zzaysen issefyen waman uca x marra imuddaren nni ittbuɛen x temmurt,  
\v 47 ḥima ad ittwagg řfarq jar min ixemjen d min izdigen u jar imuddaren inni iɛeddřen i macca d imuddaren inni war iɛeddřen i macca.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Tiweṣṣa n usizdeg ɣar wexřaq  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini: ‘Mařa teksi ict n temɣart ddeyset uca turuw-dd aḥenjir, ad tiři texmej sebɛa n wussan. Ad tiři texmej am \add deg\add* wussan n weɛzař xmi xas idammen.  
\v 3 Deg wass wiss tmenya ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaxten aysum n řeɛdařyet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 12:3 \xt Amz. 17:12; Lk. 1:59; 2:21; Yḥ. 7:22\x*  
\v 4 Awarni man aya ad teqqim třata u-třatin n wussan deg idammen n usizdeg nnes. War tᵉttḥidi walu zi min iǧan iqeddes u war tᵉttraḥ ɣar Zzawect Iqeddsen ař ɣa kemmřen wussan n usizdeg nnes.  
\v 5 Mařa turuw d taḥenjirt, ad tiři texmej tnayen n ssimanat, am deg wussan n weɛzař nnes. \add Awarni man aya\add* ad teqqim setta u-settin n wussan deg idammen n usizdeg nnes. \f ◼ \fr 12:5 \ft \+fk ssimanat\ft  - niɣ ‘imalasen’.\f*  
\v 6 Xmi ɣa kemmřen wussan n usizdeg n mmis niɣ n yeǧis, \add xenni\add* ad tawi ijj n izmar n ijj n useggʷas am tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ ijj n wedbir d ameẓyan niɣ ict n tejlilliḥt am tɣarṣt n ddenb ɣar ukehhan ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 7 D netta ad yawi man aya zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ad xas igg aṣřaḥ. \add Xenni\add* ad tiři tizdeg zi řɛunṣar n idammen nnes. Wa d azerf i tenni i ɣa yarwen ijj n mmis niɣ ict n yeǧis. \f ◼ \fr 12:7 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  
\v 8 Mařa war tiwiḍ ad tawi ijj zeg wuǧi, \add xenni\add* ad tᵉṭṭef tnayen n tejlilliḥin niɣ tnayen n idbiren imeẓyanen, ijj i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ u ijj i tɣarṣt n ddenb, uca akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ. \add Xenni\add* ad tiři tizdeg.’” \f ◼ \fr 12:8 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Tiweṣṣa zi jjihet n řehřac n řbarṣ  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa d Harun, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Mařa ijj n bnadem ɣares di teřmect n arrimet nnes \bd aɛebbuz niɣ ict n tḥebbuct niɣ ijj n wengaz iccemřeř\bd*, uca wanita izemmar ad idweř d uḍun n řbarṣ di teřmect n arrimet nnes, ad t awyen ɣar Harun, akehhan, niɣ ɣar yijjen zeg warraw nnes, ɣar ikehhanen.  
\v 3 Akehhan ad ixzar ɣar wuḍun di teřmect n arrimet nnes uca mařa iẓra aqa iẓuṭṭan deg \add wemcan n\add* wuḍun dewřen d icemřařen uca iban wuḍun ɛad yuǧeɣ x teřmect n arrimet nnes, aqa \add xenni\add* d uḍun n řbarṣ. Xmi t ɣa iẓar ukehhan, ad \add t\add* ibarreḥ d amexmuj.  
\v 4 Maca mařa angaz iccemřeř di teřmect n arrimet nnes d acemřař u war yuǧiɣ x teřmect u iẓeṭṭan war dwiřen d icemřařen, \add xenni\add* ad ibelleɛ ukehhan x wenni di iǧa uḍun \add nni\add* sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 5 \add Mařa\add* iẓra i-t ukehhan deg wass wiss sebɛa uca iẓra aqa uḍun amenni iqqim, war imɣir wuḍun di teřmect, \add xenni\add* ad t ibelleɛ ukehhan \add ɛawed\add* sebɛa n wussan nneɣni.  
\v 6 Deg wass wiss sebɛa ad t iẓar ukehhan ɛawed uca \add mařa\add* iban aqa uḍun yarsa uca war imɣir \add ɛad ktar\add* x teřmect, \add xenni\add* akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amezdag. Tuɣa-tt d ict n tfuriy. Ad issird arruḍ nnes uca ad yiři izdig.  
\v 7 \add Maca\add* mařa imɣar wuḍun aṭṭas x teřmect awarni řami t iẓra ukehhan di ṭṭweɛ n usizdeg nnes, ittxeṣṣa ad isscen \add ixef nnes\add* i ukehhan twařa nneɣni.  
\v 8 \add Mařa\add* iẓra ukehhan, aqa řehřac imɣar x teřmect, ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj. Aqa-t d řehřac n řbarṣ \add i iǧa\add*.   
\m
\v 9 Xmi uḍun n řbarṣ aqa-t deg ijj n bnadem, ad t awyen ɣar ukehhan.  
\v 10 \add Mařa\add* iẓra ukehhan, aqa iban \bd ijj n uɛebbuz d acemřař\bd* di teřmect, u iẓeṭṭan dewřen d icemřařen u iban-dd weysum iddar deg uɛebbuz,  
\v 11 aqa-t d řbars aqdim di teřmect n arrimet nnes uca akehhan ad zzayes ibarreḥ d amexmuj. War xas ittbelliɛ ca, minzi netta aqa ixmej.  
\v 12 Mařa yuyur řbarṣ x tiřmect marra uca idřa řbarṣ marra tiřmect n wenni ɣar iǧa uḍun zeg uzeǧif nnes ař iḍaren nnes, ař mani izemmar ad iẓar ukehhan s tiṭṭawin nnes,  
\v 13 uca iẓra \add i-t\add* ukehhan, iẓra řbars idřa marra arrimet nnes, \add xenni\add* netta ad ibarreḥ d amezdag i wenni di iǧa wuḍun. \add Tiřmect\add* aqa-tt d tacemřač qaɛ. Netta aqa izdig.   
\m
\v 14 \add Maca\add* deg wass mani dayes i ɣa dd-iban weysum iddar, ad yiři ixmej.  
\v 15 \add Mařa\add* iẓra ukehhan aysum \add nni\add* iddar, ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj. Aysum iddaren ixmej, aqa-t d řehřac n řbarṣ.  
\v 16 \add Maca\add* mařa ibeddeř weysum iddaren u idweř d acemřař, ittxeṣṣa as ad dd-yas ɣar ukehhan.  
\v 17 \add Mařa\add* iẓra i-t ukehhan uca aqa \add amcan n\add* uḍun idweř d acemřař, ad ibarreḥ ukehhan wenni di iǧa řehřac d amezdag. Netta aqa izdig.   
\m
\v 18 \add Mařa\add* din x teřmect n weysum ict n tḥebbuct u tᵉttwassgenfa tanita,  
\v 19 \add maca\add* \bd deg wemcan n tḥebbuct idweř d ijj n uɛebbuz imřeř niɣ d ijj n wengaz iccemřeř, acemřař iruḥ ɣar tezweɣ\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad iẓar ukehhan man aya.  
\v 20 \add Xmi\add* ɣares i ɣa ixzar ukehhan uca iẓra aqa-t sadu teřmect uca iẓeṭṭan nnes d icemřařen, \add xenni\add* akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj, aqa-t d uḍun n řbarṣ wenni yuyuren s tḥebbuct.  
\v 21 \add Maca\add* mařa iẓra i-t ukehhan uca war \add dayes\add* yufi uřa d ijj n uẓeṭṭu d acemřař uca war idwiř yuǧeɣ x teřmect, \add maca\add* idweř yarsa, \add xenni\add* ad xas ibelleɛ ukehhan sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 22 Mařa tuyur x teřmect marra, \add xenni\add* akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj. Aqa-t d uḍun \add n řbarṣ\add*.  
\v 23 \add Maca\add* mařa angaz iccemřeř n teřmect iqqim deg wemcan nnes, war imɣir ca, aqa-t d ccamet n tḥebbuct uca akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amezdag.   
\m
\v 24 Niɣ mařa idweř di teřmect n arrimet ijj n uyezzim n wecmaḍ uca aysum iddaren n \bd uyezzim n wecmaḍ idweř d ijj n wengaz iccemřeř, acemřař iruḥ ɣar tezweɣ niɣ d acemřař\bd*,  
\v 25 uca iẓra ukehhan man aya, uca xzar, iẓeṭṭan i iǧan deg wengaz iccemřeř aqa dewřen d icemřařen, uca iban \add aqa amcan n wengaz\add* yuǧeɣ di teřmect, aqa-t d řbarṣ nni dd-iffɣen zeg uyezzim n wecmaḍ. Akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj. Aqa-t d uḍun n řbarṣ.  
\v 26 \add Maca\add* mařa akehhan iẓra man aya uca war ittwiři iẓeṭṭan icemřařen deg wengaz iccemřeř uca \add iẓra angaz\add* war yuǧiɣ x teřmect uca yarsa, \add xenni\add* ad xas ibelleɛ ukehhan sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 27 Deg wass wiss sebɛa ad t iẓar ukehhan uca mařa imɣar \add wengaz\add* ktar x teřmect, akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj. Aqa-t d uḍun n řbarṣ.  
\v 28 \add Maca\add* mařa angaz iccemřeř iqqim deg wemcan nnes, war imɣir x teřmect uca yarsa, aqa-t d aɛebbuz n wecmaḍ. Akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amezdag, minzi aqa-tt d ccamet n wecmaḍ.   
\m
\v 29 Mařa ijj n weryaz niɣ ict n temɣart dayes \bd uḍun deg uzeǧif niɣ di tmart\bd*,  
\v 30 uca ixzar ukehhan ɣar uḍun, u xzar, aqa ittban yuǧeɣ di teřmect uca dayes iẓeṭṭan iwarɣen d izdaden, \add xenni\add* akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj. Aqa-tt d tfuri \add n yiřem\add*, aqa-t d řbarṣ n uzeǧif niɣ n tmart.  
\v 31 \add Maca\add* mařa iẓra ukehhan uḍun n tfuri \add n yiřem\add*, iẓra aqa war yuǧiɣ di teřmect uca war dayes iẓeṭṭan ibarcanen, \add xenni\add* ad xas ibelleɛ ukehhan x wenni di iǧa wuḍun n tfuri \add n yiřem\add* i yijj n řmijař n sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 32 Ad iẓar ukehhan uḍun deg wass wiss sebɛa uca mařa iẓra, aqa tfuri \add n yiřem\add* war temɣir, war dayes yufi iẓeṭṭan iwarɣen uca tfuri \add n yiřem\add* war tuǧiɣ x teřmect,  
\v 33 \add xenni\add* netta ad iḥeff i yixef nnes, \add maca\add* \add amcan n\add* tfuri \add n yiřem\add* war t ittḥeffi ca uca akehhan ad ibelleɛ x wenni di iǧa tfuri \add n yiřem\add* ɛad ict n twařa nneɣni i yijj n řmijař n sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 34 Deg wass wiss sebɛa ad iẓar ukehhan \add amcan n\add* tfuri \add n yiřem\add*. \add Mařa\add* iẓra aqa tfuri \add n yiřem\add* war temɣir ca, war tuǧiɣ x teřmect, \add xenni\add* akehhan ad t ibarreh d amezdag. Ad issird arruḍ nnes uca ad yiři izdig.  
\v 35 Maca mařa tfuri \add n yiřem\add* temɣar aṭṭas x teřmect awarni i usizdeg nnes,  
\v 36 uca iẓra i-t ukehhan uca iẓra tfuri \add n yiřem\add* temɣar x teřmect, \add xenni\add* war yarezzu ukehhan x iẓeṭṭan iwarɣen ɛad, netta aqa ixmej.  
\v 37 \add Maca\add* mařa tfuri \add n yiřem\add* aqa tban-dd tbedd di tiṭṭawin nnes, uca ffɣen-dd zzayes iẓeṭṭan ibarcanen, \add xenni\add* aqa tᵉggenfa tfuri \add n yiřem\add* uca netta aqa izdeg. Akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amezdag.   
\m
\v 38 Mařa banen-dd \bd imucan ccemřeřen\bd*, iccemřeřen d icemřařen, di teřmect n ijj n weryaz niɣ n ict n temɣart,  
\v 39 uca iẓra ukehhan man aya uca iẓra aqa di teřmect n arrimet banen-dd imucan arsan, icemřařen, \add xenni\add* aqa-tt d ict n tfuri n teřmect, netta aqa izdeg.   
\m
\v 40 \add Mařa\add* iwḍa ucuwwaf n uzeǧif n ijj n weryaz, aqa d \bd aqeccar\bd*, \add xenni\add* netta aqa izdig.  
\v 41 Mařa tanyart n ca n yijj ad tedweř tařeqqaɣt, aqa tanyart nnes tqeccar \add waha\add*, netta aqa izdig.  
\v 42 \add Maca\add* mařa \add din\add* ijj n uḍun imřeř iruḥ ɣar tezweɣ x uzeǧif aqeccar niɣ x tenyart taqeccart, aqa-t d řbarṣ nni dd-iffɣen x uzeǧif nnes aqeccar niɣ x tenyart nnes taqeccart.  
\v 43 \add Mařa\add* iẓra i-t ukehhan uca iẓra aqa aɛebbuz n wuḍun imřeř, iruḥ ɣar tezweɣ x uzeǧif nnes aqeccar niɣ x tenyart nnes taqeccart, iban-dd am řbarṣ n teřmect n arrimet,  
\v 44 \add xenni\add* aqa aryaz d bu-řbarṣ i iǧa, netta aqa ixmej. Akehhan ad t ibarreḥ d amexmuj, uḍun aqa-t x uzeǧif nnes.”   
\b  
\m
\v 45 “Ittxeṣṣa ad ittwacarreg warruḍ n bu-řbarṣ i di iǧa wuḍun uca ad iḍřeq i \add ucuwwaf x\add* uzeǧif nnes, ad iřeḥḥef acřaɣem ɣar uyencic, ad iřaɣa: ‘Amexmuj! Amexmuj!’ \x ◘ \xo 13:45 \xt Igjd. 4:15\x*  
\v 46 Marra ussan i dayes i ɣa yiři wuḍun, ad yiři ixmej. Netta d amexmuj. Netta ad izdeɣ weḥḥdes uca tzeddiɣt nnes ad tiři barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.”   
\b  
\m
\v 47 “\add Mařa\add* uḍun n \bd řbarṣ deg ijj n warruḍ\bd*, deg ijj n warruḍ n taḍuft niɣ deg ijj n warruḍ n řeqṭen,  
\v 48 niɣ \bd deg wecḍaḍ ixeyyḍen niɣ deg ufiřu immuden\bd*, \add niɣ\add* n řeqṭen niɣ n taḍuft, niɣ \bd ɣar yiřem, niɣ ɣar mammec ma řqecɛet n yiřem\bd*,  
\v 49 u \add ticti\add* ittwawten deg warruḍ niɣ deg yiřem, niɣ ɣar wecḍaḍ ixeyyḍen niɣ ɣar ufiřu immuden, niɣ di mammec ma n řqecɛet \add nni tteggen\add* s yiřem, tezzizu niɣ tezweɣ, aqa-t d uḍun n řbarṣ. Ad ittwasscen aya i ukehhan.  
\v 50 Akehhan ad ixzar \add ɣar wemcan n\add* uḍun uca min iḍnen ad t ibelleɛ sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 51 Deg wass wiss sebɛa ad ixzar ɣar wuḍun. Mařa imɣar uḍun deg warruḍ, niɣ ɣar wecḍaḍ ixeyyḍen niɣ ɣar ufiřu immuden, niɣ deg yiřem n mammec ma řqecɛet nni tteggen s yiřem, aqa uḍun d řbars iqesḥen i yeǧa, aqa ixmej.  
\v 52 Ad issecmeḍ arruḍ niɣ afiřu d azirar niɣ afiřu immuden, niɣ n taḍuft niɣ n řeqṭen \add i iǧa\add*, niɣ mammec ma řqecɛet \add nni tteggen\add* s yiřem i dayes tuɣa uḍun, minzi aqa-t d řbarṣ iqesḥen. Ittxeṣṣa ad ittwassecmeḍ s tmessi.  
\v 53 \add Maca\add* mařa iẓra ukehhan man aya uca aqa uḍun war imɣir ca deg warruḍ, niɣ deg wecḍaḍ ixeyyḍen niɣ deg ufiřu immuden, niɣ di mammec ma řqecɛet \add nni tteggen\add* s yiřem,  
\v 54 \add xenni\add* ad yumur ukehhan maḥend ad ssirden min di yeǧa wuḍun, uca \add awarni i man aya\add* ad xas ibelleɛ twařa nneɣni řqedd n sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 55 \add Mařa\add* iẓra ukehhan uḍun awarni i usird, uca iẓra uḍun war ibeddiř ca uca uḍun war imɣir, aqa \add arruḍ nni\add* ixmej. Ittxeṣṣa ad t tessecmeḍed s tmessi. Aqa \add uḍun\add* idweř yuǧeɣ ittᵉtt ɣar ḍeffar niɣ ɣar zzat.  
\v 56 \add Maca\add* mařa iẓra ukehhan man aya uca iẓra belli uḍun yarsa awarni i usird, \add xenni\add* ad t iqess zeg warruḍ, niɣ zeg yiřem, niɣ zeg wecḍaḍ ixeyyḍen niɣ zeg ufiřu immuden.  
\v 57 \add Maca\add* mařa iban \add wuḍun\add* twařa nneɣni deg warruḍ, niɣ ɣar wecḍaḍ ixeyyḍen niɣ ɣar ufiřu immuden, niɣ di mammec ma řqecɛet \add nni tteggen\add* s yiřem, \add aqa\add* idduqqez \add řbarṣ\add*. Ittxeṣṣa ad tessecmeḍ s tmessi min dayes i iǧan uḍun.  
\v 58 Arruḍ, niɣ afiřu d azirar niɣ afiřu immuden niɣ mammec ma řqecɛet \add nni tteggen\add* s yiřem, wenni tessirded uca iruḥ xas wuḍun, ad t tessirded twařa nneɣni uca \add xenni\add* ad yiři izdig.”  
\v 59 Wa d azerf n wuḍun n řbarṣ n warruḍ n taḍuft niɣ n řeqṭen, niɣ n wecḍaḍ ixeyyḍen niɣ n ufiřu immuden, niɣ n mammec ma řqecɛet \add nni tteggen\add* s yiřem, maḥend xenni ad barrḥen s tezdeg \add nnes\add* niɣ s řexmej \add nnes\add*.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Asizdeg n řehřac n řbarṣ  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Wa d azerf n bu-řbarṣ i wass n usizdeg nnes. Ittxeṣṣa ad t nedhen ɣar ukehhan, \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Mt. 8:4; Mk. 1:44; Lk. 5:14; 17:14\x*  
\v 3 uca ad iffeɣ ukehhan ɣar barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar. Xmi ɣares i ɣa ixzar ukehhan uca iẓra aqa iggenfa wuḍun n řbarṣ n bu-řbarṣ,  
\v 4 ad yumur ukehhan, maḥend ad ksin i wenni i ɣa ittwassizedgen tnayen n ijḍaḍ iddaren izdigen, uřa d akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt, d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen, d tɛelǧet. \f ◼ \fr 14:4 \ft \+fk tɛelǧet\ft  - niɣ ‘hisup’. Uřa di ayat 6, 49, 51 d 52.\f*  
\v 5 Ad yumur ukehhan maḥend ad ɣarṣen i yijj n wejḍiḍ deg ict n řqecɛet n třaxt, sennej i waman ittazzřen.  
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* ad iksi ajḍiḍ iddaren d ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d tɛelǧet uca ad ten issuf ak-d wejḍiḍ iddaren deg idammen n wejḍiḍ i ittwaɣarṣen sennej i waman ittazzřen.  
\v 7 Ad irucc sebɛa n twařawin x wenni ittwassizedgen zi řbarṣ. \add Xenni\add* ad t ibarreḥ d amezdag uca ad yarxu i wejḍiḍ iddaren maḥend ad iḍew sennej i wudem n yeyyar.  
\v 8 Uca wenni ittwassizedgen ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes uca ad iḥeff marra acuwwaf nnes, ad issird ixef nnes s waman. \add Xenni\add* ad yiři izdeg. Awarni as ad yadef ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar uca ad izdeɣ barra i uqiḍun nnes ɛad sebɛa n wussan.   
\m
\v 9 Deg wass wiss sebɛa ad iḥeff marra acuwwaf n uzeǧif nnes d tmart nnes d temmiwin n tiṭṭawin nnes, \add wah,\add* ad iḥeff marra acuwwaf nnes, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes uca ad issird arrimet nnes s waman, \add xenni\add* ad yiři izdeg.   
\m
\v 10 Deg wass wiss tmenya ad iksi tnayen n izmaren kemmřen d icten texsi icnan qaɛ n ijjen useggʷas ak-d třata zi ɛecra n ijjen ifa n waren azdad am tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* ixeǧḍen s zzect, u \add ɛawed\add* ijjen ulux n zzect.  
\v 11 Akehhan, wenni t issizedgen, ad yarr aryaz nni ittxeṣṣa ad ittwassizdeg, ak-d marra aya zzat i wudem n SIDI ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 12 Ad iksi ukehhan izmar nni uca ad t-i-dd-issqarreb am tɣarṣt n umarwas ak-d ulux n zzect, uca ad t issenhezz am tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* ad iɣarṣ i yezmar nni deg wemcan mani ɣarrṣen taɣarṣt n ddenb d tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, deg wemcan amqeddas. Minzi taɣarṣt n umarwas, am tɣarṣt n ddenb, i ukehhan i teǧa, aqa-tt d tamqeddast qaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 14:13 \xt Lawi 7:7\x*  
\v 14 Ad iksi ukehhan \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n tɣarṣt n umarwas uca akehhan ad ten igg x iɣes n umezzuɣ afusi n wenni i ɣa ittwassizedgen uřa x yimez n ufus nnes afusi u x yimez n uḍar nnes afusi.  
\v 15 Amenni i ɣa iksi ukehhan \add ca\add* zeg ulux n zzect uca ad tt inɣeř x třeqqa n ufus nnes azeřmaḍ.  
\v 16 Ad issuf ukehhan aḍaḍ nnes afusi s zzect nni ɣares deg ufus nnes azeřmaḍ uca \add ammu i\add* ɣa irucc s uḍaḍ nnes \add cwayt\add* zi zzect sebɛa n twařawin zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 17 Uca min iqqimen zi zzect nni ɣares deg ufus nnes, ad tt igg ukehhan x iɣes n umezzuɣ afusi n wenni i ɣa ittwassizedgen, uřa x yimez n ufus nnes afusi u x yimez n uḍar nnes afusi, tiwa n idammen n tɣarṣt n umarwas \add i xasen igga qbeř\add*.  
\v 18 Min iqqimen n zzect nni iǧan ɣar ukehhan di třeqqa n ufus nnes, ad t inɣeř x uzeǧif n wenni i ɣa ittwassizedgen uca \add ammu i\add* t ɣa isseṣřeḥ ukehhan zzat i wudem n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 14:18 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  
\v 19 Ad issewjed ukehhan \add xenni\add* taɣarṣt n ddenb uca ad isseṣřeḥ wenni ittwassizedgen zi řexmej nnes. Awarni as ad iɣarṣ i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.  
\v 20 Ad issbexxar ukehhan taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* x uɛalṭar. \add Ammu i\add* t ɣa isseṣřeḥ ukehhan uca ad yiři izdeg.   
\m
\v 21 Mařa netta iẓřeḍ uca afus nnes war t issiweḍ, \add xenni\add* ad iksi ijj n yizmar am tɣarṣt n umarwas maḥend ad xas igg aṣřaḥ am igga izmar d tewhibt n wenhezzi. Ad iksi řa d ict n teɛcart n \add ijj n ifa\add* n waren azdad ixeǧḍen s zzect am tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, uřa d ijj n ulux n zzect  
\v 22 d tnayen n tejlilliḥin niɣ tnayen n idbiren imeẓyanin, anect izemmar ufus nnes ad issiweḍ. Ict ad tiři d taɣarṣt n ddenb u tenneɣni ad tiři d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.  
\v 23 Deg wass wiss tmenya ad ten yawi di ṭṭweɛ n usizdeg nnes ɣar ukehhan, ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 24 Ad iksi ukehhan izmar n tɣarṣt n umarwas d ulux nni n zzect uca akehhan ad ten issenhezz am tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* ad iɣarṣ i izmar n tɣarṣt n umarwas uca akehhan ad iksi \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n tɣarṣt n umarwas, ad ten yarr x iɣes n umezzuɣ afusi n wenni ittwassizedgen uřa x yimez n ufus nnes afusi u x yimez n uḍar nnes afusi.  
\v 26 Ad ifarreɣ ukehhan \add ca\add* n zzect x třeqqa n ufus aẓeřmaḍ n yixef nnes.  
\v 27 S uḍaḍ nnes afusi ad irucc ukehhan s zzect nni ɣares deg ufus nnes aẓeřmaḍ sebɛa n twařawin zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 28 Akehhan ad igg \add cwayt\add* zi zzect nni ɣares iǧan deg ufus nnes x iɣes n umezzuɣ afusi n wenni ittwassizedgen uřa x yimez n ufus nnes afusi u x yimez n uḍar nnes afusi, deg wemcan \add nnit mani\add* ttwaggen idammen n tɣarṣṭ n umarwas \add qbeř\add*.  
\v 29 Min iqqimen zi zzect nni ɣar ukehhan deg ufus nnes, ad t igg x uzeǧif n wenni ittwassizedgen, maḥend ad xas igg aṣřaḥ zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* ad issewjed ijj zi tnayen n tejlilliḥin niɣ zeg idbiren imeẓyanen, anect umi izemmar ufus nnes ad issiweḍ.  
\v 31 Zi min d as ɣa issiweḍ ufus nnes, ad yiři ijj i tɣarṣt n ddenb u wenneɣni i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, sennej i tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*. Akehhan ad igg aṣřaḥ x wenni ittwassizedgen zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 32 Wa d azerf i wenni di iǧa wuḍun n řbarṣ uca afus nnes war izemmar ad issiweḍ i usizdeg nnes.”   
\b  
\m
\v 33 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa d Harun, inna:   
\m
\v 34 “Xmi ɣa tadfem ɣar temmurt n Kenɛan, tenni d awem ɣa wceɣ d agřa, uca mařa ggiɣ Necc uḍun n řbarṣ x ca n taddart n temmurt nni ɣarwem d agřa,  
\v 35 ad dd-yas \add xenni\add* wenni ɣar teǧa taddart nni, ad ixebbar akehhan, ad yini: ‘Ittɣiř ayi-dd axmi din ca n wuḍun di taddart.’  
\v 36 \add Xenni\add* akehhan ad issekk, maḥend ad ssexwan taddart qbeř i dd ɣa yas ukehhan \add s yixef nnes\add*, ḥima ad ixemm uḍun, ḥima war ittwassexmij marra min iǧan di taddart. Awarni as ad dd-yas ukehhan, maḥend ad ixemmem taddart.  
\v 37 Mařa ixzar ɣar uḍun uca iẓra aqa uḍun n řeḥyuḍ n taddart banen-dd dayes iḥufar zzizwen niɣ zewɣen, uǧɣen x \add wudem n\add* řḥiḍ,  
\v 38 \add xenni\add* ad iffeɣ ukehhan zi taddart \add nni\add* zi wadaf n taddart uca ad iqqen taddart sebɛa n wussan.  
\v 39 Deg wass wiss sebɛa ad dd-idweř ukehhan uca mařa iẓra aqa uḍun ibezzeɛ x řeḥyuḍ n taddart,  
\v 40 \add xenni\add* ad iweṣṣa ukehhan, maḥend ad kksen iẓra mani iřseq wuḍun u ad ten nḍaren deg ijj n wemcan ixemjen barra i tendint.  
\v 41 Ad yejj ad qeccaren daxeř n taddart ɣar \add marra\add* iɣezdisen nnes, uca ad zeǧɛen abeǧaɛ i qeccaren barra i tendint deg ijj n wemcan d amexmuj.  
\v 42 \add Xenni\add* ad ksin iẓra nneɣni, ad ten ggen deg wemcan n iẓra \add nni iheřcen\add* uca ad ksin abeǧaɛ nneɣni maḥend ad zzayes ḥenncen taddart.  
\v 43 Mařa uḍun idweř-dd uca issfuffi \add ɛawed\add* di taddart awarni řami kksen iẓra u qeccaren taddart awarni řami tt ḥenncen,  
\v 44 \add xenni\add* ad dd-yas ukehhan ad \add tt\add* iqeǧeb. Mařa iẓra, aqa uḍun ibezzeɛ di taddart, \add xenni\add* aqa din ijj n řbarṣ iqesḥen di taddart. Aqa-tt texmej.  
\v 45 Ad hedmen taddart, iẓra nnes d tḥenya nnes d marra tarrist n taddart uca ad ssiggʷejen aya barra i tendint ɣar ijj n wemcan d amexmuj.  
\v 46 Wi ɣa yadfen ɣar taddart deg ijj n wass zeg wussan awarni řami bellɛen \add taddart\add*, netta ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 47 Wi ɣa iṭṭṣen di taddart, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes u wi ɣa iccen di taddart, ad issird arruḍ nnes.  
\v 48 Mařa yudef ukehhan, maḥend ad \add tt\add* iqeǧeb uca iẓra aqa uḍun war imɣir di taddart, awarni řami ḥenncen taddart, \add xenni\add* ad ibarreḥ ukehhan belli taddart tezdeg, minzi uḍun ittwassgenfa.  
\v 49 Ad iksi tnayen n ijḍaḍ d ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen d tɛelǧet, maḥend ad zzaysen ikkes ddenb x taddart. \f ◼ \fr 14:49 \ft \+fk tɛelǧet\ft  - niɣ ‘hisup’\f*  
\v 50 Ad iɣarṣ i yijj n wejḍiḍ deg ict n řqecɛet n třaxt, sennej i waman iddaren.  
\v 51 Ad iksi akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt d tɛelǧet d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen uřa d ajḍiḍ iddaren uca ad issuf \add marra\add* aya deg idammen n wejḍiḍ ittwaɣarṣen u deg waman iddaren uca ad irucc taddart sebɛa n twařawin.  
\v 52 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ikkes ddenb x taddart s idammen n wejḍiḍ, s waman iddaren d wejḍiḍ iddaren d ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt d tɛelǧet d uzeggʷaɣ iḥedqen.  
\v 53 Ad yejj ajḍiḍ iddaren ad iḍwa barra i tendint sennej i wudem n yeyyar. \add Ammu i\add* ɣa igg aṣřaḥ x taddart \add nni\add* uca ad tiři tizdig.”   
\m
\v 54 “Wa d azerf x marra řehřacat n řbarṣ u x tfuri \add n yiřem\add*,  
\v 55 x řbarṣ n arruḍ u n taddart,  
\v 56 x ijj n uɛebbuz, x ict n tḥebbuct u x ijj n wengaz iccemřeř \add n teřmect\add*.  
\v 57 \add Azerf-a\add* aqa i tɣuri deg wass i di ɣa yiři ḥed ixmej niɣ deg wass i di ɣa yiři ḥed izdeg. Wa d azerf n řbarṣ.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Asizzeř zi arrimet n yeryazen d temɣarin  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa d Harun, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, inim asen: \bd ‘Mařa aryaz ɣares ijj n useyyeř zi arrimet nnes\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad yiři ixmej zi ssibbet n useyyeř.  
\v 3 Wa ad yiři d řexmej nnes zi ssibbet n useyyeř nnes: \add mařa\add* arrimet nnes tᵉttejja aseyyeř nnes niɣ arrimet nnes tessbedda aseyyeř nnes, aqa-t d řexmej nnes.  
\v 4 Kuř qama min xef ɣa iṭṭeṣ wenni di iǧa useyyeř, ad yiři ixmej u kuř řqecɛet i xef ɣa iqqim, ad tiři texmej.  
\v 5 Marra wi ɣa iḥadan qama nnes, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird ixef nnes \add ɛawed\add* s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 6 Wenni i ɣa iqqimen x ca x min xef tuɣa iqqim wenni di iǧa useyyeř, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird ixef nnes \add ɛawed\add* s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 7 Wenni i ɣa iḥadan arrimet n wenni di iǧa useyyeř, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes uca netta simant nnes ad issird s waman, uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 8 Mařa wi di iǧa useyyeř issusef x ijj n umezdag, aqa \add wa\add* ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird ixef nnes s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 9 Kuř trict min xef iqqim wenni di iǧa useyyeř, ad tiři texmej.  
\v 10 Marra wi ɣa iḥadan \add mammec ma\add* řqecɛet nni iǧan sadu nnes, ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit uca wi tt ɣa iksin, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird ixef nnes s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 11 Marra wi ɣa ittwaḥadan zeg wenni di iǧa useyyeř břa ma ad issird wa ifassen nnes \add amezwaru\add*, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird ixef nnes s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 12 Ṭṭebṣi n třaxt nni iḥada wenni di iǧa useyyeř, ittxeṣṣa ad ittwarẓ, \add maca\add* marra řqecɛet n tefřawt ad tt sirden s waman. \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt Lawi 6:21; 11:33\x*   
\m
\v 13 Xmi wenni di iǧa useyyeř ad ittwassizdeg zeg useyyeř nnes, ittxeṣṣa as simant nnes ad iḥseb i sebɛa n wussan. \add Xenni\add* ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird arrimet nnes s waman iddaren uca ad yiři izdig.  
\v 14 Deg wass wiss tmenya ad iksi tnayen n tejlilliḥin niɣ tnayen n idbiren imeẓyanen uca ad dd-yas zzat i wudem n SIDI ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca ad ten iwc i ukehhan.  
\v 15 Akehhan ad issewjed ict n tɣarṣt n ddenb d ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ. Akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ zzat i wudem n SIDI x useyyeř nnes.’”\f ◼ \fr 15:15 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*   
\m
\v 16 “\bd Mařa iffeɣ-dd useyyeř n waǧu zeg weryaz\bd*, ad issird arrimet nnes marra s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 17 Kuř arruḍ d kuř iřem i xef iǧa useyyeř n waǧu, ittxeṣṣa ad t sirden s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 18 \add Mařa\add* iṭṭeṣ yijj weryaz ak-d temɣart uca inḍar \add dayes\add* netta, \add xenni\add* ad ssirden \add s tnayen idsen\add* s waman uca ad iřin xemjen ař tameddit.”   
\b  
\m
\v 19 “\bd Mařa tamɣart tuɣa-tt tseyyeř\bd*, aqa xas idammen di arrimet nnes, \add xenni\add* ad teɛzeř sebɛa n wussan. Marra wi tt ɣa iḥadan ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit. \f ◼ \fr 15:19 \ft \+fk teɛzeř\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad tiři di weɛzař nnes’.\f*  
\v 20 Marra min xef tuɣa tᵉṭṭeṣ deg weɛzař nnes, ad yiři ixmej uca marra min xef tuɣa teqqim, ad yiři ixmej.  
\v 21 Marra wi ɣa iḥadan qama nnes, ad issird arruḍ nnes, ad issird ixef nnes s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 22 Marra wi ɣa iḥadan ca n řqecɛet min xef tuɣa tᵉttɣima, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird ixef nnes s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 23 Niɣ mařa iqqim x qama niɣ x řqecɛet i xef tuɣa teqqim nettat, umi iḥada aya ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 24 Mařa iṭṭeṣ akides ijj n weryaz uca yusa-dd xas weɛzař nnes, \add xenni\add* ad yiři ixmej sebɛa n wussan. Kuř qama i x tuɣa iṭṭeṣ, ad tiři texmej.   
\m
\v 25 Mařa usin-dd idammen x ict n temɣart aṭṭas n wussan barra i řmijař n weɛzař nnes niɣ mařa tuɣa aseyyeř ktar x řmijař n weɛzař nnes, \add xenni\add* ad tiři texmej marra ussan n useyyeř i dd-yusin ak-d řexmej nnes, am deg wussan n weɛzař nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:25 \xt Mt. 9:20\x*  
\v 26 Kuř qama min xef tᵉṭṭeṣ marra ussan n useyyeř nnes, ad as tiři am qama n weɛzař nnes u marra řqecɛet min xef teqqim, ad tiři texmej amecnaw řexmej n weɛzař nnes.  
\v 27 Marra wi ɣa iḥadan timesřayin nni, ad yiři ixmej. Ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes uca ad issird ixef nnes s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit.  
\v 28 Mařa tᵉttwassizdeg zeg useyyeř nnes, ittxeṣṣa ad teḥseb i yixef nnes sebɛa n wussan, awarni as ad tiři tezdeg.  
\v 29 Deg wass wiss tmenya ad teksi i yixef nnes tnayen n tejlilliḥin niɣ tnayen n idbiren imeẓyanen uca ad ten tawi ɣar ukehhan ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 30 Akehhan ad issewjed ict n tɣarṣt n ddenb d ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ uca akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ \add di tmesřact\add* n useyyeř n řexmej nnes zzat i wudem n SIDI.   
\m
\v 31 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa tɛezřed ayt n Israil x řexmej nsen, ḥima war ttᵉmettin di řexmej nsen, umi ssxemmajen Tazeddiɣt inu nni \add iǧan\add* di řwesṭ nsen.”   
\m
\v 32 Wa d azerf i wenni ɣar iǧa useyyeř u i wenni zi ɣa iffeɣ waǧu nnes uca \add xenni\add* ad yiři ixmej  
\v 33 u \add ɛawed\add* i tenni min xef iǧa idammen uca \add xenni\add* teɛzeř ixef nnes u \add ɛawed\add* i wi di tuɣa aseyyeř, i weryaz uřa i temɣart, u \add ɛawed\add* i weryaz i tuɣa iṭṭṣen ak-d tenni iǧan texmej.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Ass n Weṣřaḥ  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa awarni i řmewt n tnayen n warraw n Harun, awarni řami dd-qarrben nitni zzat i wudem n SIDI uca mmuten. \x ◘ \xo 16:1 \xt Lawi 10:1, 2\x*  
\v 2 SIDI inna i Musa: “Siweř ak-d Harun, umac, ḥima war ittidef řebda ɣar Uqeddas daxeř i uřeḥḥaf zzat i tqebbart n weṣřaḥ nni iǧan x Ttabut, ḥima war ittmetti ca, minzi Necc ttbaneɣ-dd deg ijj n useynu sennej i tqebbart n weṣřaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 16:2 \xt Uf. 30:10; Ɛbr. 9:7\x*  
\v 3 S uya ad yadef Harun ɣar Uqeddas: s ijj n ufunas, ameẓyan n tfunast, i tɣarṣt n ddenb, u \add s\add* yijj n icarri i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.  
\v 4 Ad yarḍ tcamir iqeddsen n řeqṭen uca ssarwař n řeqṭen ad yiři x arrimet nnes. Ad ibyes taḥezzamt n řeqṭen uca ad yarekkeb areẓẓet n řeqṭen. Aqa man aya d arruḍ iqeddsen. Mařa ad ten yarḍ, ittxeṣṣa as ad issird arrimet nnes s waman d amezwaru.  
\v 5 Ad iksi zi tmesmunt n ayt n Israil tnayen n imyanen zeg iɣayḍen i tɣarṣt n ddenb d ijj n icarri i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.  
\v 6 Ad dd-issqarreb Harun afunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, wenni iǧan i yixef nnes, uca ad igg aṣřaḥ i yixef nnes u i taddart nnes. \f ◼ \fr 16:6 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 16:6 \xt Ɛbr. 7:27, 28\x*  
\v 7 Ad iksi tnayen n imyanen uca ad ten igg zzat i wudem n SIDI ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar.  
\v 8 Ad inḍar Harun taqedduḥt x tnayen n imyanen: ict n tqedduḥt x SIDI u ict n tqedduḥt x iɣayḍ innufsřen, \add qqaren as ‘Ɛazazil’\add*.  
\v 9 Ad dd-issqarreb Harun amyan nni x dd-tewḍa taqedduḥt i SIDI uca ad t issewjed d tɣarṣt n ddenb.  
\v 10 Amyan i x dd-tewḍa taqedduḥt n iɣayḍ innufsřen, ad t igg iddar zzat i wudem n SIDI, maḥend ad zzayes igg aṣřaḥ uca \add xenni\add* ad t issekk am yiɣayḍ innufsřen ɣar řexřa.   
\m
\v 11 Ad dd-issqarreb Harun afunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb, wenni tuɣa i yixef nnes, uca ad igg aṣřaḥ i yixef nnes u i \add aytbab n\add* taddart nnes uca ad iɣarṣ i ufunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb, wenni \add iǧan\add* i yixef nnes.  
\v 12 Ad iksi \add ɛawed\add* ijj n řmejmar iccur s řefḥem itteḥduduqen n uɛalṭar zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ad iccur tnayen n ifassen nnes s řebxur azdad ittfuḥen, uca ad yawi marra aya daxeř i uřeḥḥaf.  
\v 13 Ad igg řebxur x tmessi zzat i wudem n SIDI, ḥima aseynu \add n řefwar\add* n řebxur ad ideř taqebbart n weṣřaḥ i iǧan x Cchadet, uca war ittmetti ca.  
\v 14 Ad iksi \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n ufunas ameẓyan uca ad ten irucc s uḍaḍ nnes x wudem n tqebbart n weṣřaḥ ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq uca \add ɛawed\add* ad irucc \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen sebɛa n twařawin s uḍaḍ nnes zzat i tqebbart n weṣřaḥ. \x ◘ \xo 16:14 \xt Lawi 4:6; Ɛbr. 9:25; 10:4\x*  
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* ad iɣarṣ i umyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb, wenni \add iǧan\add* i řgens uca ad yawi idammen ɣar daxeř i uřeḥḥaf uca ad igg s idammen nnes am mammec igga s idammen n ufunas ameẓyan: ad ten irucc x tqebbart n weṣřaḥ u zzat i tqebbart n weṣřaḥ.  
\v 16 \add Ammu i\add* i ɣa igg aṣřaḥ x Uqeddas i řḥajjat ixemjen n ayt n Israil u i ixeṭṭan nsen i dd-ittasen ak-d marra ddnub nsen. Ammu i ɣa yegg di ssibbet n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, wenni iǧan akidsen di řwesṭ n marra timesřayin ixemjen nsen.   
\m
\v 17 Uřa d ijj n bnadem ad yiři ɛad deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar zeg wami i ɣa yadef maḥend ad igg aṣřaḥ deg Uqeddas ař ɣa iffeɣ \add ɛawed\add*. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa igg aṣřaḥ i yixef nnes u i marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil.  
\v 18 Ad iffeɣ ař uɛalṭar i iǧan zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ad igg asřaḥ x uɛalṭar. Ad iksi \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n ufunas ameẓyan u \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen n umyan uca ad issars \add aya\add* x waccawen n uɛalṭar deg wenneḍ nnes.  
\v 19 Sebɛa n twařawin ad xas irucc s uḍaḍ nnes \add cwayt\add* zeg idammen uca ad t issizdeg u ad t issqeddes zi řexmej n ayt n Israil.  
\v 20 \add Awarni řami\add* ikemmeř aṣřaḥ n Uqeddas d Uqiḍun n Umsagar d uɛalṭar, ad dd-issqarreb \add xenni\add* amyan iddaren.  
\v 21 Ad issars Harun tnayen n ifassen nnes x uzeǧif n umyan iddaren uca \add ammu i\add* ɣa inɛem Harun sennej \add i uzeǧif n umyan\add* x marra řmuɛṣiyyet n ayt n Israil d marra ixeṭṭan nsen i dd-yusin ak-d marra ddnub nsen uca ad ten issars x uzeǧif n umyan uca ad t issekk ɣar řexřa s ufus n ijj n weryaz \add wenni isswejden\add* i ddegga.  
\v 22 Uca iɣayḍ ad yawi ak-d ixef nnes marra řmuɛṣiyyet nsen ɣar ict n jjihet texřa. Netta ad issekk amyan ɣar řexřa.   
\m
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* ad yadef Harun ɣar Uqiḍun n Umsagar uca ad ikkes arruḍ n řeqṭen nni yarḍ, umi yudef ɣar Uqeddas uca ad t yejj din.  
\v 24 Ad issird arrimet nnes s waman deg wemcan amqeddas uca ad yarḍ arruḍ nnes. \add Xenni\add* ad iffeɣ, ad issewjed taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ nnes d tɣarṣt n řgens uca ad igg aṣřaḥ i yixef nnes u i řgens.  
\v 25 Ad issbexxar tadunt n tɣarṣt n ddenb x uɛalṭar.   
\m
\v 26 Wi dd-isekken amyan am umyan innufsřen, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird arrimet nnes s waman. Awarni as ad yadef ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.   
\m
\v 27 Afunas ameẓyan n tɣarṣt n ddenb d umyan n ṭɣarṣt n ddenb i zi ttwassidfen idammen nsen, maḥend ad zzaysen ittwagg aṣřaḥ deg Uqeddas, ad ten ssuffɣen barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar uca ad zzaysen sscemḍen iřmawen nsen d weysum nsen d umessař nsen s tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 16:27 \xt Lawi 6:23; Ɛbr. 13:11\x*  
\v 28 Wi ten ɣa isscemḍen, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes, ad issird arrimet nnes s waman. Awarni as ad yadef ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.   
\m
\v 29 Ta d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i kenniw. Deg uyur wiss sebɛa, deg \add wass\add* wiss ɛecra n uyur, ad tesswaḍɛem ixef nwem uca war tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet, niɣ wenni dd-ixeřqen di temmurt niɣ ubarrani nni izeddɣen di řwest nwem. \x ◘ \xo 16:29 \xt Lawi 23:27\x*  
\v 30 Minzi deg wass nni ad ittwagg weṣřaḥ i kenniw, maḥend ad tᵉttwassizedgem. Kenniw marra ad tᵉttwassizedgem zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 31 \add Ass nni\add* ad yiři d ijj wass n ssebt, arraḥet tmun i kenniw. Ad tesswaḍɛem ixef nwem, aqa-tt d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda.  
\v 32 Akehhan, wenni dehnen u řeqqmen nitni deg wemcan n babas, maḥend ad yiři d akehhan, ad igg aṣřaḥ uca ad yarḍ arruḍ n řeqṭen, arruḍ iqeddsen.  
\v 33 Ad igg aṣřaḥ x Zzawect Iqeddsen u x Tqiḍunt n Umsagar u x uɛalṭar. Ad igg aṣřaḥ \add ɛawed\add* x marra ikehhanen u x marra řgens n wegraw.  
\v 34 Ta d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i kenniw, ḥima ad ittwagg weṣřaḥ x marra ayt n Israil i marra ddnub nsen, ict n twařa deg useggʷas.” Uca igga am mammec iweṣṣa SIDI i Musa. \x ◘ \xo 16:34 \xt Uf. 30:10; Ɛbr. 9:7\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 17
\s1 Ittxeṣṣa ad awyen tiɣarṣa d tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d Harun d warraw nnes u ak-d marra ayt n Israil, ini asen: ‘Wa d awař i iweṣṣa SIDI, iqqar:  
\v 3 Kuř aryaz zi taddart n Israil, wenni iɣarṣen i ufunas niɣ i yezmar niɣ i iɣayḍ di řmargeḥ niɣ wenni \add t\add* iɣarṣen barra i řmargeḥ,  
\v 4 \add maca\add* war t yiwi d tawhibt ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, maḥend ad t-i-dd-issqarreb d tawhibt ɣar SIDI zzat n Tzeddiɣt n SIDI, ad as dd-ittwaḥseb idammen \add nni\add*. Netta issizzeř idammen, \add s uyenni\add* ad ittwaqes weryaz nni zi řgens nnes,  
\v 5 maḥend, xmi ɣa qeddmen ayt n Israil tiɣarṣa nsen, tinni \add nnumen\add* ɣarrṣen barra deg iyyar, nitni ad tent awyen ɣar SIDI, ɣar ukehhan ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, maḥend ad tent qeddmen \add din am\add* tɣarṣa n řehna i SIDI.  
\v 6 Akehhan ad izeǧeɛ idammen x uɛalṭar n SIDI ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar u netta ad issbexxar tadunt am yict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Uf. 29:18; Lawi 4:31\x*  
\v 7 War ttqeddamen ɛad tiɣarṣa nsen i imuyan \add ijennin\add*, inni ḍeffaren nitni am ayt n farq-ccɣeř. Ta d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i nitni i \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen.’  
\v 8 Ad asen tinid ɛawed: ‘Kuř aryaz n ayt n Israil u n ibarraniyyen, inni iǧan di řwesṭ nsen, wenni ixsen ad issbexxar ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ niɣ ca n ṭaɣarṣt \add i ɣares\add*,  
\v 9 \add maca\add* war tt-i-dd-yiwi ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, ḥima ad tt issewjed i SIDI, aryaz nni ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tawṣeyyet ḥima war ttᵉtten idammen  
\m
\v 10 “Kuř ijj zi taddart n Israil niɣ zeg ibarraniyyen, inni izeddɣen di řwesṭ nsen, wenni i ɣa iccen idammen mammec ma ggin, Necc ad qeřbeɣ udem inu x řeɛmar nni iccen idammen nni, uca ad t qeḍɛeɣ zi řwesṭ n řgens nnes. \x ◘ \xo 17:10 \xt Amz. 9:4; Lawi 3:17; 7:27; 19:26; Aɛwd. 12:16, 23; 1 Ṣm. 14:33\x*  
\v 11 Minzi řeɛmar n arrimet deg idammen uca Necc wciɣ awem \add idammen\add* x uɛalṭar, maḥend ad zzaysen ittwagg weṣřaḥ i řeɛmur nwem, minzi idammen d ina i ɣa iwyen aṣřaḥ i řeɛmar.  
\v 12 X uya aqa nniɣ i ayt n Israil: Uřa d ijj zzaywem war ittett zeg idammen, uřa d abarrani i izeddɣen di řwesṭ nwem war ittett idammen.  
\v 13 Kuř ijj zeg ayt n Israil u zeg ibarraniyyen i izeddɣen di řwesṭ nwem, wenni iymaren ijj n umuddar niɣ ijj n wejḍiḍ nni izemmar ad ittwacc, ad issizzeř idammen nnes uca ad ten issduriy s ucař.  
\v 14 Minzi řeɛmar n kuř aysum d idammen nnes, aqa aten \add d ijjen\add* ak-d řeɛmar nnes. S uyenni nniɣ i ayt n Israil: ‘War ttᵉttem zeg idammen n mammec ma igga weysum!’, minzi řeɛmar n marra aysum d idammen nnes. Wenni zzaysen ɣa iccen, ad ittwaqess \add zi řgens nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 17:14 \xt Amz. 9:4\x*  
\v 15 Marra wenni i ɣa iccen zeg ict n řxecbet niɣ zeg ijj n \add umuddar\add* imezzqen, ma netta zi tarwa n temmurt niɣ netta d ijj n ubarrani, ad iṣebben arruḍ nnes uca ad issird ixef nnes s waman uca ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit. \add Awarni aya\add* ad yiři izdeg. \x ◘ \xo 17:15 \xt Uf. 22:31; Lawi 11:40; Ḥiz. 44:31\x*  
\v 16 Mařa war issird \add arruḍ\add* u war issird arrimet nnes, \add xenni\add* ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet nnes.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 18
\s1 Izerfan ḍidd i min iǧan d řefḍiḥet di twacunt u di familiya  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca ini asen: ‘Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!  
\v 3 War tteggem am mammec tteggen di temmurt n Miṣra mani tuɣa tzeddɣem kenniw, u war tᵉtteggem am mammec tteggen di temmurt n Kenɛan mani kenniw ɣa nedheɣ, u war tᵉtteggem ɛlaḥsab tiweṣṣa nsen. \f ◼ \fr 18:3 \ft \+fk war tᵉtteggem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘war tᵉggurem’.\f*  
\v 4 Ad teggem lfarayiḍ inu uca ad teḥḍam tiweṣṣa inu, maḥend ad daysen tuyurem: Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!  
\v 5 Ad teḥḍam tiweṣṣa inu d lfarayiḍ inu: bnadem nni tent itteggen, ad zzaysent iddar, Necc d SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 18:5 \xt Ḥiz. 20:11, 13; Rum. 10:5; Gal. 3:12\x*   
\m
\v 6 Uřa d ijj ad dd-iqarreb ɣar ca n yijjen zi raǧ nnes, ḥima ad issɛarra řɛar nnes: Necc d SIDI.   
\m
\v 7 War ttessɛarri ca řɛar n babac d řɛar n yemmac. Aqa-tt d yemmac, war ttessɛarri ca řɛar nnes.  
\v 8 Řɛar n temɣart n babac war t ttessɛarri ca. Aqa-t d řɛar n babac. \x ◘ \xo 18:8 \xt Lawi 20:11; 1 Kur. 5:1\x*  
\v 9 \add X\add* řɛar n učmac, yeǧis n babac niɣ yeǧis n yemmac, niɣ nettat tᵉttwaxřeq-dd di taddart niɣ barra i taddart, aqa řɛar nnes war t tessɛarri ca.  
\v 10 \add X\add* řɛar n yeǧis n mmic niɣ n yeǧis n yeǧic, war ttessɛarri ca řɛar nsen minzi aqa d řɛar nnec.  
\v 11 War ttessɛarri ca řɛar n yeǧis n temɣart n babac, tenni dd-ittwaxeřqen i babac. Aqa-tt d učmac. \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt Lawi 20:17\x*  
\v 12 War ttessɛarri ca řɛar n učmas n babac. Aqa-tt d raǧ n babac. \x ◘ \xo 18:12 \xt Lawi 20:19\x*  
\v 13 War ttessɛarri ca řɛar n učmas n yemmac, minzi nettat d raǧ n yemmac.  
\v 14 War ttessɛarri ca řɛar n umas n babac u war dd-ttqarrabed ɣar temɣart nnes, aqa-tt d ɛentic. \x ◘ \xo 18:14 \xt Lawi 20:20; Ḥiz. 22:11\x*  
\v 15 War ttessɛarri ca řɛar n temɣart n mmic, aqa-tt d tamɣart n mmic. War ttessɛarri ca řɛar nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:15 \xt Lawi 20:12\x*  
\v 16 War ttessɛarri ca řɛar n temɣart n umac, aqa-t d řɛar n umac. \x ◘ \xo 18:16 \xt Lawi 20:21\x*  
\v 17 War tessɛarri ca řɛar n temɣart d yeǧis. War dd-ttawi ca yeǧis n mmis niɣ yeǧis n yeǧis, maḥend ad tessɛarrid řɛar nnes. Aqa atent d raǧ \add nnec\add*, aqa-tt d ict n tmeɛmuč \add ifesden\add*. \x ◘ \xo 18:17 \xt Lawi 20:14\x*  
\v 18 War dd-ttawi tamɣart \add d tacna\add* ak-d učmas maḥend ad tt tɣenned \add ammu\add*, xmi ɣa tessɛarrid řɛar nnes am ɛad teddar.  
\v 19 War dd-ttqarrab ca ɣar ict n temɣart xmi ɣa teɛzeř ixef nnes zi ssibbet n řexmej nnes ḥima ad tessɛarrid řɛar nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:19 \xt Lawi 20:18\x*  
\v 20 War ttᵉṭṭeṣ ak-d temɣart n jjar nnec, maɣar \add ammu\add* i ɣa tfesded ixef nnec zzayes. \x ◘ \xo 18:20 \xt Lawi 20:10; Aɛwd. 22:22; Yḥ. 9:5 \x*   
\m
\v 21 War ttejji arraw nnec ad ẓwan ɣar Mulak, war ssexsara Isem n AREBBI nnec, Necc d SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 18:21 \xt Lawi 20:2; Aɛwd. 18:10; 2 Ij. 17:17; 23:10\x*  
\v 22 War ttᵉṭṭeṣ ca ak-d ca n weryaz am tᵉṭṭeṣed ak-d temɣart. Aqa-tt d jjɛifect. \x ◘ \xo 18:22 \xt Lawi 20:13\x*  
\v 23 War fessed ca ixef nnec ak-d ca n řebhimet am tfeḥḥřed ixef nnec akides, u tamɣart war tᵉttbeddi zzat i řebhimet maḥend ad tfesded ixef nnes zzayes. Aqa d ijj n uxeǧeḍ \add ifesden\add*. \x ◘ \xo 18:23 \xt Lawi 20:15, 16\x*  
\v 24 War fessdem ca ixef nwem s marra timesřayin-a, minzi řegnus nni i ɣa ssuffɣeɣ zzat i uɣembub nwem, tuɣa fessden ixef nsen s marra timesřayin-a.  
\v 25 \add S uyenni\add* tedweř temmurt tefsed uca Necc ad as xeǧṣeɣ řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, uca ad tɛuqq temmurt imezdaɣ nnes.  
\v 26 \add Maca\add* kenniw ad teḥḍam tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ inu, war tteggem uřa d ict n řḥajjet zi marra jjɛayef-a, niɣ wenni zi tarwa n temmurt uřa d abarrani nni izeddɣen di řwesṭ nwem. \x ◘ \xo 18:26 \xt Lawi 20:22\x*  
\v 27 Minzi iryazen n temmurt, \add inni tuɣa\add* qbeř nwem, aqa ggin marra jjɛayef-a uca \add ammu i\add* tedweř temmurt tefsed.  
\v 28 War ttejji tammurt ad kenniw tɛuqq umi tt tfessdem, am mammec tɛuqq \add temmurt\add* řgens nni tuɣa \add din\add* qbeř nwem.  
\v 29 Minzi marra inni iggin ca zi marra jjɛayef-a, aqa řeɛmur i ɣa iggin \add ammu\add*, ad ttwaqeḍɛen zi řgens nsen.  
\v 30 Ad teḥḍam min d awem umureɣ, maḥend war tḍeffarem tiweṣṣa yurṣuḍen am mammec tt ggin \add řegnus\add* qbeř nwem. War zzaysent tfessdem ixef nwem, Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 19
\s1 Tiweṣṣa x uweqqar di tudart  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ɣar Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d marra tamesmunt n ayt n Israil uca ini asen: ‘Ittxeṣṣa ad tiřim d imqeddasen, minzi Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, aqa ayi d amqeddas! \x ◘ \xo 19:2 \xt Lawi 11:44; 20:7, 26; 1 Bṭ. 1:16\x*  
\v 3 Kuř ijj ad iweqqar yemmas d babas uca ussan inu n ssebt ad ten teḥḍam, Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!\x ◘ \xo 19:3 \xt Uf. 20:12; 31:13; Lawi 26:2\x*  
\v 4 War ddikkʷiřem ɣar l’aṣnam u war tteggem i yixef nwem \add řexyařat\add* ifesyen d irebbiten. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem! \x ◘ \xo 19:4 \xt Uf. 34:17\x*  
\v 5 Xmi ɣa tqeddmen taɣarṣt n řehna i SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad tt tqeddmem s ijj n webrid i zi ɣa tᵉttwaqebřem s arḍa.  
\v 6 Ittxeṣṣa ad tᵉttwacc deg wass n tɣarṣt nwem uřa di tiwecca awarni as. Min iqqimen ař wass wiss třata ad ittwassecmeḍ s tmessi. \x ◘ \xo 19:6 \xt Lawi 7:16\x*  
\v 7 Mařa tᵉttwacc ɛad deg wass wiss třata, ad tiři d jjɛifect, war tᵉttwaqebbeř s arḍa.  
\v 8 Wi zzayes ɣa iccen ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, minzi issexsara min iǧan d amqeddas n SIDI uca \add xenni\add* ad ittwaqess bnadem nni zi řgens nnes.   
\m
\v 9 Mařa temjarem ṣṣabet n temmurt nwem, war mejjar cek iyyar nnec ař aɣezdis aneggar niɣ ad tjemɛed min iqqimen awarni tameyra nnec. \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt Lawi 23:22; Aɛwd. 24:19\x*  
\v 10 War řeqqeḍ uḍiř n umarjeɛ nnec kuřci, war ḥruw marra min din iqqimen \add di temmurt\add* deg umarjeɛ nnec n uḍiř. Ad tejjed aya i umezřuḍ u i ubarrani, Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!   
\m
\v 11 War ttacar u war ssxarriq, uřa d ijj ad icmet jjar nnes. \x ◘ \xo 19:11 \xt Uf. 20:15\x*  
\v 12 War ttjaǧam ẓur s Yisem inu. War ssexsara Isem n AREBBI nnec. Necc d SIDI.\x ◘ \xo 19:12 \xt Uf. 20:7; Aɛwd. 5:11\x*   
\m
\v 13 War ssḥissif jjar nnec niɣ ad \add t\add* tacared. War ttᵉṭṭef řmunet n icewwařen zi ǧiřet ař tiwecca. \f ◼ \fr 19:13 \ft \+fk war ttᵉṭṭef\ft  - nican zi Tɛibranit ‘war ttnusi’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:13 \xt Aɛwd. 24:14; Yaɛ. 5:4\x*  
\v 14 War ttekkʷar adehcur u war ttegg ca min di ɣa inqareḍ udarɣař, maca ittxeṣṣa ad teggʷeded AREBBI, Necc d SIDI!   
\m
\v 15 Ɣar weḥkam war ttɣeccim. War sɛizzi amezřuḍ u war sɛeddu ɣar bu-txuba. Ittxeṣṣa ad tḥekmed x jjar nnec s usegged. \x ◘ \xo 19:15 \xt Aɛwd. 1:17; 16:19; Awřn. 24:23\x*  
\v 16 War ggur jar řgens nnec s unemmem, war ttbeddi x idammen n jjar nnec, Necc d SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 19:16 \xt Uf. 23:1\x*   
\m
\v 17 War carreh umac deg wuř nnec. Ad tɛeřmed aɛřam i jjar nnec u war tkessid ddenb xak zi ssibbet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 19:17 \xt Mt. 18:15; Lk. 17:3; 1 Yḥ. 2:9, 11; 3:15\x*  
\v 18 War ttentiqim niɣ ad txemmřed antaqem x tarwa n řgens nnec. Ad texsed jjar nnec amecnaw ixef nnec, Necc d SIDI.\x ◘ \xo 19:18 \xt Mt. 5:39,43,44; 22:39; Lk. 6:27; Rum. 12:19; 13:9; 1 Kur. 6:7; Gal. 5:14; 1 Ts. 5:15; 1 Bṭ. 3:9; Yaɛ. 2:8\x*   
\m
\v 19 Ad teḥḍam tiweṣṣa inu. War ttřeqqam ca řebhimet nnec ak-d ijj n marka nneɣni. War zarreɛ tnayen n markat n zzariɛet deg iyyar nnec u war yarreḍ arruḍ ittwaggen s tnayen n markat n ukettan. \x ◘ \xo 19:19 \xt Aɛwd. 22:9, 11\x*   
\m
\v 20 Mařa aryaz iṭṭeṣ ak-d ict n temɣart, ict n tayya ixḍeb i-tt yijj n weryaz \add nneɣni\add*, maca war ittwaxeǧeṣ ɛad ttaman nnes n ufekki niɣ temmewc as třelli, \add xenni\add* ad yiři řeḥsab, \add maca\add* war ttwaneqqen ca, minzi nettat tuɣa \add ɛad\add* war tᵉttwaḥar ca.  
\v 21 Netta ad yawi taɣarṣt n umarwas nnes i SIDI ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar, ijj n icarri \add am\add* tɣarṣt n umarwas.  
\v 22 Akehhan ad xas igg aṣřaḥ s icarri n tɣarṣt n umarwas zzat i wudem n SIDI i ddenb nnes i igga uca ddenb nnes i igga ad as ittwaɣfar. \f ◼ \fr 19:22 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*   
\m
\v 23 Xmi ɣa tawḍem di temmurt uca teẓẓum ɛřam kuř ticejjura, maḥend ad zzaysent teccem, \add xenni\add* war txettnem ‘řeɛdařyet nnes’, tenni d řɣiǧet nnes. Třata n iseggʷusa war tent txettnem, war zzaysent ttettem ca.  
\v 24 Deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa ad tiři marra řɣiǧet nnes tqeddes, i usemɣar i SIDI.  
\v 25 Deg useggʷas wiss xemsa ad teccem řɣiǧet nnes uca ṣṣabet nnes ad tt tewcem i yixef nwem. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!   
\m
\v 26 War ttettem ca ak-d idammen. War iɛeddeř ad tgezznem niɣ ad tceɣřem ixef nwem s tbezgiwt.  
\v 27 War ttḥeffim acuwwaf n uzeǧif nwem deg wenneḍ nnes u war ttḍeyyiɛem ca tma n tmart nwem. \x ◘ \xo 19:27 \xt Lawi 21:5; Irm. 9:25; 25:23; 49:32\x*  
\v 28 War iɛeddeř ad tcarḍem arrimet nwem zi ssibbet n yijj n umettin niɣ ad tarecmem tiggaz di \add arrimet\add* nwem. Necc d SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 19:28 \xt Aɛwd. 14:1\x*   
\m
\v 29  War sdeǧi yeǧic, ad tt tarred d tamɣart n farq-ccɣeř, ḥima war tweṭṭi temmurt di farq-ccɣeř uca \add xenni\add* ad teccur temmurt s řefḍiḥet.  
\v 30 Ad teḥḍam ussan inu n ssebt uca ad tweqqarem Zzawect inu Iqeddsen. Necc d SIDI!  
\v 31 War ttdikkwiřem ɣar yinni issawařan ak-d imettan u ɣar igezzanen, war ɣarsen arezzfem, ḥima ad zzaysen tᵉttwaxemjem. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem! \x ◘ \xo 19:31 \xt Lawi 20:6\x*   
\m
\v 32 Ad tekkared i wenni ɣar iǧa ucuwwaf icab uca ad tweqqared udem n iwessura uca ad teggʷeded AREBBI nnec. Necc d SIDI!   
\m
\v 33 Xmi kidek ɣa izdeɣ ijj n ubarrani di temmurt nwem, war t ttḍeǧmem. \x ◘ \xo 19:33 \xt Uf. 22:21\x*  
\v 34 Abarrani, wenni ɣarwem izeddɣen, ad awem yiři am yijjen zi tarwa n temmurt nwem. Ad t texsed am yixef nnec, minzi tuɣa kenniw d ibarraniyyen di temmurt n Miṣra. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!   
\m
\v 35 Xmi ɣa tiřim ɣar weḥkam war ttɣeccem ca s \add řeɛbar n\add* tuzzeggart niɣ n ddqeř niɣ s \add řeɛbar\add* n min dayes.  
\v 36 Ad ɣarwem yiři d ijj n řmizan nican d iẓra n řmizan nican uřa d ijj n ifa nican d ijj n uhinu nican, Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni kenniw dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 19:36 \xt Awřn. 11:1; 16:11; 20:10\x*  
\v 37 Ad teḥḍam marra tiweṣṣa d řumur inu uca ad ten teggem. Necc d SIDI!’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 20
\s1 Izerfen x mammec i ɣa yiři řɛiqab  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Ad tinid i ayt n Israil: ‘Kuř ijjen zeg ayt n Israil niɣ zeg ibarraniyyen, wenni i ɣa iwcin zeg iḥenjiren nnes i Mulak, ad ittwaneɣ nican. Řgens n temmurt ad t yarjem. \f ◼ \fr 20:2 \ft \+fk ad t yarjem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘ad t yarjem s iẓra’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:2 \xt Lawi 18:21\x*  
\v 3 Necc ad qeřbeɣ udem inu x weryaz nni uca ad t qeḍɛeɣ zi řgens nnes, minzi netta aqa iwca zi zzariɛet nnes i Mulak. S uyenni tuɣa issexmej Zzawect inu Iqeddsen uca issexsar Isem amqeddas inu.  
\v 4 Mařa tarwa n temmurt qqnen tiṭṭawin nsen x weryaz nni, xmi ɣa iwc netta zi zzariɛet nnes i Mulak, uca nitni war t neqqen,  
\v 5 xenni Necc ad qeřbeɣ udem inu x weryaz nni u x řaǧ nnes uca ad t qeḍɛeɣ zi jar řgens nnes, netta d marra inni issefsaden ixef nsen am ddekkwařen awarni as maḥend ad ssfesden ixef nsen ak-d Mulak.’”   
\m
\v 6 “Bnadem nni i ɣa iqeřben ixef nnes ɣar yinni issawařan ak-d imettan d igezzanen, maḥend ad dewřen awarni asen am ssfesden ixef nsen, Necc ad qeřbeɣ udem inu x bnadem nni uca ad t qeḍɛeɣ zi jar řgens nnes.”\f ◼ \fr 20:6 \ft \+fk Bnadem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Řeɛmar’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:6 \xt Lawi 19:31\x*   
\m
\v 7 “Sqeddsem ixef nwem, iřim d imqeddasen, minzi Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem! \x ◘ \xo 20:7 \xt Lawi 11:44; 19:2; 1 Bṭ. 1:16\x*  
\v 8 Ḥḍam tiweṣṣa inu uca ggem zzaysent. Necc d SIDI, wenni kenniw issqeddsen.”   
\m
\v 9 “Maɣar kuř aryaz nni i ɣa ineɛřen x babas niɣ x yemmas, ad ittwaneɣ nican. Inɛeř x babas niɣ x yemmas, idammen nnes \add aqa aten\add* xas. \x ◘ \xo 20:9 \xt Uf. 21:17; Awřn. 20:20; Mt. 15:4\x*  
\v 10 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz izna ak-d temɣart n weryaz \add nneɣni\add*, \add xenni\add* wenni tuɣa izennan ak-d temɣart n jjar nnes ad ittwaneɣ nican, wenni iznan d tenni iznan. \x ◘ \xo 20:10 \xt Lawi 18:20; Aɛwd. 22:22; Yḥ. 8:5\x*  
\v 11 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz, am iṭṭeṣ ak-d temɣart n babas, aqa issɛurri řɛar n babas, \add xenni\add* nitni s tnayen ad ttwanɣen nican. Idammen nsen aqa aten xasen. \f ◼ \fr 20:11 \ft \+fk Aqa ggint i yixef nsen.\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Idammen nsen aqa-ten xasen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:11 \xt Lawi 18:8\x*  
\v 12 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz iṭṭeṣ ak-d temɣart n mmis, \add xenni\add* nitni s tnayen ad ttwanɣen nican. Aqa ggin ijj n uxeǧeḍ ifesden. Idammen nsen aqa aten xasen. \f ◼ \fr 20:12 \ft \+fk temɣart n mmis\ft  - aqa-tt d tasřit nnes.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:12 \xt Lawi 18:15\x*  
\v 13 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz iṭṭeṣ ak-d ijj n weryaz nneɣni am mammec itteṭṭeṣ \add weryaz\add* ak-d ict n temɣart, \add xenni\add* aqa nitni s tnayen idsen ggin ict n řefḍiḥet temɣar. Ad ttwanɣen nican. Idammen nsen \add aqa aten\add* xasen. \x ◘ \xo 20:13 \xt Lawi 18:22\x*  
\v 14 \add Mařa\add* imeřc ijj n weryaz ca n temɣart uřa d yemmas, aqa-tt d řefḍiḥet. Ad t sscemḍen s tmessi, netta d nitenti \add s tnayen\add*, ḥima xenni war tᵉttiři \add ɛad\add* d řefḍiḥet di řwesṭ nwem. \x ◘ \xo 20:14 \xt Lawi 18:17\x*  
\v 15 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz iṣṣur ixef nnes ak-d ict n řebhimet, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaneɣ nican. Ittxeṣṣa \add ɛawed\add* ad tenɣem řebhimet. \x ◘ \xo 20:15 \xt Lawi 18:23\x*  
\v 16 \add Mařa\add* ca n temɣart tqarreb-dd ɣar ca n řebhimet mammec ma tegga, maḥend ad kides tfeḥḥeř, \add xenni\add* ad tenɣed tamɣart d řebhimet. Ad ttwanɣen nican. Idammen nsen \add aqa aten\add* xasen.  
\v 17 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz iṭṭef učmas, yeǧis n babas niɣ yeǧis n yemmas, uca iẓra řɛar nnes uca nettat teẓra řɛar nnes, aqa-tt d řefḍiḥet. Ad ttwanɣen \add s tnayen\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin n tarwa n řgens nsen. Aqa issɛurri řɛar n učmas, ad yarbu řmuɛṣiyyet nnes. \x ◘ \xo 20:17 \xt Lawi 18:9\x*  
\v 18 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz iṭṭeṣ ak-d ict n temɣart tenni x iǧa idammen uca aqa issɛurri řɛar nnes, issɛurri anu \add n idammen\add* nnes, uca nettat simant nnes tessɛurri anu n idammen nnes, \add xenni\add* ad ttwaqeḍɛen s tnayen zi řwesṭ n řgens nsen. \x ◘ \xo 20:18 \xt Lawi 18:19\x*  
\v 19 War sɛarri ca učmas n yemmac niɣ učmas n babac, minzi \add xenni\add* issfeṭṭaḥ \add bnadem\add* řɛar n raǧ nnes. Nitni ad arbun řmuɛṣiyyet nsen. \x ◘ \xo 20:19 \xt Lawi 18:12, 13\x*  
\v 20 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz, wenni ittᵉṭṭṣen ak-d ɛentis, aqa issɛurri řɛar n ɛemmis, ad arbun nitni řmuɛṣiyyet nsen. Ad mmten břa tarwa. \f ◼ \fr 20:20 \ft \+fk ɛentis\ft  - aqa-tt d tamɣart n umas n babas.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:20 \xt Lawi 18:14\x*  
\v 21 \add Mařa\add* ijj n weryaz yiwi tamɣart n umas, \add aqa\add* man aya d \add aɛeddi\add* x weɛzař \add n temɣart\add*. Aqa issɛurri řɛar n umas. Ad iřin břa iḥenjiren.’” \x ◘ \xo 20:21 \xt Lawi 18:16\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 22 “Ḥḍam marra tiweṣṣa inu d marra lfarayiḍ inu uca ggem tent, maḥend war kenniw tᵉttɛuqqi temmurt mani kenniw i ɣa nedheɣ, ḥima ad dayes tzedɣem. \x ◘ \xo 20:22 \xt Lawi 18:26\x*  
\v 23 War ggurem x tebridt n tweṣṣa n řgens nni ɣa ssuffɣeɣ zzat i wudem nwem, minzi nitni ggin marra timesřayin-a u \add s uya\add* carrheɣ ten. \x ◘ \xo 20:23 \xt Lawi 18:3,30\x*  
\v 24 Necc nniɣ awem: Kenniw ad twartem tammurt nsen uca ad awem tt-i-dd wceɣ d řwart, ict n temmurt ifeyyḍen s uɣi d tamment. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni kenniw ifarzen zi jar řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 20:24 \xt Uf. 3:8\x*   
\m
\v 25 \add X uya\add* kenniw ad tmeyyzem jar řebhayem n řeḥřař d yinni ixemjen u jar ijḍaḍ ixemjen d yinni n řeḥřař. War ssexsaram řeɛmuř nwem ak-d \add ca\add* n řebhimet niɣ ak-d \add ca\add* n wejḍiḍ niɣ ak-d \add ca\add* zi marra min ittbuɛen x temmurt, \add marra\add* min d awem ḥarrmeɣ, ḥima ad t tḥesbem d řexmej.” \x ◘ \xo 20:25 \xt Lawi 11:2; Aɛwd. 14:4\x*  
\v 26 “Aqa kenniw ad ayi tiřim d imqeddasen, minzi Necc d SIDI d amqeddas uca Necc farzeɣ kenniw zi řegnus, ḥima ad tiřim inu.   
\m
\v 27 Mařa ijj n weryaz niɣ ict n temɣart ɣares buḥbeř n uɛezzem n imettan niɣ n tgezzant, \add xenni\add* ad ttwanɣen nican. Ad ten arejmen. Idammen nsen \add aqa aten\add* xasen.” \x ◘ \xo 20:27 \xt Aɛwd. 18:10; 1 Ṣm. 28:7\x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 21
\s1 Asizdeg n ikehhanen  
\m
\v 1 Inna SIDI i Musa: “Siweř ak-d ikehhanen, arraw n Harun, uca ini asen: ‘War iɛeddeř i uřa d ijj \add zzaywem\add* ad issexmej ixef nnes s ijj n umettin jar řgens nnes.  
\v 2 mɣir s raǧ nnes yudsen, s yemmas niɣ s babas niɣ s mmis niɣ s yeǧis niɣ s umas.  
\v 3 Uřa s učmas nni d taɛzarct, tenni d řaǧ nnes yudsen u war ɣares tuɣi weryaz, aqa iɛeddeř ad zzayes issexmej ixef nnes.  
\v 4 Bab \add n taddart\add* war issxemmaj ixef nnes jar řgens nnes. S uya ittwaf issexsar ixef nnes.”   
\m
\v 5 “War tteggen ca n wemcan iquccar x izeǧif nsen, u war ttḥeffin ṭṭarf n tmart nsen u war carrḍen acarreḍ deg weysum nsen. \x ◘ \xo 21:5 \xt Lawi 19:27; Irm. 9:25; 25:23; 49:32\x*  
\v 6 Ad iřin d imqeddasen i AREBBI nsen uca war feṭṭḥen Isem n AREBBI nsen, minzi aqa d nitni i ittawyen tiwhibin n tmessi ɣar AREBBI, tinni d macca n AREBBI nsen. S uya ad iřin d imqeddasen.  
\v 7 War iɛeddeř ad awyen tamɣart nni iǧan d lfasda niɣ icten tᵉttwaɣṣeb. Uřa d ict n temɣart nni ittwaǧfen zeg weryaz nnes, war tt ttiwyen, minzi \add akehhan\add* d amqeddas i AREBBI nnes.  
\v 8 Ad t tḥesbed d amqeddas, minzi netta ittawi macca n AREBBI nnec. Ad yiři d amqeddas i cek, minzi Necc d amqeddas, \add Necc d\add* SIDI wenni kenniw issqeddsen.”   
\m
\v 9 “Mařa yeǧis n ijj n weryaz \add nni iǧan d\add* akehhan tessefḍeḥ ixef nnes s farq-ccɣeř \add nnes\add*, \add xenni\add* aqa tessefḍeḥ babas uca ittxeṣṣa as ad tᵉttwassecmeḍ s tmessi.”   
\m
\v 10 “Arrays n ikehhanen jar aytmas, wenni x uzeǧif nnes tᵉttwafarreɣ zzect n wedhan u wenni ittwařeqqmen, maḥend ad yarḍ arruḍ \add n ukehhan\add*, netta war izemmar ad iḍřeq i \add ucuwwaf x\add* uzeǧif nnes niɣ ad icarreg arruḍ nnes.  
\v 11 War iɛeddeř ad dd-iqarreb ɣar ijj n umettin, \add ɛad\add* s babas d yemmas war iɛeddeř ad issexmej ixef nnes.  
\v 12 War itteffeɣ zi Zzawect Iqeddsen, ḥima war issexsara Zzawect Iqeddsen n AREBBI, minzi ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* n zzect n wedhan n AREBBI nnes aqa-t xas. Necc d SIDI!  
\v 13 Ad yawi ict n teɛzarect d tamɣart.  
\v 14 War ittiwi tajjač niɣ taneǧaft niɣ tenni ittwaɣeṣben \add d tamɣart\add*, maca ad yawi ict n teɛzarect zi řgens nnes d tamɣart.  
\v 15 War issexsara zzariɛet nnes jar řgens nnes, minzi Necc d SIDI, wenni t issqeddsen.”   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 17 “Siweř ak-d Harun, ini: ‘Uřa d ijj zi zzariɛet nnec di \add marra\add* jjiřat nsen i di iǧa ca n uneɛḍab, ad dd-iqarreb, ḥima ad yawi macca \add n tewhibt\add* n AREBBI nnes.  
\v 18 Minzi uřa d ijj n weryaz war dd-ittqarrib ca s yijj n řɛib, ma d adarɣař i iǧa niɣ d aqidar niɣ s ca war iḥři niɣ ɣares ṣṣifet tfarɣ  
\v 19 niɣ ijj n weryaz yarẓ as uḍar niɣ afus  
\v 20 niɣ bu-teɛrurt niɣ \add ḥed yařwes di ca n\add* yijj n ttejjař niɣ s ict n tiṭṭ tuff niɣ s jdam niɣ s ict n ccamet texsar niɣ s iqeǧařen idgedgen.  
\v 21 War iɛeddeř i uřa d ijj n weryaz zi zzariɛet n ukehhan Harun, wenni di iǧa ca n řɛib, ad ireḥḥeg, maḥend ad iqeddem tiwhibin n tmessi n SIDI. Aqa dayes aneɛḍab, war izemmar ad iffeɣ maḥend ad iqeddem macca \add n tewhibt\add* n AREBBI nnes.  
\v 22 Zi macca \add n tewhibt\add* n AREBBI nnes iɛeddeř ad zzayes yecc, am zi min iǧan iqeddsen qaɛ am zi min iqeddsen.  
\v 23 Maca war iɛeddeř ad dd-iqarreb ɣar uřeḥḥaf uřa ɣar uɛalṭar, minzi dayes ict n uneɛḍab, ḥima war issexsara Tizawiyyin Iqeddsen inu, minzi Necc d SIDI wenni ten issqeddsen.’”   
\m
\v 24 \add Ammu\add* i issiweř Musa ak-d Harun u ak-d warraw nnes u ak-d marra ayt n Israil.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 22
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d Harun u ak-d warraw nnes, maḥend, \add mařa ittxeṣṣa\add*, war ttakkwaḍen ɣar tewhibin iqeddsen n ayt n Israil tinni d ayi ssqeddsen, ḥima war ssexsaran Isem amqeddas inu. Necc d SIDI!   
\m
\v 3 Ini asen: ‘Marra aryaz zi zzariɛet nwem di \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem, wenni dd ɣa iqarrben ɣar tewhibin iqeddsen, tinni ssqeddsen ayt n Israil i SIDI, am ixmej netta, aqa ad ittwaqess řeɛmar nni zi zzat i wudem inu. Necc d SIDI.  
\v 4 Uřa d ijjen zi zzariɛet n Harun nni di iǧa řbarṣ niɣ wenni ɣar iǧa useyyeř, war ittett zi tewhibin iqeddsen ař ɣa yiři izdig. Wenni iḥadan ca zi min ittwassxemjen s ijj n umettin niɣ s ijj n weryaz nni tuɣa s useyyeř n waǧu, \x ◘ \xo 22:4 \xt Lawi 15:2\x*  
\v 5 niɣ s ijj n weryaz nni iḥadan ca min ittbuɛen i zi idweř ixmej, niɣ \add iḥada\add* ijj n bnadem i zi idweř ixmej s mammec ma tegga texmuji nnes,  
\v 6 řeɛmar nni iḥadan tmesřact niɣ bnadem nni ad yiři ixmej ař tameddit, war ittett zi tewhibin iqeddsen, mɣir awarni i ɣa issird arrimet nnes s waman.  
\v 7 \add Xmi\add* dd ɣa teɣři tfuct, ad yiři izdig. Awarni aya ad yecc zi tewhibin iqeddsen, minzi aqa atent d macca nnes.  
\v 8 War ittett zeg ict n řxecbet niɣ zeg \add ijj n umuddar\add* imezzqen, minzi zzayes i ɣa issexmej ixef nnes, Necc d SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 22:8 \xt Uf. 22:31; Lawi 17:15; Ḥiz. 44:31\x*  
\v 9 Ad ḥḍan min xef ten weṣṣiɣ, ḥima war ssarebbun x yixef nsen ddenb u xenni ad zzayes mmten, xmi ɣa ssɛiǧten aya. Necc d SIDI wenni ten issqeddsen.   
\m
\v 10 Uřa d ijj n ubarrani war ittett zi tewhibt iqeddsen. Amɛezzeb \add i izeddɣen\add* jar ikehhanen uřa d acewwař war ttᵉtten zi tewhibt iqeddsen.  
\v 11 \add Maca\add* mařa akehhan isɣa ijj n bnadem s nnuqart nnes, aqa iɛeddeř i wa maḥend ad yecc zi macca \add n tewhibt\add* nnes, uřa i yinni dd-ittwaxeřqen di taddart nnes.  
\v 12 Mařa yeǧis n ukehhan tedweř d tamɣart n ijj n ubarrani, war tᵉttett ca zi \add tewhibt\add* i dd-ittwassgeɛɛden zi tewhibin iqeddsen.  
\v 13 \add Maca\add* mařa yeǧis n ukehhan aqa-tt d tajjač niɣ tᵉttwaǧef \add zeg weryaz nnes\add* uca war ɣares aḥenjir uca tedweř-dd ɣar taddart n babas, am di temẓi nnes, \add xenni\add* ad tecc zi macca \add n tewhibt\add* n babas, \add maca\add* uřa d ijj n ubarrani ad zzayes yecc. \x ◘ \xo 22:13 \xt Lawi 10:14\x*   
\m
\v 14 Mařa ca n yijjen icca zi tewhibt iqeddsen s uweddar, \add xenni\add* ad ɣares yarni tasɣart n texmusect uca ad yarr tawhibt iqeddsen ɣar ukehhan.  
\v 15 War iɛeddeř ad ssexsaren tiwhibin iqeddsen n ayt n Israil, tinni ssgeɛɛden nitni ɣar SIDI,  
\v 16 \add ařami\add* i ɣa ssarbun amarwas n řmuɛṣiyyet \add x ayt n Israyil\add*, umi ɣa ccen nitni zi tewhibin nsen iqeddsen \add i d yawyen nitni s yixef nsen\add*, minzi Necc d SIDI, wenni ten issqeddsen.’”   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tiɣarṣa i iṭṭewɛen ayt n Israil  
\m
\v 17 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa inna:   
\m
\v 18 “Siweř ak-d Harun d warraw nnes u ak-d marra ayt n Israil uca ini asen: ‘D man aya iggur i kuř ijjen zi taddart n Israil u i ibarraniyyen di Israil, wenni i ɣa yiwyen tawhibt nnes tenni dd-yusin ak-d marra řewɛud nsen d marra tiwhibin nsen nni wcin s řxaḍar, tenni qeddmen nitni d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI.  
\v 19 Maḥend ad kenniw yarr ad tiřim tᵉttwaqebbřem ittxeṣṣa ad tiři tewhibt d ijj n wewtem icnan qaɛ zeg ifunasen niɣ zeg izmaren niɣ zeg icarriyyen.  
\v 20 War iɛeddeř ad tqeddmem ca \add n řmař\add* dayes aneɛḍab, minzi aya war kenniw dd-ittarri ad daywem ittwaf arḍa.   
\m
\v 21 Mařa ijj n weryaz iqeddem ict n tɣarṣt n řehna ɣar SIDI, maḥend ad ikemmeř ijj n lwaɛd niɣ am yict n tewhibt s řxaḍar, \add xenni ad tiři taɣarṣt d ijj n umuddar\add* icnan qaɛ zi řebhayem niɣ zeg wuǧi, ḥima ad dayes ittwaf arḍa. War iɛeddeř ad dayes yiři uřa d ijj n řɛib. \x ◘ \xo 22:21 \xt Aɛwd. 15:21; 17:1\x*  
\v 22 Min iǧan d adarɣař niɣ min ittwarẓen niɣ min di iǧan ijj n uyezzim yarezmen niɣ min di ǧant tfiḍřiwin niɣ jdam niɣ ccamet texsar war t-i-dd-tessqarrabem ca ɣar SIDI uca war zzayes ttiwyem tawhibt n tmessi i SIDI x uɛalṭar.   
\m
\v 23 \add Maca\add* ijj n ufunas niɣ ijjen zeg wuǧi i iqebḥen zi ssibbet n tuzzeggart niɣ tuquḍeḍt aṭṭas, iɛeddeř ad t-i-dd-tesswejded am yict n tewhibt s řxaḍar, maca war dayes ittwaf arḍa i yijj n lwaɛd.  
\v 24 Min idgeddgen, min iřebzen, min imezzqen, min ittwaqessen war t ttiwyem ɣar SIDI, war tteggem \add aya\add* di temmurt nwem.  
\v 25 Zeg ufus n mmis n ubarrani war ttqeddamem ca zi marra man aya uřa d \add ict n tewhibt d macca\add* i AREBBI, minzi dayes řɣecc nsen uřa d nneqṣan nnes, \add man aya\add* war ittwaqebbiř ca di ṭṭweɛ nwem.’”   
\m
\v 26 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 27 “Xmi dd-ixeǧeq ufunas niɣ izmar niɣ iɣayḍ, \add xenni\add* ad yiři sadu \add ḥeṭṭu\add* n yemmas sebɛa n wussan. Zeg wass wiss tmenya u awarni as ad iṣřeḥ i yarḍa am tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI.  
\v 28 War iɛeddeř ad tɣarṣed i ufunas niɣ i yijjen zeg wuǧi ak-d mmis deg wass d ijj.  
\v 29 X minni texsem ad tqeddmem tawhibt n uqadi i SIDI, qeddem \add xenni\add* min iṣeřḥen i yarḍa nwem.  
\v 30 Ad tᵉttwacc deg wass nni nnit. War zzayes ttejjim ca ař ṣṣbeḥ. Necc d SIDI! \x ◘ \xo 22:30 \xt Lawi 7:15\x*   
\m
\v 31 Ad teḥḍam tiweṣṣa inu uca ad zzaysent teggem. Necc d SIDI!   
\m
\v 32 War ssexsaram Isem inu iqeddsen, \add ḥima\add* Necc ad ttwaqeddseɣ di řwest n ayt n Israil. Necc d SIDI, wenni kenniw issqeddsen,  
\v 33 d wenni kenniw dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima ad iřiɣ d AREBBI i kenniw. Necc d SIDI!’”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 23
\s1 Řeɛyudat n SIDI  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca ini asen: ‘Řeɛyudat ittwaggen n SIDI, inni x ɣa tbarrḥem, ad iřin d imuniten iqeddsen, aqa atent d řeɛyudat inu ittwaggen.  
\v 3 Setta n wussan ad txedmem, maca deg \bd wass wiss sebɛa ad yiři d ssebt\bd*, arraḥet imun, ijj n umuni iqeddsen. Ittxeṣṣa war dayes txeddmem. Aqa d ssebt i SIDI di marra tizeddiɣin nwem. \x ◘ \xo 23:3 \xt Uf. 20:9; 23:12; Aɛwd. 5:13; Lk. 13:14\x*   
\m
\v 4 Aqa d ina d řeɛyudat ittwaggen n SIDI, imuniten iqeddsen, inni i ɣa tbarrḥem deg wussan nsen ittwaggen.   
\m
\v 5 Deg uyur amezwaru, deg \add wass\add* wiss arbeɛṭac n uyur, jar beddu n wezyen n wass ař dd-tewḍa tmeddit, ad tiři d \bd \+bdit Tɣarṣt n\+bdit* Useɛdu n SIDI\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 23:5 \xt Uf. 12:18; 23:15; Řxř. 28:16; Aɛwd. 16:1\x*  
\v 6 Deg wass wiss xemmesṭac n uyur nnit, \add ad yiři\add* d \bd Řɛid n Weɣrum břa Antun\bd* i SIDI. Sebɛa n wussan ad teccem aɣrum břa antun.  
\v 7 Ass amezwar ad teggem ijj n umuni iqeddsen. War tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet i ittxeṣṣan ad tᵉttwagg.  
\v 8 Sebɛa n wussan \add kemmřen\add* ad tawyem ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI uca deg wass wiss sebɛa ad din yiři ijj n umuni iqeddsen. War tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet i ittxeṣṣan ad tᵉttwagg.’”   
\m
\v 9 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 10 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini asen: ‘Mařa tiwḍem ɣar temmurt nni d awem ɣa wceɣ uca ad temjarem ṣṣabet nnes, xenni ad tawyem \bd ict n tqebbiḍt zi tmezwarut n ṣṣabet nwem\bd* ɣar ukehhan.  
\v 11 Uca netta ad issenhezz taqebbiḍt \add nni\add* zi ssa ɣar da zzat i wudem n SIDI, maḥend ad tᵉttwaqebřem s arḍa. Di tuffut awarni ssebt ad tt issenhezz ukehhan.  
\v 12 Deg wass min di i ɣa tenhezzem taqebbiḍt, ad tesswejdem \add ɛawed\add* ijj n izmar icnan qaɛ n ijj n useggʷas am yict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI.  
\v 13 Ad tiři tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* zi tnayen n teɛcuray n ijj n ifa n waren azdad ixeǧḍen s zzect, aqa-tt d ict n tewhibt n tmessi s ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI, u tawhibt nnes n useyyeb ad tiři d binu, ijj n arbeɛ zeg ijj n uhinu.  
\v 14 War ttᵉttem aɣrum uřa d tidrin yurfen niɣ tizizawin ař ass min di dd-tiwyem tawhibt nwem ɣar AREBBI. Aqa-tt d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem mani ma tzeddɣem.   
\m
\v 15 \add Awarni as\add* ad tḥesbem s řmeqřub i yixef nwem zi ṣṣbeḥ awarni i ssebt, zeg wass min di dd-tiwyem taqebbiḍt n tewhibt n wenhezzi: ittxeṣṣa ad iřin \bd sebɛa n wussan n ssebt kemmřen\bd*. \x ◘ \xo 23:15 \xt Aɛwd. 16:9, 10 \x*  
\v 16 Ad tḥessbem \bd xemsin n wussan\bd* ař tuffut n ssebt wiss sebɛa. Xenni ad tawyem ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* n jdid i SIDI.  
\v 17 Ad dd-tawyem tnayen n tecnifin n weɣrum i wenhezzi zeg imucan mani tzeddɣem. Ad iřint zi tnayen n teɛcuray \add n yijj n ifa\add* n waren azdad, ggwint s wentun. Aqa atent d timenza i SIDI.  
\v 18 Kenniw ad dd-tessqarrbem ak-d weɣrum \add ɛawed\add* sebɛa n izmaren cnan qaɛ n ijj n useggʷas d ijj n ufunas - ameẓyan n tfunast - d tnayen n icarriyyen. Ad iřin i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI ak-d tewhibt nsen \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tewhibin nsen n useyyeb, \add aqa\add* d ict n tewhibt n tmessi s ict n řefwaḥet ittfuḥen i SIDI.  
\v 19 Ad tesswejdem \add ɛawed\add* ijj n umyan zeg iɣayḍen d taɣarṣt n ddenb u tnayen n izmaren n ijj n useggʷas d tɣarṣt n řehna.  
\v 20 Ad ten issenhezz ukehhan ak-d weɣrum n tamenzut zi ssa ɣar da am yict n tewhibt n wenhezzi zzat i wudem n SIDI, uřa d tnayen n izmaren. Ad iřin qeddsen i SIDI, i ukehhan.  
\v 21 Deg wass nnit ad tbarrḥem i yijj n umuni iqeddsen. War tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet i ittxeṣṣan ad tᵉttwagg. \add Aqa-tt\add* d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda mani ma i ɣa tzedɣem i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem.   
\m
\v 22 Xmi ɣa temjarem řɣiǧet n temmurt nwem, war mejjar ař aneggar n ṭṭarf n yeyyar nnec, u min iqqimen n řɣiǧet nnec war t tkessed ca. Ittxeṣṣa ad tejjem \add cwayt\add* i umezřuḍ u i ubarrani. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!’” \x ◘ \xo 23:22 \xt Lawi 19:9; Aɛwd. 24:19\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 23 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 24 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil, ini asen: ‘Deg uyur wiss sebɛa, deg \add wass\add* amezwaru n uyur, ad yiři d ssebt i kenniw, \bd ijj n \+bdit wass\+bdit* n řidaret ak-d usuḍi s wesruddeḥ \+bdit deg uyicc n icarri\+bdit*\bd*, ijj n umuni iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 23:24 \xt Řxř. 29:1\x*  
\v 25 War tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet i ittxeṣṣan ad tᵉttwagg. Ad dd-tesqarrbem ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI.’”   
\m
\v 26 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 27 “Deg \add wass\add* wiss ɛecra n uyur wiss sebɛa ad yiři d \bd Ass n Weṣřaḥ\bd*. Ad teggem ijj n umuni iqeddsen i kenniw. Ad tesswaḍɛem ixef nwem uca ad tqeddmem ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 23:27 \xt Lawi 16:29,31; Řxř. 29:7\x*  
\v 28 War tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet deg wass nni nnit, minzi aqa-t d Ass n Weṣřaḥ, maḥend ad ittwagg weṣřaḥ i kenniw zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem.  
\v 29 Minzi marra bnadem nni war isswaḍɛen ixef nnes deg wass nni nnit, ad ittwaqess zi řgens nnes.  
\v 30 Kuř bnadem nni i ɣa iggin ca n řxedmet deg wass nni nnit, Necc ad teḥḥiɣ bnadem nni zi řwesṭ n řgens nnes. \f ◼ \fr 23:30 \ft \+fk bnadem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*  
\v 31 War tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet. \add Aqa-tt\add* d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem mani ma i ɣa tzedɣem.  
\v 32 Ad yiři d ijj n ssebt n arraḥet tmun i kenniw. Ad iřin řeɛmur nwem ḥṣaren. Deg \add wass\add* wiss tesɛa n uyur, di ǧiřet, zeg uɛecci ɣar uɛecci nneɣni ad teḥḍam arraḥet nwem n ssebt.”   
\m
\v 33 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 34 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca ini: ‘Deg wass wiss xemmesṭac n uyur wiss sebɛa \add ad yiři\add* d \bd Řɛid n Iɛuccuten\bd* i SIDI, sebɛa n wussan. \x ◘ \xo 23:34 \xt Uf. 23:16; Řxř. 29:12; Aɛwd. 16:15\x*  
\v 35 Deg wass amezwaru ad yiři yijj n umuni iqeddsen. War tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet i ittxeṣṣan ad tᵉttwagg.  
\v 36 Sebɛa n wussan ad tqeddmem tiwhibin n tmessi ɣar SIDI. Deg wass wiss tmenya ad din yiři yijj n umuni iqeddsen uca ad tawyem ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI. Aqa d ijj n umuni ifarzen \add d amqeddes\add*, war tteggem uřa d ict n řxedmet i ittxeṣṣan ad tᵉttwagg. \x ◘ \xo 23:36 \xt Yḥ. 7:37\x*   
\m
\v 37 Tina d řeɛyudat ittwaggen n SIDI, tinni zi ɣa tbarrḥem d imuniten iqeddsen, maḥend ad tqeddmem ict n tewhibt n tmessi ɣar SIDI, ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet,\add* ict n tewhibt i tɣarṣt d tewhibin n useyyeb, kuř ass min ittwaggen i wass nni,  
\v 38 barra i \add tɣarṣa nwem n\add* wussan n ssebt n SIDI d tewhibin nwem n lwuɛud nwem d tewhibin nwem s řxaḍar, inni \add tᵉttnumem\add* ad tent tewcem i SIDI.  
\v 39 Maca deg wass wiss xemmesṭac n uyur wiss sebɛa, xmi ɣa tessmunem řɣiǧet n temmurt, \add xenni\add* ad tɛeyydem Řɛid n SIDI, sebɛa n wussan. Deg wass amezwaru \add ad yiři\add* yijj n wass n ssebt uřa deg wass wiss tmenya \add ad din yiři\add* yijj n wass n ssebt.  
\v 40 Deg wass amezwaru ad teksim řɣiǧet n tcejjura icewwaren: tiseḍwin n tini d tiseḍwin n tcejjura s tefray aṭṭas d \add tseḍwin\add* n tcejjart n tnemřač n tɣezratin. Sebɛa n wussan ad tfarḥem zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem. \f ◼ \fr 23:40 \ft \+fk tacejjart n tnemřač\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘tacejjart n yeɣzar’.\f*  
\v 41 Ad tɛeyydem Řɛid \add n Iɛuccuten\add* sebɛa n wussan deg useggʷas i SIDI. \add Aqa-tt\add* d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem. Ad t tɛeyydem deg uyur wiss sebɛa.  
\v 42 Ad tzedɣem sebɛa n wussan deg iɛuccuten. Marra inni dd-ittwaxeřqen di Israil ad zedɣen deg iɛuccuten,  
\v 43 ḥima ad ssnen \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem, belli Necc ggiɣ ad zedɣen ayt n Israil deg iɛuccuten, umi ten ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra. Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!’”   
\m
\v 44 \add Ammu\add* i issiweř Musa ak-d ayt n Israil x řeɛyudat ittwaggen n SIDI.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 24
\s1 Izerfen i řqendiř d weɣrum n wesscan  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Umur ayt n Israil maḥend ad ac dd-awyen i tfawt zzect iṣfan ttwaddzen tt-i-dd zi zzitun, ḥima ad tejjem tafawt tareqq řebda.  
\v 3 Harun ad tt isettef řebda zzat i wudem n SIDI zi ǧiřet ař ṣṣbeḥ zzat n uřeḥḥaf n Cchadet deg Uqiḍun n Umsagar. \add Aqa-tt\add* d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda i \add marra\add* jjiřat nwem.  
\v 4 Ittxeṣṣa as ad isettef řebda \add tiftiřin n\add* tfawin i iǧan x řqendiř izdigen zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 5 Ad teksid waren azdad uca ad zzayes tᵉssenggʷed tenɛac n řemsemnat. Ict n temsemmemt ad tiři zi tnayen n teɛcurin \add n yijj n ifa n waren azdad\add*.  
\v 6 Ad tent tegged di tnayen n isettifen, setta deg ijj n usettif x tzewḍa izdigen zzat i wudem n SIDI.  
\v 7 Ad tegged x \add kuř\add* asettif jjawi iṣfan nni ɣa yiři i řidaret ak-d weɣrum. \add Aqa-tt\add* d ict n tewhibt n tmessi i SIDI.  
\v 8 Di kuř ass n ssebt ad isettef aya řebda zzat i wudem n SIDI di ṭṭweɛ n ayt n Israil. \add Aqa-t\add* d ijj n Řɛahd i řebda.  
\v 9 Ad yiři \add weɣrum\add* i Harun d warraw nnes, inni t ɣa iccen deg wemcan amqeddas, minzi i netta i iǧa uya d amqeddas qaɛ zi tewhibin n tmessi n SIDI. \add Aqa-tt\add* d ict n tewṣeyyet i řebda.” \x ◘ \xo 24:9 \xt Uf. 29:32; Lawi 8:31; 1 Ṣm. 21:6; Mt. 12:4\x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Řɛiqab i wenni iceqqfen di SIDI u i wenni iggin tuɛeffna  
\m
\v 10 Mmis n ict n temɣart Tisra’ilect teffeɣ ɣar barra. Netta tuɣa-t d mmis n ijj n weryaz d Amiṣri izeddɣen jar ayt n Israil. Mmis n temɣart-a Tisra’ilect u ijj n weryaz Israyili mmenɣen ak-d wayawya di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.  
\v 11 Mmis n temɣart Tisra’ilect iceqqef deg Yisem uca ikkʷar. \add Xenni\add* iwyen t ɣar Musa. Yemmas, qqaren as Cilumiya, yeǧis n Dibri, zi teqbič n Dan.  
\v 12 Ggin ad xas ḥḍan ařami d asen i ɣa immeř \add min i ɣa ggen\add* zeg uqemmum n SIDI.  
\v 13 Uca issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:  
\v 14 “Suffeɣ wenni ineɛřen barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar uca ejj marra inni d as isřin ad ssarsen ifassen nsen x uzeǧif nnes. \add Xenni\add* ad t tarjem tmesmunt am tekmeř.  
\v 15 Ad tessiwřed ak-d marra ayt n Israil uca ad asen tinid: ‘Kuř aryaz i ɣa ineɛřen AREBBI, ad yarbu ddenb nnes.  
\v 16 Wenni ittceqqafen deg Yisem n SIDI, ad ittwaneɣ nican!’ Marra tamesmunt ad t tarjem. Ad ittwaneɣ ubarrani uřa d wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen di temmurt mařa ittceqqef deg Yisem.”   
\b  
\m
\v 17 “Mařa ijj n weryaz inɣa řeɛmar n ca n bnadem nneɣni, \add xenni\add* ad ittwaneɣ nican.  
\v 18 \add Maca\add* wenni inɣin řeɛmar n ict n řebhimet, ad yarr řeɛmar s řeɛmar.  
\v 19 Mařa ijj n weryaz issyizem jjar nnes, \add xenni\add* ad zzayes ggen am mammec igga netta:  
\v 20 tareẓẓit s tareẓẓit, tiṭṭ s tiṭṭ, tiɣmest s teɣmest. Anect issyizzem netta ijj n bnadem, \add ammu\add* i d as ɣa ggen \add ɛawed\add*. \x ◘ \xo 24:20 \xt Uf. 21:24; Aɛwd. 19:21; Mt. 5:38\x*  
\v 21 Wenni inɣin ict n řebhimet, ad tt yarr, u wenni inɣin ijj n bnadem, ad ittwaneɣ \add simant nnes\add*.  
\v 22 Ad ɣarwem yiři d ijj n uzerf i ubarrani am i wenni dd-ixeřqen di temmurt, minzi Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!”   
\b  
\m
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* inna Musa i ayt n Israil ad ssuffɣen wenni tuɣa ineɛɛřen barra i řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, ḥima ad t arejmen. Uca ayt n Israil ggin am mammec d as yumur SIDI i Musa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 25
\s1 Aseggʷas n ssebt d useggʷas n usřiwřew  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa x wedrar n Sina, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca ini asen: ‘Xmi ɣa tawḍem ɣar temmurt nni d awem ɣa wceɣ, xenni ad tareyyeḥ temmurt, ijj n wareyyeḥ n ssebt i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 25:2 \xt Uf. 23:10\x*  
\v 3 Setta n iseggʷusa ad tzarɛed iyyar nnec uca setta n iseggʷusa ad tezbared tizayarin n umarjeɛ nnec uca ad tessmuned řɣiǧet nnes,  
\v 4 maca \bd deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa ad tiři ict n arraḥet n ssebt i temmurt, ijj n ssebt i SIDI\bd*. War tzarrɛed ca iyyar nnec u war tzebbared ca tizayarin n umarjeɛ nnec.  
\v 5 Min dd-iɣemmyen amenni waha, war t mejjarem u aḍiř war t zebbarem zi \add tzayart\add* nnec i war ittwiḥidin. Ad yiři d ijj n useggʷas n ssebt i temmurt.  
\v 6 Ṣṣabet n arraḥet n ssebt n temmurt nnec ad awem tiři d macca, i cek, i yismeɣ nnec, i tayya nnec, i ucewwař nnec uřa i umɛezzeb nnec, inni akidek izeddɣen am yibarraniyyen.  
\v 7 Ṣṣabet nnes marra ad tiři d macca i řebhayem u i řmař nni \add iǧan\add* di temmurt nnec.’”   
\m
\v 8 “Ad tḥessbem kenniw \add ɛawed\add* sebɛa n ssimanat n iseggʷusa, sebɛa wwet i-tt di sebɛa n iseggʷusa, maḥend ad awḍen wussan n sebɛa n simanat n iseggʷusa \add munen\add* ɣar tesɛa u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa. \f ◼ \fr 25:8 \ft \+fk ssimanat\ft  - niɣ ‘imalasen’.\f*  
\v 9 Xenni deg uyur wiss sebɛa, deg wass wiss ɛecra n uyur, ad tejjed asuḍi deg uyicc n icarri ad ittekk \add x temmurt nwem\add* s wesruddeḥ. Deg Wass n Weṣřaḥ ad tejjem ad ittekk usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri x marra tammurt nwem. \f ◼ \fr 25:9 \ft \+fk Ass n Weṣřaḥ\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘Ass n Řefdiyyat’.\f*  
\v 10 Ad tessqeddsem aseggʷas n useggʷas wiss xemsin. Ad tbarrḥem s třelli i marra imezdaɣ di \add marra\add* tammurt. Ad yiři d \bd ijj n \+bdit useggʷas n\+bdit* usřiwřew\bd* i kenniw uca ad dd-iɛqeb kuř aryaz ɣar wagřa nnes u ɣar raǧ nnes.  
\v 11 Aseggʷas n useggʷas wiss xemsin ad awem yiři d ijj n \add useggʷas\add* n usřiwřew. War tzarrɛem u war tmejjarem min dd-iɣemmyen amenni waha, u war tzebbarem ca zi tzayart war ittwiḥidin,  
\v 12 minzi aqa d aseggʷas n usřiwřew! Aqa tzemmarem ad teccem řɣiǧet n yeyyar.  
\v 13 Deg useggʷas-a n usřiwřew ad dd-iɛqeb kuř ijjen ɣar wagřa nnes.”   
\m
\v 14 “Meřmi cek ɣa tezzenzed ca i jjar nnec niɣ mařa tesɣid ca zeg ufus n jjar nnec, war iɛeddeř uřa d ijjen ad iɣebben wenneɣni.  
\v 15 \add Ɛlaḥsab\add* řqedd n iseggʷusa zeg wami iǧa useggʷas n usřiwřew ad tesɣed \add tammurt\add* zi jjar nnec u \add ɛlaḥsab\add* řqedd n iseggʷusa n ṣṣabet ad kik yegg tamenziwt.  
\v 16 Ma aqa dinni ɛad aṭṭas n iseggʷusa ɣar zzat, xenni ad tarnid di ttaman n tmesɣiwt nnes u mařa aqa dinni ɛad drus n iseggʷusa ɣar zzat, xenni ad tessneqṣem di ttaman n tmesɣiwt nnes, minzi netta ad ac tt izzenz ɛlaḥsab řqedd n \add iseggʷusa n\add* ṣṣabet.  
\v 17 War ittɣebbi ḥed jjar nnes. Ggʷed AREBBI nnec, minzi aqa Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem!”   
\m
\v 18 “Ḍfarem tiweṣṣa inu, ḥḍam lfarayiḍ inu uca ggem zzaysent, ad tzedɣem \add xenni\add* di temmurt di řaman.  
\v 19 Tammurt ad tewc řɣiǧet nnes u kenniw ad zzayes teccem ař ɣa tejjiwnem uca ad din tzedɣem di řaman.  
\v 20 Uca mařa tennim: ‘Min ɣa necc deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa? Xzar, war nzemmar ad nzarreɛ u war nzemmar ad nessmuni ṣṣabet nneɣ!’,  
\v 21 \add xenni\add* deg useggʷas wiss setta Necc ad awem dd-ssekkeɣ lbaraka inu ḥima tammurt ad tewc rɣiǧet i třata n iseggʷusa.  
\v 22 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenya ad tzarɛem \add ɛawed\add*. Uca ad teccem zi ṣṣabet taqdimt ař aseggʷas wiss tesɛa. Ař i ɣa tiři ṣṣabet nnes n jdid, ad teccem \add ɛad\add* zi \add ṣṣabet\add* taqdimt.”   
\m
\v 23 “Tammurt war tᵉttmenzi i řebda, minzi tammurt aqa-tt Inu uca kenniw \add xenni\add* d ibarraniyyen d imeɛzab ɣari.  
\v 24 S uya ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad tewcem ttesriḥ maḥend ad ifdi tammurt di marra tammurt i ɣarwem iǧan d wagřa. \f ◼ \fr 25:24 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  
\v 25 Mařa umac iẓřeḍ uca izzenz ca zeg wagřa nnes, ad dd-yas umefdi nnes, řaǧ nnes yudsen, maḥend ad ifdi min izzenz umas. \f ◼ \fr 25:25 \ft \+fk amefdi\ft  - aryaz wenni t i ɣa ifdin. Xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*  
\v 26 Mařa aryaz war ɣares bu umefdi, \add maca\add* afus nnes izemmar ad yaf min icfan, maḥend ad t ifdi,  
\v 27 \add xenni\add* ad iḥseb iseggʷusa zeg wami tᵉttwammenz \add temmurt\add* uca ad ixeǧeṣ min iqqimen i weryaz umi tt izzenz uca ad tt-i-dd-yarr ɣar wagřa nnes.  
\v 28 Mařa afus nnes war yufi řqedd, ḥima ad as dd-yarr min tuɣa izzenz, \add xenni\add* min tuɣa izzenz ad iqqim deg ufus n wenni t isɣin ař \add aseggʷas n\add* usřiwřew. \add Maca\add* deg useggʷas n usřiwřew ad ittwafekk man aya uca ad t-i-dd-yarr ɣar wagřa nnes.”   
\b  
\m
\v 29 “Mařa ca n yijjen izzenz taddart nnes deg ict n tendint umi dd-nnḍen s weɣbar \add xenni\add* iɛeddeř ad yiři ufekki nnes ař d iɛdu ijj n useggʷas am ikmeř zi tmenziwt nnes. \add Marra\add* ussan nni iɛeddeř ad tt ifdi.  
\v 30 \add Maca\add* mařa war tᵉttwafdi di řmijař n ijj n useggʷas, \add xenni\add* taddart di tendint nni dd-innḍen s weɣbar, ad tiři řebda i wenni tt isɣin, i \add marra\add* jjiřat nnes. War tᵉttwafekk deg useggʷas n usřiwřew.  
\v 31 \add Maca\add* tudrin nni n ředcur i umi war dd-inniḍ řeɣbar ad ttwaḥesbent am yijj n yeyyar n temmurt. Danita izemmar ad yiři řḥeqq n ufekki uca ad ittwafekk yeyyar deg useggʷas n usřiwřew.  
\v 32 \add X\add* tneddam n Ilawiyyen, tudrin di tneddam n wagřa nsen, aqa Ilawiyyen ɣarsen řḥeqq i řebda ḥima ad tent fdin.  
\v 33 Mařa ca n yijjen ifda \add i-tt\add* zeg \add ufus n\add* Ilawiyyen, xenni ad tᵉttwafekk taddart i immenzen \add i ijjen i war iǧin zeg Ilawiyyen\add*, \add tenni iǧan\add* di tendint n wagřa nnes, deg useggʷas n usřiwřew, minzi tudrin n tneddam n Ilawiyyen aqa atent d agřa nsen di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil.  
\v 34 Iyyar nni iqqnen ɣar tneddam, war ittmenzi, minzi \add aqa-t\add* d agřa nsen i řebda.”   
\m
\v 35 “Mařa umac iẓřeḍ uca ifassen nnes bdan ad arjijen din ɣarek, \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad t-i-dd-tsennded maḥend ad ibedd, uřa d abarrani niɣ d amɛezzeb, maḥend ad iqqim ad ɣarek iddar.  
\v 36 War zzayes tkessid arriba uřa d arbeḥ, maca ad teggʷded AREBBI nnec, ḥima umac i din ɣarek ad iqqim iddar. \f ◼ \fr 25:36 \ft \+fk arriba\ft  - niɣ ‘řfayda’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 25:36 \xt Uf. 22:25; Aɛwd. 23:18; Awřn. 28:8; Ḥiz. 18:8; 22:12\x*  
\v 37 War d as ttic \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart s arriba u war d as ttic macca s warbeḥ.  
\v 38 Aqa Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni kenniw dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima ad awem wceɣ tammurt n Kenɛan u ḥima ad iřiɣ d AREBBI i kenniw.”   
\m
\v 39 “Mařa umac iẓřeḍ am kik iǧa uca immenz ac i cek, war t tᵉttarrid ad ixdem am yismeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 25:39 \xt Uf. 21:2; Aɛwd. 15:12; Irm. 34:14\x*  
\v 40 Ad kik izdeɣ amecnaw acewwař, amecnaw ijj n umɛezzeb, uca ad ɣarek ixdem ař aseggʷas n usřiwřew.  
\v 41 \add Xenni\add* ad xak iffeɣ, netta \add simant nnes\add* ak-d tarwa nnes, uca ad idweř ɣar řaǧ nnes u ad idweř ɣar wagřa n řejdud nnes.  
\v 42 Minzi aqa aten d imsexarren inu inni ssuffɣeɣ Necc zi temmurt n Miṣra. War ttmenzin am mammec ittmenza ijj n ismeɣ.  
\v 43 War xas ttṣeǧeḍ s řeqsaḥet, maca ad teggʷded AREBBI nnec. \x ◘ \xo 25:43 \xt Afa. 6:9; Kul. 4:1\x*  
\v 44 \add X\add* ismeɣ nnec niɣ x tayya nnec, inni ɣarek ɣa yiřin, ad iřin zi řegnus i d ac dd-innḍen. Zzaysen ad tesɣed isemɣan d teyyawin.  
\v 45 Tzemmarem ad ten tesɣem zeg iḥenjiren n imeɛzab nni izeddɣen jar awem am yibarraniyyen u zi řaǧat nsen, inni akidwem iǧan, inni ten dd-ijjin di temmurt nwem. Nitni ad dewřen d agřa nwem.  
\v 46 Uca ad ten tejjed d řwart i iḥenjiren nwem awarni awem. Tzemmarem ad ten tarrem ad awem sexxaren řebda, \add maca\add* x aytmatwem, ayt n Israil, war ttṣellṭem kuř ijj x wenneɣni s řeqsaḥet.”   
\m
\v 47 “Mařa yiweḍ ufus n ijj n ubarrani niɣ n ijj n umɛezzeb \add i izeddɣen\add* jar awem, uca umac i ɣares izeddɣen idweř iẓřeḍ uca ad izzenz ixef nnes i ubarrani nni izeddɣen ɣarek niɣ i yijjen zi jjadira n řaǧ n ubarrani nni,  
\v 48 \add xenni\add* iɛeddeř, awarni ma izzenz ixef nnes, ad ittwafdi. Ijjen zeg aytmas ad t ifdi.  
\v 49 Iɛeddeř i ɛemmis niɣ i mmis n ɛemmis ad t ifdi niɣ ijjen zi raǧ nnes i-t-i-dd-yudsen, zi řwacun nnes, ad t ifdi, niɣ mařa ɣares s min zi, \add xenni\add* iɛeddeř ad ifdi ixef nnes.  
\v 50 Ad igg řeḥsab ak-d wenni t isɣin zeg useggʷas min di izzenz ixef nnes ař aseggʷas n usřiwřew u ttaman n tmenziwt s nnuqart ad yiři ɛlaḥsab řqedd n iseggʷusa, \add inni i ɣa ittwaḥesben\add* am wussan n ijj n ucewwař \add ixeddmen\add* akides.  
\v 51 Mařa aqa din ɛad aṭṭas n iseggʷusa ɣar zzat, ad ixeǧeṣ maḥend ad ittwafdi anect n tesɣart n ttaman s \add tmenyat n\add* nnuqart i zi ittwaseɣ.  
\v 52 Mařa \add ɛad\add* drus i iqqimen n iseggʷusa ař aseggʷas n usřiwřew, \add xenni\add* ad igg i yixef nnes ijj n řeḥsab uca ad ixeǧeṣ ttaman n ufekki nnes ɛlaḥsab iseggʷusa \add i din iqqimen\add*.  
\v 53 Am yijj n ucewwař ad ɣares iqqim zeg useggʷas ař aseggʷas. War iɛeddeř ad xas ṣellṭen s řeqsaḥet zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec.  
\v 54 Mařa war ittwafdi s marra aya, \add xenni\add* ad ifekk deg useggʷas n usřiwřew, netta d tarwa nnes akides.  
\v 55 Minzi ayt n Israil aqa aten d imsexxaren inu, inni ssuffɣeɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra. Aqa Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem.”   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 26
\s1 Lbaraka d nneɛřet  
\m
\v 1 “War tteggem i yixef nwem l’aṣnam, war sbeddam řexyař ineqcen uřa d umayḍu \add iqeddsen\add*, war ssrusam řexyař n weẓru di temmurt nwem, ḥima ad as tbendqem, minzi Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem! \x ◘ \xo 26:1 \xt Uf. 20:4; Aɛwd. 5:8; 16:22; Izhd. 97:7\x*   
\m
\v 2 Ad teḥḍam ussan n ssebt inu uca ad awem iqarr ijj n uweqqar yuǧɣen i Zzawect inu Iqeddsen, aqa Necc d SIDI!” \x ◘ \xo 26:2 \xt Lawi 19:30\x*   
\m
\v 3 “Mařa ad tuyurem di tweṣṣa inu uca ad tᵉṭṭfem di tweṣṣa inu uca ad zzaysent teggem, \x ◘ \xo 26:3 \xt Aɛwd. 28\x*  
\v 4 \add xenni\add* Necc ad awem wceɣ anẓar di řweqt nnes, uca tammurt ad dd-tawi ṣṣabet nnes, uca ticejjura n yeyyar ad wcent řɣiǧet nsent.  
\v 5 Ad yiři usarwet ař ařqaḍ n uḍiř uca ařqaḍ n uḍiř ad yiři ař \add řweqt n\add* uzarreɛ uca ad teccem ař ɣa tejjiwnem uca ad tzedɣem di řaman di temmurt nwem. \x ◘ \xo 26:5 \xt Lawi 25:19\x*  
\v 6 Necc ad ggeɣ řehna di temmurt. \add Mařa\add* tᵉṭṭṣem, war ittiři wi \add kenniw\add* i ɣa issiggʷden. Necc ad mḥiɣ řewḥuc iwɛaren zi temmurt uca ssif war dd-iẓekkʷi x temmurt nwem. \x ◘ \xo 26:6 \xt Ayub 11:18, 19\x*  
\v 7 Ad teḍfarem řɛedyan nwem uca nitni ad wḍan s ssif nwem zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem.  
\v 8 Xemsa n yeryazen zzaywem ad ḍfaren mya uca mya zzaywem ad ḍfaren ɛecra-ařaf uca řɛedyan nwem ad wḍan s \add řeqḍeɛ n\add* ssif zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem. \f ◼ \fr 26:8 \ft \+fk zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem\ft  - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i wudmawen nwem’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 26:8 \xt Yac. 23:10\x*  
\v 9 Minzi Necc ad ɣarwem dd-dewřeɣ uca ad awem dd-jjeɣ řɣiǧet uca ad kenniw arniɣ uca ad ssmetneɣ Řɛahd inu akidwem.  
\v 10 \add Am\add* i ɣa teccem \add ɛad\add* zi zzad nni txeznem, ad tekksem deɣya \add zzad\add* aqdim, \add maḥend ad tejjem amcan\add* i jdid.  
\v 11 Necc ad ggeɣ Tazeddiɣt inu di řwest nwem uca řeɛmar inu war zzaywem ittɛiffi ca \add ɛad\add*. \x ◘ \xo 26:11 \xt Ḥiz. 37:26; 2 Kur. 6:16\x*  
\v 12 Ad uyureɣ jar awem, Necc ad iřiɣ d AREBBI nwem uca kenniw ad ayi tiřim d řgens inu.  
\v 13 Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni kenniw dd-issuffɣen zi temmurt n Miṣra, ḥima war tᵉttiřim \add ɛad\add* d isemɣan nsen. Necc arẓiɣ imqeǧaḍen n uzayřu nwem uca nedheɣ kenniw s wudem yuři.”   
\m
\v 14 “\add Maca\add* mařa war d ayi tesřim niɣ war tᵉtteggim marra min zi kenniw weṣṣiɣ, \x ◘ \xo 26:14 \xt Aɛwd. 28:15; Igjd. 2:17; Mal. 2:2\x*  
\v 15 uca mařa tesseḥqarem tiweṣṣa inu u řeɛmar nwem ad iɛiff zi lfarayiḍ inu, ař ɣa tawḍem war tᵉtteggem \add ɛad\add* marra tiweṣṣa inu, uca \add ammu i\add* ɣa tarẓem Řɛahd inu,  
\v 16 \add xenni\add* Necc ad awem ggeɣ aya: ad xawem dd-ssehwiɣ arjef d bu-deǧis d tmessi n arwaḥ nni i ɣa iteḥḥan tiṭṭawin uca ad ɛeddben řeɛmar. Ad tzarɛem zzariɛet nwem baṭeř, \add minzi\add* řɛedyan nwem ad tt ccen.  
\v 17 Ad ggeɣ udem inu ḍidd nwem ařami i ɣa ttwassexsarem zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nwem uca inni kenniw icarrhen ad xawem ṣellṭen uca kenniw ad tarewřem břa ad yiři wi kenniw iraran.” \x ◘ \xo 26:17 \xt Awřn. 28:1\x*   
\m
\v 18 “U mařa awarni man aya ɛad war ɣari tesřim, Necc ad ɣares arniɣ sebɛa n twařawin, maḥend ad kenniw webbxeɣ x ddnub nwem.  
\v 19 Necc ad arẓeɣ aɛeffar n jjehd nwem, Necc ad arreɣ ajenna nwem am wuzzař d temmurt nwem am nnḥaṣ.  
\v 20 Ad tḍeyyɛem jjehd nwem baṭeř, \add minzi\add* tammurt nwem war tᵉttic ṣṣabet nnes u ticejjura n temmurt war tticent řɣiǧet.  
\v 21 Mařa temɛařam kidi uca war tᵉttexsem ad ayi tesřim, \add xenni\add* Necc ad xawem dd-ssehwiɣ \add ɛad\add* sebɛa n jjrayeḥ anect n ddnub nwem.  
\v 22 Ad ɣarwem dd-ssekkeɣ řewḥuc n řexřa, maḥend ad awem xeḍfen tarwa nwem, ad sshellken řebhayem nwem, uca ad ssneqṣen \add lɛadad nwem\add*, \add ařami\add* ibriden nwem ad dewřen d ddmani.”   
\m
\v 23 “Mařa s man aya kenniw war ɣari dd-ttesřim, maca \add teqqimem\add* tᵉttemɛařam akidi,  
\v 24 \add xenni\add* uřa d Necc ad qqimeɣ ttemɛařaɣ akidwem uca ad xawem dd-ssehwiɣ \add ɛad\add* sebɛa n jjrayeḥ x ddnub nwem. \x ◘ \xo 26:24 \xt 2 Ṣm. 22:27; Izhd. 18:27\x*  
\v 25 Ad xawem ssekkeɣ ijj n ssif nni i ɣa issekkaren antaqem n Řɛahd inu ař ɣa tᵉttwassmunem di tneddam nwem. \add Xenni\add* Necc ad ssekkeɣ ṭṭaɛun di řwesṭ nwem uca kenniw ad tᵉttwasellmem deg ufus n řeɛdu nwem.  
\v 26 Xmi ɣa arẓeɣ řeɛweč n weɣrum nwem, \add xenni\add* ɛecra n temɣarin ad ssenggʷent aɣrum nwem di tefqunt d ict, uca awarni i ɣa weznent aɣrum ad t i-dd-arrent uca kenniw ad t teccem, maca war tᵉttjiwinem. \f ◼ \fr 26:26 \ft \+fk řeɛweč n weɣrum\ft  - s ḥarf ‘azeǧaḍ n weɣrum’.\f*  
\v 27 Mařa \add ɛad\add* s man aya war ɣari dd-tᵉttesřim, \add maca ad teqqimem\add* ad temɛařam akidi,  
\v 28 \add xenni\add* Necc ad xawem sɛareɣ u ad kenniw arebbiɣ, wah sebɛa n imuren Necc \add ad kenniw arebbiɣ\add* di ssibbet n ddnub nwem.  
\v 29 Ad teccem aysum n iḥenjiren nwem uřa d aysum n tḥenjirin nwem ad t teccem. \x ◘ \xo 26:29 \xt Aɛwd. 28:53; 2 Ij. 6:28; Igjd. 4:10\x*  
\v 30 Ad areddǧeɣ řegɛudi \add mani tᵉttwehhabem ddbayeḥ nwem\add*, ad nḍareɣ ipilaren nwem n arebbi n tfuct, ad arreɣ řxecbat nwem x řxecbat n imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam nwem\add* uca řeɛmar inu ad zzaywem iɛiff. \x ◘ \xo 26:30 \xt 2 Im. 34:7\x*  
\v 31 Ad arreɣ tineddam nwem d řxarbet uca ad areddǧeɣ tizawiyyin iqeddsen nwem uca war ttexseɣ ad cemmeɣ \add ɛad\add* řefwaḥet ittfuḥen nwem.  
\v 32 Wah, Necc ad areddǧeɣ tammurt uca řɛedyan nwem, inni dayes izeddɣen, ad zzayes nnxeřɛen.”   
\m
\v 33 “Ad kenniw zuzzareɣ jar řegnus uca ad kseɣ ssif awarni awem uca tammurt nwem ad tedweř d řexřa uca tineddam nwem ad iřint d řxarbet.  
\v 34 Xenni tammurt ad xas arḍan wussan n ssebt nnes, marra ussan n wareddeǧ \add n temmurt\add*, \add umi\add* i ɣa tiřim di temmurt n řɛedyan nwem. Xenni ad tareyyeḥ temmurt u ad tegg tcuni x wussan n ssebt nnes. \x ◘ \xo 26:34 \xt Lawi 25:2\x*  
\v 35 Mařa ussan n wareddeǧ ad ɣares yiři wareyyeḥ, minzi tammurt war tareyyiḥ ca deg wussan n ssebt nwem řami tuɣa kenniw tzeddɣem dinni.”   
\m
\v 36 “Ad ggeɣ tiggʷudi deg wuřawen n yinni zzaywem i ɣa iqqimen di temmura n řɛedyan nsen, ařami řḥess n ict n tfarect i yiwi usemmiḍ ad xasen yaẓẓeř u ad ten yarr ad arewřen am mammec ittarekkwař bnadem zi ssif. Nitni ad wḍan, waxxa war xasen ittiẓẓeř ḥed.  
\v 37 Ad nqarḍen ijjen deg wenneɣni am xmi ẓrin \add řeqdeɛ n\add* yijj n ssif, waxxa war xawem ittiẓẓeř ḥed. Kenniw war tzemmaren ad teqqimem tbeddem zzat i tiṭṭawin n řɛedyan nwem,  
\v 38 \add maca\add* kenniw ad tᵉttwahellkem jar řegnus uca tammurt n řɛedyan nwem ad kenniw tecc.”   
\m
\v 39 “Inni zzaywem i ɣa iqqimen ad isřawen di temmura n řɛedyan nwem di ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet nsen. Uřa di ssibbet n řmuɛṣiyyet n řejdud nsen ad sřawen nitni \add jmiɛ\add* akidsen.   
\m
\v 40 \add Maca\add* mařa neɛmen x řmuɛṣiyyet nsen d řmuɛṣiyyet n ibabaten nsen zi ssibbet n řeɣdar nsen i zi d ayi ɣdaren uca ɛawed mmɛařan akidi  
\v 41 - uca \add xenni\add* uřa d Necc mmɛařiɣ akidsen u iwyeɣ ten ɣar temmurt n řɛedyan nsen, maḥend ad taɣ uř nsen war ixtinen ad yaḍar uca ad qebřen řexřaṣ i řmuɛṣiyyet nsen -  
\v 42 \add xenni\add* Necc ad xarrṣeɣ \add ɛawed\add* di Řɛahd inu ak-d Yaɛqub uca ɛawed di Řɛahd inu ak-d Isḥaq uca ad xarrṣeɣ di Řɛahd inu ak-d Ibrahim uca ad xarrṣeɣ \add ɛawed\add* di temmurt.  
\v 43 Tammurt ad tᵉttwajj zzaysen uca ad xas arḍan wussan n ssebt nnes umi ɣa teqqim d ict n řxarbet xmi war dayes zeddɣen ɛad, uca nitni \add ad řemden\add* ad qebřen lɛiqab n řmuɛṣiyyet nsen, minzi nḍaren lfarayiḍ inu u minzi řeɛmar nsen iɛiff zi tweṣṣa inu.”   
\m
\v 44 “Sennej i uya, aqa d man aya: mařa aqa aten di temmurt n řeɛdyan nsen, Necc war ten neṭṭareɣ ca u war ten ttɛiffiɣ ař ten ɣa teḥḥiɣ u ad mḥiɣ Řɛahd inu akidsen minzi Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nsen! \x ◘ \xo 26:44 \xt Aɛwd. 4:31; Rum. 11:1, 26\x*  
\v 45 \add Maca\add* di ṭṭweɛ nsen ad ɛeqřeɣ x Řɛahd inu ak-d imezwura, inni nedheɣ zi temmurt n Miṣra zzat i tiṭṭawin n řegnus, maḥend ad iřiɣ d AREBBI i nitni, Necc d SIDI!”   
\m
\v 46 Tina d tiweṣṣa d lfarayiḍ d izerfan nni igga SIDI jar as d jar ayt n Israil deg wedrar n Sina s tsexxart n Musa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 27
\s1 Lwuɛud d ufekki zzaysen  
\m
\v 1 Issiweř SIDI ak-d Musa, inna:   
\m
\v 2 “Siweř ak-d ayt n Israil uca ini asen, aqa mařa ixs ḥed ad igg ijj n lwaɛd i AREBBI, ad yiři ttaman n ufekki n \bd řeɛmur\bd* \add ittwassqeddsen\add* i SIDI ɛlaḥsab řqimet i tqeddared cek.  
\v 3 Mařa řqimet i tqeddared cek aqa d řqedd n ijj n weryaz \bd zi ɛicrin ař settin n iseggʷusa\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad tiři řqimet i tqeddared xemsin ciqlu n nnuqart ɛlaḥsab ciqlu n Zzawect Iqeddsen.  
\v 4 Mařa d ict n temɣart, \add xenni\add* ad tiři řqimet i tqeddared třatin ciqlu.”   
\m
\v 5 “Uca mařa d ijj n ubřiɣ \bd zi xemsa ař ɛicrin n iseggʷusa\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad tiři řqimet i tqeddared i yijj n weryaz ɛicrin ciqlu u i yict n temɣart ɛecra ciqlu.”   
\m
\v 6 “Mařa d ijj n uḥenjir \bd zeg yijj n uyur ař xemsa n iseggʷusa\bd*, \add xenni\add* ad tiři řqimet i tqeddared i yijj n weryaz xemsa ciqlu n nnuqart u i yict n temɣart třata ciqlu n nnuqart.”   
\m
\v 7 “Mařa d ijj n mmis \add n bnadem\add* \bd zi settin iseggʷusa niɣ sennej\bd*, \add xenni\add*, mařa netta d aryaz, ad tiři řqimet i tqeddared xemmesṭac ciqlu u mařa d tamɣart \add ad tiři řqimet i tqeddared\add* ɛecra n ciqlu.”   
\m
\v 8 “Mařa tuɣa iẓřeḍ aṭṭas u war izemmar \add ad iwc\add* řqimet \add i tqeddared\add* cek, \add xenni\add* ad t ssbedden zzat i wudem n ukehhan uca \add xenni\add* ad iqeddar ukehhan řqimet nnes. Ad t iqeddar ukehhan ɛlaḥsab min izemmar ad issmun ufus n wenni iwcin awař, \add ammu\add* i t ɣa iqeddar ukehhan.”   
\b  
\m
\v 9 “Mařa d \bd řebhayem\bd* i zi ɣa qeddmen tawhibt i SIDI, \add xenni\add* marra min zzaysen ɣa iwc netta i SIDI, ad yiři iqeddes.  
\v 10 War ittbeddiř u war ixeǧef \add amuddar\add* icnan x wenni iqebḥen niɣ \add amuddar\add* iqebḥen x wenni icnan. Mařa ibeddeř ɛad ict n řebhimet s ict n řebhimet nneɣni, \add xenni\add* ta d tenni i x tt ibeddeř ad iřint qeddsent.  
\v 11 Mařa teǧa d ict n řebhimet texmej, war iɛeddeř ad tt qeddmen d tawhibt i SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad yarr řebhimet nni ad tbedd zzat i wudem n ukehhan.  
\v 12 Akehhan ad iqeddar řqimet nnes jar min icnan d min war iḥřin. Uca am mammec i tt ɣa tqeddared cek, am ukehhan, ammu i ɣa tiři.  
\v 13 Mařa netta ixs ɛad ad tt ifdi, ad xas yarni ict n tesɣart n texmusect n řqimet i tqeddared cek.”\f ◼ \fr 27:13 \ft \+fk ifdi\ft  - xzar Izhd. 78:35.\f*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 “Mařa ca n yijjen issqeddes \bd taddart\bd* nnes, maḥend ad tiři tqeddes i SIDI, \add xenni\add* ad iqeddar ukehhan řqimet nnes jar min icnan d min iqebḥen. Am mammec iqeddar ukehhan řqimet nnes, \add ammu i\add* ɣa tiři.  
\v 15 Mařa wenni tt issqeddsen ixs ad ifdi taddart nnes, \add xenni\add* netta ad xas yarni ict n tesɣart n texmusect n řqimet ittwaggen s nnuqart uca ad tiři nnes \add ɛawed\add*.”   
\b  
\m
\v 16 “Mařa ca n yijjen issqeddes i SIDI \add ca n tesɣart\add* n \bd yeyyar\bd* nni ɣares iǧan, \add xenni\add* ad tqeddared řqimet nnes ɛlaḥsab zzariɛet nnes. Zzariɛet n ijj n uḥumir n imendi \add ad as ggen\add* xemsin ciqlu. \f ◼ \fr 27:16 \ft \+fk aḥumiř\ft  - ‘aḥumir’ d ijj n ‘kur’ (Ḥiz. 45:11, 14). Ijj n uḥumir niɣ ijj n kur, aqa 222 litr.\f*  
\v 17 Mařa tuɣa issqeddes iyyar nnes zeg useggʷas n usřiwřew, \add xenni\add* ad tedweř \add řqimet n yeyyar\add* tbedd ɛlaḥsab řqimet i tqeddared.  
\v 18 Mařa tuɣa issqeddes iyyar nnes awarni i useggʷas n usřiwřew, \add xenni\add* akehhan ad as ihṣeb \add řqimet s\add* nnuqart n iseggʷusa iqqimen ař aseggʷas n usřiwřew \add i dd ɣa yasen\add* u \add xenni\add* ad tiři řqimet qell x řqimet \add tmun\add* i tuɣa tqeddared cek.  
\v 19 Mařa wenni issqeddsen iyyar, ixs ad t ifdi nican, \add xenni\add* ad yarni ict n tesɣart n texmusect di nnuqart x řqimet i tqeddared cek uca \add xenni\add* ad as yiři \add ɛawed\add*.”   
\m
\v 20 “Mařa war ixs ad ifdi iyyar \add nni\add* niɣ mařa izzenz iyyar i yijj n weryaz nneɣni, \add xenni\add* war izemmar ad ittwafdi ɛad \add yeyyar\add*.  
\v 21 Awarni řami dd-iffeɣ deg useggʷas n usřiwřew, ad yiři iyyar iqeddes i SIDI am yijj n yeyyar ittwaḥarrmen qaɛ. Ad yiři d agřa n ukehhan.”   
\m
\v 22 “Mařa ca n yijjen issqeddes ijj n yeyyar nni isɣa i SIDI, \add maca\add* war iǧi yeyyar n wagřa nnes,  
\v 23 \add xenni\add* akehhan ad as iḥseb ttaman n řqimet i tqeddared cek ař aseggʷas n usřiwřew uca netta ad ixeǧeṣ řqimet i tqeddared deg wass nni d ijj \add am\add* ict n tmesřact tqeddes i SIDI.  
\v 24 Deg useggʷas n usřiwřew ad dd-iɛqeb yeyyar ɛawed i wenni x t isɣa, i wenni tuɣa ɣar teǧa temmurt d agřa.  
\v 25 Aqeddar ad yiři ɛlaḥsab ciqlu n Zzawect Iqeddsen. Ad yiři ciqlu ɛicrin jira.”\x ◘ \xo 27:25 \xt Uf. 30:13; Řxř. 3:47; Ḥiz. 45:12\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 26 “Maca \bd amenzu, wenni ifarzen i SIDI zi řebhayem\bd* am umenzu, war iɛeddeř ad t issqeddes uřa d ijjen, niɣ d afunas \add i iǧa\add* niɣ d ijjen zeg wuǧi, aqa-t i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 27:26 \xt Uf. 13:2; 22:29; 34:19; Řxř. 3:13; 8:17\x*  
\v 27 \add Maca\add* mařa tuɣa-t zeg ict n řebhimet ixemjen, izemmar ad tt ifdi ɛlaḥṣab řqimet i tqeddared cek uca ad xas yarni ict n tesɣart n texmusect. Mařa war tᵉttwafeddi, \add xenni\add* ad temmenz ɛlaḥsab řqedd i tqeddared cek.”   
\b  
\m
\v 28 “\add Maca\add* uřa d ict n řḥajjet nni ittwaḥarrmen zeg ijj n weryaz i SIDI zi marra min ɣares iǧan n iwdan d řebhayem d iyyaren, war iɛeddeř ad temmenz niɣ ad tᵉttwafdi. \bd Marra min ittwaḥarrmen, ad yiři d amqeddas qaɛ i SIDI.\bd* \x ◘ \xo 27:28 \xt Yac. 6:18; 7:13-26.\x*  
\v 29 Marra min ittwaḥarrmen qaɛ \add i uteḥḥi\add*, min ittwaḥarrmen zeg iwdan, war iɛeddeř ad ittwafdi, \add maca\add* ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaneɣ nican.”   
\b  
\m
\v 30 “\bd Marra tiɛcuray n temmurt\bd*, zi zzariɛet n temmurt u zi řɣiǧet n tcejjura, \add ad iřint\add* i SIDI, aqa atent qeddsent i SIDI.  
\v 31 Mařa ca n yijjen ixs ad ifdi ca zi řeɛcur nnes, \add xenni\add* ad xas yarni ict n tesɣart di xemsa.  
\v 32 X marra tiɛcuray zeg ifunasen d tfunasin d wuǧi, zi marra min ikkin sadu uzeǧaḍ \add n umeksaw\add*, ad yiři \add umuddar\add* wiss ɛecra iqeddes i SIDI.  
\v 33 War iɛeddeř ad yarzu mammec tecna niɣ mammec war teḥři \add i teǧa\add*, uřa war t ittbeddiř ca, \add maca\add* mařa ibeddeř i-t, \add xenni\add* \add amuddar\add* nni d wenni zi t i ɣa ibeddeř ad iřin qeddsen. War iɛeddeř ad ittwafdi.”   
\m
\v 34 Aqa tina d tiweṣṣa nni i zi iweṣṣa SIDI i Musa u i ayt n Israil deg wedrar n Sina.   